decoDesc.en: You have met several operators for the first time. You now have enough operators to support more complicated tactical plans.

desc.en: Operator Contact

desc.en: Potential Unleashed

decoDesc.cn:
您的部分干员已解放了自身潜能。
正视自我是提高实力的第一步。
decoDesc.en:
Full potential has been unlocked for some of your operators. 
Proper self-reflection is the first step towards growth.

desc.cn: 潜能解放奖章
desc.en: Potential Unleashed

decoDesc.cn:
您的部分干员已解放了自身潜能。
他们超越了瓶颈，但他们相信这仅仅是一个开始。
decoDesc.en:
Full potential has been unlocked for some of your operators. 
Despite overcoming their bottlenecks, these operators believe this is just the beginning.

desc.cn: 潜能解放奖章
desc.en: Potential Unleashed

decoDesc.cn: 您的部分干员已将作战技能磨练的炉火纯青。
decoDesc.en: Some of your operators have honed their battle skills to incredible levels.

desc.cn: 技能提升奖章
desc.en: Skill Master

decoDesc.cn: 您的部分干员已将作战技能磨练的炉火纯青。您与干员之间的信任促成了这一现状。
decoDesc.en: Some of your operators have honed their battle skills to incredible levels. The trust you have built with your operators helped to make this happen.

desc.cn: 技能提升奖章
desc.en: Skill Master

decoDesc.cn: 您的部分干员已将作战技能磨练的炉火纯青。不同领域，不同专精，但您正带领着干员们向共同的未来前进。
decoDesc.en: Some of your operators have honed their battle skills to incredible levels. Despite the great diversity in their fields of expertise and skill sets, different operators work together as you lead them towards a shared vision of the future.

desc.cn: 技能提升奖章
desc.en: Skill Master

decoDesc.cn: 它承载着您的伤痕、您的荣耀、您的生命，从始至终。
decoDesc.en: It carried your scars, your glories, and your life from the beginning, and will keep doing so till the very end.

desc.cn: 完美装备奖章
desc.en: Perfect Gearing

decoDesc.cn: 证明您抵达更高探索等级的奖章。
decoDesc.en: A medal proving that you have achieved a higher Exploration Level.

desc.cn: 深度探索奖章
desc.en: Deep Explorer

decoDesc.cn:
证明您抵达更高探索等级的奖章。
更艰难的环境，更多的机会
decoDesc.en:
A medal proving that you have achieved a higher Exploration Level. 
Tougher environments offer greater opportunities.

desc.cn: 深度探索奖章
desc.en: Deep Explorer

证明您抵达更高探索等级的奖章。

decoDesc.en:
A medal proving that you have achieved a higher Exploration Level. 
You have reached the zenith.

decoDesc.cn: 您的武器库略显充实。
decoDesc.en: Your weapon arsenal seems well stocked.

desc.cn: 武库完备奖章
desc.en: Arsenal Collection

decoDesc.cn:
您的武器库略显充实。
无论是梅什科工业还是熔炉要塞，各公司的精品就在其中。
decoDesc.en:
Your weapon arsenal seems well stocked. 
It now includes some of the finest pieces manufactured by Mieszko Industries or even Fort Forgefane.

desc.cn: 武库完备奖章
desc.en: Arsenal Collection

decoDesc.cn:
您的武器库略显充实。
如此全面的收集，您是否在替武库工程师进行同类产品调研？
decoDesc.en:
Your weapon arsenal seems well stocked. 
Why acquire such an extensive collection? Are you helping our Arsenal Engineer compare weapons from various manufacturers?

desc.cn: 武库完备奖章
desc.en: Arsenal Collection

decoDesc.cn: 在无数次精致保养后，您的武器已与各种伟大传说中的珍宝并无差别。
decoDesc.en: After countless rounds of meticulous upgrades and rework, your weapon is now considered the equal of treasured relics wielded by great legends.

desc.cn: 终极武器奖章
desc.en: Ultimate Weaponry

decoDesc.cn: 在无数次精致保养后，您的武器已与各种伟大传说中的珍宝并无差别。
decoDesc.en: After countless rounds of meticulous upgrades and rework, your weapon is now considered the equal of treasured relics wielded by great legends.

desc.cn: 终极武器奖章
desc.en: Ultimate Weaponry

decoDesc.cn: 这并非刻意为之的陷阱，联盟工团正在调查抓捕相关责任人，请您放心。
decoDesc.en: Be rest assured. These pitfalls are not deliberate traps. The UWST is also conducting an investigation with the aim of apprehending those responsible.

desc.cn: “正在抓捕验收人员”
desc.en: "Auditors Trapped"

decoDesc.cn: 帝江号正计划为您研发贴地飞行设备。
decoDesc.en: Dijiang has made plans to research and develop a device capable of low altitude flight for you.

desc.cn: “非正常移动”
desc.en: "Unconventional Movement"

decoDesc.cn: 显然，本次出现在空中的并非轨道漂浮物，而是您和您的干员。
decoDesc.en: Are those fowls? Are they pieces of orbital debris? No! They're you and your operators.

desc.en: "Protocol ε 20.00m"

decoDesc.cn: 但这仍然无法令斧甲兽回头，真是可惜。
decoDesc.en: But the Axe Armorbeast still refused to turn around. Shame.

desc.cn: “人造南墙”
desc.en: "We Built the Southern Bastion"

decoDesc.cn: 您协助四位源石虫完成了搬家工作。
decoDesc.en: You helped four Originium Slugs move house.

desc.cn: “四皇会战”
desc.en: "Battle of the Four Emperors"

decoDesc.cn:
几件小事，几个包裹。
您与她相会于黄昏下的天空，空白信件之上终将写满美好记忆的馈赠。
decoDesc.en:
A few tiny errands, a few packages to deliver. 
You met her under the sunset skies. Beautiful memories and moments shall be the gifts that fill her empty letter.

desc.cn: “信使的信”
desc.en: "Letter From a Messenger"

decoDesc.cn: 您已重归塔卫二。
decoDesc.en: You have returned to Talos-II.

desc.cn: “苏醒”
desc.en: "Awaken"

decoDesc.cn: 开拓的未来已降下至四号谷地。
decoDesc.en: The future of frontier development has descended upon Valley IV.

desc.cn: “核心降落”
desc.en: "Core ex Machina"

decoDesc.cn:
您击败了“碾骨之拳”。
拥抱超域？迎来新生？您如何看待聂菲斯的宣言？
decoDesc.en:
You have defeated the "Bonekrushing Fist". 
Embrace the Æther and usher in a new future? What is your opinion about Nefarith's speech?

desc.cn: “重拳落空”
desc.en: "The Fist Misses"

decoDesc.cn:
您目击了一场突如其来的“爆炸”。
显然，发电站并非易守难攻。
decoDesc.en:
You witnessed an unexpected "explosion". 
The Power Plant is apparently not as defensible as it seems.

desc.cn: “易守‘难’攻？”
desc.en: "The Refugees Strike Back?!"

decoDesc.cn: 您击碎了局部“复生”的巨大天使。
decoDesc.en: You have defeated a partially revived Aggelos of massive proportions.

desc.cn: “碾碎星辰的残片”
desc.en: "Shards of the Crushed Star"

decoDesc.cn: 即将吞噬四号谷地的裂隙已在您与同伴们的努力下关闭。
decoDesc.en: You and your team fought hard and sealed the rift that was about to devour the entirety of Valley IV.

desc.cn: “关闭裂隙”
desc.en: "Rift Sealing"

decoDesc.cn: 不祥的征兆显现于塔卫二各处，您的旅途尚未结束。
decoDesc.en: Foreboding signs have appeared throughout Talos-II. Your journey is not yet complete.

desc.cn: “回归的噩兆”
desc.en: "Returning Signs of Ill Omen"

decoDesc.cn: 您已抵达了武陵城。
decoDesc.en: You have reached Wuling City.

desc.cn: “初至武陵城”
desc.en: "First Visit to Wuling"

decoDesc.cn:
记忆之痕于大火中变幻。
即便名为过去的碎片层峦叠嶂，但您依旧与莱万汀携手走出了无尽回廊。
decoDesc.en:
The scars of memories may change in the fire. 
Though fragments of the past have built up like imposing mountains, you took Laevatain's hand and left the unending corridor.

desc.cn: “燃尽记忆之灰”
desc.en: "Let Fire Consume the Ashen Past"

decoDesc.cn:
狼卫查明了真相，处决了背叛者。
那柄短刀插在坟前……狼群不同以往，他已清楚自己应该做些什么。
decoDesc.en:
Wulfgard found the truth and executed the traitor. 
He plunged that dagger in the earth before the grave... The Pack had changed. He knew what he had to do.

desc.cn: “离群之狼”
desc.en: "Lone Wolf"

decoDesc.cn:
一箱迟到的颜料。
沿着塔塔的行迹，绘下一幅幅涂鸦，伊冯在色彩中看到了重逢。
decoDesc.en:
A crate of pigments had arrived late. 
You followed Tata's trail and created various graffiti. In these colors, Yvonne saw the potential of reunion.

desc.cn: “爱，呐喊和原型机”
desc.en: "Love, Scream & The Prototype"

decoDesc.cn: 您帮助许许多多人解决了问题。
decoDesc.en: You helped plenty of people with their problems.

desc.cn: 助人为乐奖章
desc.en: True Altruist

decoDesc.cn:
您帮助许许多多人解决了问题。
并非作战任务，亦不谋求回报。
decoDesc.en:
You helped plenty of people with their problems. 
Not all of them involved combat, and your goal transcends monetary pay.

desc.cn: 助人为乐奖章
desc.en: True Altruist

decoDesc.cn:
您帮助许许多多人解决了问题。
受助者在今后的生活中也将帮助他人，在塔卫二，人类必须相互搀扶。
decoDesc.en:
You helped plenty of people with their problems. 
Those who benefited from your assistance will help others in return. The people of Talos-II must learn to support one another.

desc.cn: 助人为乐奖章
desc.en: True Altruist

decoDesc.cn: 您的设备已受到了一定次数的维护。
decoDesc.en: Your facility has received some repairs.

desc.cn: 依依难舍奖章
desc.en: Can't Do Without It

decoDesc.cn: 您的设备已受到了多次维护。
decoDesc.en: Your facility has received plenty of repairs.

desc.cn: 依依难舍奖章
desc.en: Can't Do Without It

decoDesc.cn:
您的设备已受到了大量维护。
显然，您帮助到了许多人，受助者无不对您的设备依依难舍，他们对您的设备竭力挽留。
decoDesc.en:
Your facility has received a massive amount of repairs. 
Evidently, you have helped many and the beneficiaries became rather attached to your facilities. They have done all that they could to keep the factory machines around.

desc.cn: 依依难舍奖章
desc.en: Can't Do Without It

decoDesc.cn: 您设置于帝江号的生产设施高效运转中，这离不开好友的慷慨助力。
decoDesc.en: Production facilities you furnished aboard Dijiang are working efficiently, thanks to the generous help from your friends.

desc.cn: 收获助力奖章
desc.en: Assist Recipient

decoDesc.cn:
您慷慨地向好友提供了生产助力。
塔卫二因您这样的助人精神而欣欣向荣。
decoDesc.en:
You generally offered production assist to your friends. 
Your altruism is the reason why Talos-II can prosper.

desc.cn: 慷慨助力奖章
desc.en: Generous Helper

decoDesc.cn:
您已进行了一定次数的情报交流。
世界随您的目光，因您的情报而扩大。
decoDesc.en:
You performed a certain number of clue exchanges. 
The world grows with your vision and the intel you have collected.

desc.cn: 情报交流奖章
desc.en: Clue Exchanger

decoDesc.cn: 能恢复理智的药剂。如果阅读本说明时眼前出现重影，建议加倍服药。
decoDesc.en: A pharmaceutical agent capable of restoring sanity. Consider doubling your intake if you see double while reading these instructions.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复理智，有使用时间限制
desc.en: Use this to recover Sanity. This item also has an expiration date.

decoDesc.cn: 应急灌装的大剂量理智药剂，效果立竿见影。它的副作用都写在了说明书上，包括造成严重失眠等等。祝您好运！
decoDesc.en: A large dose of Sanity syrup contained with an emergency-use package. Its effects are immediate. A list of side-effects, including severe insomnia, have been provided in the user's manual. Good luck!

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复100点理智，有使用时间限制
desc.en: Use this to recover 100 Sanity. This item also has an expiration date.

decoDesc.cn: 应急灌装的理智药剂，稍微加大了剂量。研发者似乎从文件中翻到了什么秘密配方，因此成倍增加了本款药剂中的糖分含量。
decoDesc.en: A moderate dose of Sanity syrup contained with an emergency-use package. The developer seemed to have acquired a secret formula from some strange documents that multiplied the amount of sugar within this specific preparation.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复40点理智，有使用时间限制
desc.en: Use this to recover 40 Sanity. This item also has an expiration date.

decoDesc.cn: 应急灌装的理智药剂小样，剂量较少。请合理安排使用，务必不要长期囤积。
decoDesc.en: A small dose of Sanity syrup sample contained within an emergency-use package. Use this item on time and avoid unnecessary stockpiling to avoid expiration.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复10点理智，有使用时间限制
desc.en: Use this to recover 10 Sanity. This item also has an expiration date.

decoDesc.cn: 请向前走吧，崭新的、无限的世界正等待着您。
decoDesc.en: Go forth. A new, boundless world awaits.

decoDesc.cn: 坚硬的血和炽热的钢在北地筑成堡垒。那里不是她的梦魇，那里仍是下一个终点。
decoDesc.en: Red hot steel and solid blood were the brick and mortar of the northern bastions. The North is not her nightmare. It is merely her next destination.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。
desc.en: A theme for the Profile screen. Profile themes are shown at various places.

decoDesc.cn: 将视野倒转，你会发现不一样的景色、不一样的心情、不一样的自己。世界变成了崭新的。
decoDesc.en: Turn your vision upside down and you'll see different views, experience different moods, and become a different you. Oh my, the world has become completely new.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。

decoDesc.cn: 如璞玉，千琢而不晦。
decoDesc.en: Like a block of natural jade, he will endure the chiseling and retain his purity of heart.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。
desc.en: A theme for the Profile screen. Profile themes are shown at various places.

decoDesc.cn: 陪她走进无忆的长夜，陪她焚尽黑暗的梦魇，陪她点燃映照前路的火焰。
decoDesc.en: Accompany her through long nights without memories. Fight with her and burn the dark, nightmarish enemies. Stand with her as she lights fires to illuminate future journeys.

desc.en: A theme for the Profile screen. Profile themes are shown at various places.

name.en: An Invite to the Melting Fire

decoDesc.cn: 亮丽的涂装，轻快的音乐，还有游戏获胜时的笑容……每个开心的时刻，她都记录了下来，与你共享。
decoDesc.en: Bright-colored coatings, an upbeat soundtrack, and a satisfied smile of victory... She has recorded every joyous moment and now she's sharing them with you.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。
desc.en: A theme for the Profile screen. Profile themes are shown at various places.

decoDesc.cn: 冰冷坚硬的岩石上开满了花朵，荒漠充满生机和暖意，悠扬的旋律在耳边哼唱……前辈，这不是梦，对吧？
decoDesc.en: Flowers blooming on cold, hard rocks ... barren lands teeming with life and warmth ... and idyllic songs humming by our ears... Professor, this isn't just a dream, right?

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。
desc.en: A theme for the Profile screen. Profile themes are shown at various places.

decoDesc.cn: 她还有许多问题等待解答，她还有许多困难需要克服。即便如此，她也一定会完成你给的每一项任务，让更多人找回笑容。
decoDesc.en: She has many unanswered questions, and many difficulties not yet overcome. Nevertheless, she will complete all of your assignments and bring back the smiles on everyone's faces.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。
desc.en: A theme for the Profile screen. Profile themes are shown at various places.

decoDesc.cn: 硝烟似散非散，千钧之躯落下生与死的棋子；剑锋倚地，支撑着铁誓，亦支撑着守望——此刻，将军。
decoDesc.en: The smoke of ruin still lingered. Numerous pieces, living and dead, fell off the ponderous corpse. His blade served as the support of his body, his steel oath, and his vigil — And then he made his move. Checkmate.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。

decoDesc.cn: 欢迎来到塔卫二，管理员。
decoDesc.en: Welcome to Talos-II, Endministrator.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。
desc.en: A theme for the Profile screen. Profile themes are shown at various places.

decoDesc.cn: 一管针剂、一朵花卉与一声感谢，您伸出了手，大地随即重新连接。
decoDesc.en: A syringe, a flower, and an echo of gratitude. You extend your hand and relink the lands.

desc.cn: 用于在个人名片处更换名片主题，会在多种场合进行展示。

decoDesc.cn: 协议启动，生命的进程已向前迈进，愿您与我们携手前行。
decoDesc.en: The Protocol has been activated. The process of life is moving forward. May you join us in our march forward.

管理员的聘用证明。
“呃，虽然您是管理员，但我想，一些具备仪式感的内容还是必不可少的……”

Endministrator's employment contract. 
"You might be the Endministrator, but protocol and directive have necessitated these formalities..."

decoDesc.cn:
佩丽卡的聘用证明。
“我们的监督如此年轻，却为所有人描绘出了终末地的未来景象。”
decoDesc.en:
Perlica's employment contract. 
"Our Supervisor might be very young, yet she has conveyed the Endfield vision to everyone."

desc.cn: 佩丽卡是一名使用施术单元的术师干员，可造成电磁属性的伤害。
desc.en: Perlica is an Arts Unit-wielding caster who deals Electric DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
陈千语的聘用证明。
“让我看看……本月陈千语和他人切磋次数增加了……呃……她一定是想通了什么武学关窍。”
decoDesc.en:
Chen Qianyu's employment contract. 
"Let me check how many times Operator Chen challenged other Endfielders to a spar... Uh... Oh dear... She probably figured out a new move and wanted to show everyone."

desc.cn: 陈千语是一名使用单手剑的近卫干员，可造成物理属性的伤害。
desc.en: Chen Qianyu is a Sword-wielding guard who deals Physical DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
狼卫的聘用证明。
“在处理开拓区居民及裂地者的相关事宜上，请您相信这位来自狼群的好猎手。”
decoDesc.en:
Wulfgard's employment contract. 
"Trust this skilled hunter of the Pack to help you deal with frontiersmates and Landbreakers."

desc.cn: 狼卫是一名使用手铳的术师干员，可造成灼热属性的伤害。
desc.en: Wulfgard is a Handcannon-wielding caster who deals Heat DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
弧光的聘用证明。
“我很想了解弧光干员作为众生长地游人是如何理解这个世界的……但和她聊天真的存在一定难度。”
decoDesc.en:
Arclight's employment contract. 
"I really want to know how Operator Arclight understands this world as a Songseeker of the Hannabit Circuit... Talking with her feels quite ... exhausting."

desc.cn: 弧光是一名使用单手剑的先锋干员，可造成电磁属性的伤害。
desc.en: Arclight is a Sword-wielding vanguard who deals Electric DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
余烬的聘用证明。
“她仍是利刃与铁壁，她的远征尚未结束。”
decoDesc.en:
Ember's employment contract. 
"Though ever the razor blade and ferric bastion, her Crusade has yet to end."

desc.cn: 余烬是一名使用双手剑的重装干员，可造成灼热属性的伤害。
desc.en: Ember is a Greatsword-wielding defender who deals Heat DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
赛希的聘用证明。
“我想我不得不承认，赛希极为擅长和机械造物相处，虽然我不是很理解她为什么想要一个和我同款的逻辑组件。”
decoDesc.en:
Xaihi's employment contract. 
"I have no choice but to endorse Xaihi's exceptional abilities in living together with various mechanical contraptions. However, I do not understand why she wants a logic module of the same model I'm using."

desc.cn: 赛希是一名使用施术单元的辅助干员，可造成寒冷属性的伤害。
desc.en: Xaihi is an Arts Unit-wielding supporter who deals Cryo DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
艾维文娜的聘用证明。
“她拥有高昂的热情，超乎常人的话术……居然还能同时拥有杰出的武力……”
decoDesc.en:
Avywenna's employment contract. 
"She is incredibly motivated and passionate... Her communication skills are impeccable... Surprising enough, she also has the fighting abilities to match..."

desc.cn: 艾维文娜是一名使用长柄武器的突击干员，可造成电磁属性的伤害。
desc.en: Avywenna is a Polearm-wielding striker who deals Electric DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
洁尔佩塔的聘用证明。
“繁复的色彩，无限的可能性，还有一丝丝甜味……”
decoDesc.en:
Gilberta's employment contract. 
"Complex hues of color, infinite possibilities, plus a dash of sweetness."

desc.cn: 洁尔佩塔是一名使用施术单元的辅助干员，可造成自然属性的伤害。
desc.en: Gilberta is an Arts Unit-wielding supporter who deals Nature DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
昼雪的聘用证明。
“‘有昼雪小姐这样可靠的人在嘛’，这是很多干员前往极端环境执行任务前为自己打气的原话。”
decoDesc.en:
Snowshine's employment contract. 
"Well, at least little miss reliable Snowshine is in the SAR team." Many operators will tell themselves this when receiving missions in extreme environments."

desc.cn: 昼雪是一名使用双手剑的重装干员，可造成寒冷属性的伤害。
desc.en: Snowshine is a Greatsword-wielding defender who deals Cryo DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
黎风的聘用证明。
“淳朴、真诚、善解人意……我感觉就在我写下这些文字的时间内，黎风说不定又完成了几项额外工作。”
decoDesc.en:
Lifeng's employment contract. 
"Simple, sincere, understanding... I got a sudden feeling that Lifeng might have completed a few more errands while I'm writing this down."

desc.cn: 黎风是一名使用长柄武器的近卫干员，可造成物理属性的伤害。
desc.en: Lifeng is a Polearm-wielding guard who deals Physical DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
莱万汀的聘用证明。
“不必害怕触碰火焰……你只需与她同行，留下难忘的记忆。”
decoDesc.en:
Laevatain's employment contract. 
"Do not fear the fire... Simply walk with her to create lasting moments together."

desc.cn: 莱万汀是一名使用单手剑的突击干员，可造成灼热属性的伤害。
desc.en: Laevatain is a Sword-wielding striker who deals Heat DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
伊冯的聘用证明。
“特立独行正是其作为天才的证明，无论是研究项目的走向，还是发现同伴们的闪光点，她总能提供最与众不同的视角。”
decoDesc.en:
Yvonne's employment contract. 
"Her unique approach and modus operandi are proof of her ingenuity. She always offers the most unique views regarding the directions of research projects or the strengths of her colleagues."

desc.cn: 伊冯是一名使用手铳的术师干员，可造成寒冷属性的伤害。
desc.en: Yvonne is a Handcannon-wielding caster who deals Cryo DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
大潘的聘用证明。
“大潘干员的亲切态度和幽默谈吐？我想一定是得益于他丰富的职业生涯：厨师、个体摊贩、电工、木工、司机……真是全面。”
decoDesc.en:
Da Pan's employment contract. 
"What about Operator Da Pan's friendly and easy-going nature? He probably acquired them from his rich career experiences: chef, small business proprietor, electrician, carpenter, chauffeur... Suffice to say, it is quite extensive."

desc.cn: 大潘是一名使用双手剑的突击干员，可造成物理属性的伤害。
desc.en: Da Pan is a Greatsword-wielding striker who deals Physical DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
秋栗的聘用证明。
“她不只是一名自荐而来的商学院优秀毕业生，更是胸中奔腾着滚烫热忱的理想主义者。”
decoDesc.en:
Akekuri's employment contract. 
"More than just a top graduate of a business school who recommended herself to Endfield Industries. She is an idealist driven by fiery passion."

desc.cn: 秋栗是一名使用单手剑的先锋干员，可造成灼热属性的伤害。
desc.en: Akekuri is a Sword-wielding vanguard who deals Heat DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
卡契尔的聘用证明。
“你是说，这次行动确定有卡契尔先生参与吗？呼，太好了，这下就让人安心多了。”
decoDesc.en:
Catcher's employment contract. 
"Did you just tell me that Mr. Catcher is gonna be part of this operation? Woot! Awesome! Now I can breathe easy."

desc.cn: 卡契尔是一名使用双手剑的重装干员，可造成物理属性的伤害。
desc.en: Catcher is a Greatsword-wielding defender. He deals Physical DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
埃特拉的聘用证明。
“你可以在任何地方信赖埃特拉，除了生活之中。对了，千万别去尝试她推荐的‘美食’，这是为你好。”
decoDesc.en:
Estella's employment contract. 
"You can trust Estella on anything EXCEPT life. And don't try any of the 'yummies' she might recommend. It's for your own good."

desc.cn: 埃特拉是一名使用长柄武器的近卫干员，可造成寒冷属性的伤害。
desc.en: Estella is a Polearm-wielding guard who deals Cryo DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
萤石的聘用证明。
“实际上，没有干员觉得她真的在存心捣乱，但这就是最麻烦的地方。”
decoDesc.en:
Fluorite's employment contract. 
"Actually, none of the operators felt that she deliberately committed the mischief. That's where things get really complicated."

desc.cn: 萤石是一名使用手铳的术师干员，可造成自然属性的伤害。
desc.en: Fluorite is a Handcannon-wielding caster who deals Nature DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
安塔尔的聘用证明。
“以安塔尔干员在源石技艺上的天赋，确实是合适的同行人选……不过最好让他少讲一点冷笑话，耶尔什够冷了。”
decoDesc.en:
Antal's employment contract. 
"Operator Antal is indeed a suitable teammate, given his talents in the Originium Arts... But Kjersch is a very cold place. His bad jokes will only make it worse."

desc.cn: 安塔尔是一名使用施术单元的辅助干员，可造成电磁属性的伤害。
desc.en: Antal is an Arts Unit-wielding supporter who deals Electric DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
阿列什的聘用证明。
“闲暇时可以和他一起垂钓，去鳞店挑选当日活鳞、新鲜情报或者下一个上钩的幸运儿。”
decoDesc.en:
Alesh's employment contract. 
"If you have time, you can go angling with him and visit his fin stall for a rich selection of live fins, fresh intel, or the next lucky person he might catch for that day."

desc.cn: 阿列什是一名使用单手剑的先锋干员，可造成寒冷属性的伤害。
desc.en: Alesh is a Sword-wielding vanguard who deals Cryo DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
艾尔黛拉的聘用证明。
“跟上她轻快的脚步，聆听大地的低语，治愈这颗星球的病痛与创伤。”
decoDesc.en:
Ardelia's employment contract. 
"Follow her light, gentle strides, listen to the murmurs of the land, and heal the suffering and pain of this planet."

desc.cn: 艾尔黛拉是一名使用施术单元的辅助干员，可造成自然属性的伤害。
desc.en: Ardelia is an Arts Unit-wielding supporter who deals Nature DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
别礼的聘用证明。
“请站得再靠前一些，别礼小姐。他们只是来看热闹，您用不着躲到墙角去。”
decoDesc.en:
Last Rite's employment contract. 
"Please, you can come a little closer, Miss Last Rite. There's no need to hide at the corner. They're just here for the crowd."

desc.cn: 别礼是一名使用双手剑的突击干员，可造成寒冷属性的伤害。
desc.en: Last Rite is a Greatsword-wielding striker who deals Cryo DMG.

decoDesc.cn:
骏卫的聘用证明。
“卫戍文明边塞的黎博利，无论是多么艰难的战况，他总是会在关键时刻，出现在文明需要他出现的位置。”
decoDesc.en:
Pogranichnik's employment contract. 
"A Liberi garrisoned at the border forts of Civilization. No matter how hard the battle goes, he would always show up in the most critical moments and at positions where Civilization needs him most."

desc.cn: 骏卫是一名使用单手剑的先锋干员，可造成物理属性的伤害。
desc.en: Pogranichnik is a Sword-wielding vanguard who deals Physical DMG.

decoDesc.cn: 用来判断是否收集到该地图的拼块，此物品不应显示
decoDesc.en: PLACEHOLDER: This item is used to test if a map piece has been acquired. This item SHOULD NOT BE DISPLAYED.

decoDesc.cn: 击败危险敌人掉落的活性化物质，可以用于调整武器，强化特殊武器性能。此样品为无瑕级。
decoDesc.en: A reactive material dropped by dangerous enemies. Can be used for weapon activation and performance boosting. This sample is rated as flawless.

desc.cn: 可以注入到武器内，提升武器技能等级。
desc.en: Infuse this into a weapon to improve its skill level.

你也太不小心了，这么贵重的芯片可不能随处乱丢，我先带走了，一会儿放到宿舍。

Letter from Witte: 
You've been careless. Don't leave important chips lying around like that. Anyways, I took it back to the dorms. You'll find it there.

decoDesc.cn: 拥有更多“体力”的象征。在必要时，概念会变成某种砖石；在更必要时，生命自然而然也是一种概念。我们的高塔即将建成。
decoDesc.en: The symbol of endurance. If necessary, this conceptual entity can become a brick. If things get even more desperate, life itself becomes a concept as well. The completion of our Tower is at hand.

desc.cn: 获取后，永久提升闪避/冲刺的体力上限。

decoDesc.cn: 在探索旅程中能够获得的经验。管理员，塔卫二广袤的大地仍在等待着您，一如既往。
decoDesc.en: A form of experience you earn as you explore Talos-II. Like always, these lands await your discovery, Endministrator.

desc.cn: 用于提升管理员的权限等阶。

desc.en: A mental concept essential for sustaining one's ego and supporting the planning and execution of various operations.

decoDesc.cn:
特制的自动化萃取器。
“您敏锐的思维将在其中与您探索世界的愿望融合，成为备用的理智药剂。”
decoDesc.en:
A special auto-extractor.
"Your keen senses shall be fused with your desires to explore this world, and create medicinal sanity supplements that you can hold in reserve."

desc.cn: 填充理智后，可以转化为理智精粹药剂。
desc.en: Fill this with Sanity to convert it into Sanity Essence.

decoDesc.cn: 能恢复理智的药剂。如果阅读本说明时眼前出现重影，建议加倍服药。
decoDesc.en: A pharmaceutical agent capable of restoring sanity. Consider doubling your intake if you see double while reading these instructions.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复理智，有使用时间限制
desc.en: Use this to recover Sanity. This item also has an expiration date.

decoDesc.cn: 应急灌装的大剂量理智药剂，效果立竿见影。它的副作用都写在了说明书上，包括造成严重失眠等等。祝您好运！
decoDesc.en: A large dose of Sanity syrup contained with an emergency-use package. Its effects are immediate. A list of side-effects, including severe insomnia, have been provided in the user's manual. Good luck!

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复100点理智，有使用时间限制
desc.en: Use this to recover 100 Sanity. This item also has an expiration date.

decoDesc.cn: 应急灌装的理智药剂，稍微加大了剂量。研发者似乎从文件中翻到了什么秘密配方，因此成倍增加了本款药剂中的糖分含量。
decoDesc.en: A moderate dose of Sanity syrup contained with an emergency-use package. The developer seemed to have acquired a secret formula from some strange documents that multiplied the amount of sugar within this specific preparation.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复40点理智，有使用时间限制
desc.en: Use this to recover 40 Sanity. This item also has an expiration date.

decoDesc.cn: 应急灌装的理智药剂小样，剂量较少。请合理安排使用，务必不要长期囤积。
decoDesc.en: A small dose of Sanity syrup sample contained within an emergency-use package. Use this item on time and avoid unnecessary stockpiling to avoid expiration.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复10点理智，有使用时间限制

decoDesc.cn: 能恢复理智的药剂。如果阅读本说明时眼前出现重影，建议加倍服药。

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复40点理智。
desc.en: Use this to recover 40 Sanity.

decoDesc.cn: 极特殊的理智药剂。若您服用后出现咽喉肿痛、胃部不适等症状，请不必担心，多喝温水即可有效缓解。
decoDesc.en: A very special Sanity potion. There is no need to panic if you experience throat swelling, throat pain, or abdominal discomfort after use. Just drink some warm water to alleviate the said symptoms.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复120点理智。
desc.en: Use this to recover 120 Sanity.

decoDesc.cn:
康克戴尔景致！体验真正上流生活！
新开拓区周边！百万机会一手掌握！
100-200㎡山水景致，宏山艺术大师精心设计。
30cm加厚防御钢板，天使超域危险与我无关。
1615年开年大促！我们做出承诺，首付最低1万，只有1万！
decoDesc.en:
Enjoy the Koncerdel view! Experience what it truly means to live the life! 
Edge of the new frontier! An investment that will rake in millions! 
100-200 square meters of picturesque scenery with interiors designed by master Hongshan artisans. 
300 mm of reinforced defensive steel (RDS) for a peace of mind against Aggeloi or Ætherside threats. 
1615 New Year Sale. Available while this special discount lasts! Make this dream home yours for a minimum down payment of 10,000! That's JUST 10K!

decoDesc.en: A uniquely flavored meat stew made using Anthony's family recipe. A wildland wanderer like Anthony often carried this chili along with him. It reminds him of home and gives him the calories he needs.
