decoDesc.cn: 一张浸水的剪报，上面所记载的事件似乎发生于很久以前的泰拉。这和莱万汀的记忆有关吗？
decoDesc.en: A soaked newspaper cutting. The events it describes seem to have occurred on distant Terra. Is it related to Laevatain's memories?

desc.cn: 一张浸水的剪报，部分文字因为被水洇湿而漫漶难辨。
desc.en: A news cutting that has been utterly soaked through. The water has made the words hardly legible.

decoDesc.cn: 莱万汀留下的一页笔记，上面记录了各种各样的地点、事物和景象，大多数都已经被划掉了。
decoDesc.en: Laevatain left this page of notes. It has a list of various locations, events, items, and sceneries, most of which have been crossed out.

desc.cn: 莱万汀留下的一页笔记。
desc.en: A page of notes that Laevatain left behind.

decoDesc.cn: 多级加工后，碳块在碳元素状态上获得了微妙且稳定的平衡。
decoDesc.en: Multiple processing steps have achieved a delicate balance for this brick of elemental carbon.

desc.cn: 致密碳粉末精炼融合后的高级材料，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: An advanced material prepared by refining Dense Carbon Powder. Can be used to make other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在协议技术介入下，经过精细研磨后，碳粉已拥有了独特的细腻质地。
decoDesc.en: Techno-Protocol grinding is used to create this uniquely fine powdered preparation of Carbon.

desc.cn: 碳粉末研磨后的细粉，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Acquired by grinding Carbon Powder. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业在战争时期就已完成了对制碳过程中废气处理的相关技术的优化。
decoDesc.en: During the war, Endfield Industries managed to optimize their waste emission carbon capture technology.

desc.cn: 植物烧制的碳材料，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Carbon captured from refinery incineration of plant matter. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，碳拥有了更细腻的质地。
decoDesc.en: Carbon can be shredded to yield a powdered product.

desc.cn: 碳材料的粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Powdered form of Carbon. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 装有武器生产流水线中剩余材料的补给箱。由于是生产结束后手动装箱，箱子中的材料数并不统一。
decoDesc.en: A supply crate filled with leftovers from a weapon production line. Since the crates are manually packed at the end of a shift, their contents are less than uniform.

desc.cn: 开启后可获得包含嵌晶玉在内的随机奖励。
desc.en: Open this to get a random reward. You might even get Oroberyls.

decoDesc.cn: 装有武器生产流水线中剩余材料的补给箱。无论怎么看，这份惊喜箱中的补给材料也着实太多了一些。
decoDesc.en: A supply crate filled with leftovers from a weapon production line. This crate-o-surprise seems to have way too much leftovers.

desc.cn: 开启后可获得包含嵌晶玉在内的随机奖励。
desc.en: Open this to get a random reward. You might even get Oroberyls.

decoDesc.cn: 装有武器生产流水线中剩余材料的补给箱。“谁的惊喜箱中材料更多”，这在一段时间内曾是帝江号食堂的主流竞猜小游戏。
decoDesc.en: A supply crate filled with leftovers from a weapon production line. "Whose Crate-o-Surprise is Truly Loaded" used to be quite an official game event in the Dijiang canteen.

desc.cn: 开启后可获得包含嵌晶玉在内的随机奖励。
desc.en: Open this to get a random reward. You might even get Oroberyls.

decoDesc.cn: 装着进阶类材料的补给箱。突破自身极限的第一步是触碰到自身极限，这需要漫长、痛苦的磨炼。
decoDesc.en: A supply crate containing promotion or tuning materials. The first step of personal breakthrough is to hit one's true limit. This alone is a long and arduous process.

desc.cn: 开启后可选择获得干员精英化或武器突破素材。
desc.en: Opening this lets you choose to receive either operator promotion or weapon tuning materials.

decoDesc.cn: 从作战记录到认知载体，为了面对更残酷的战场，我们学习战斗技巧的方式亦需不断革新。
decoDesc.en: We learn combat techniques by using combat records and other forms of cognitive carriers. Learning must also be revolutionized to prepare us for battlefields of ever-increasing brutality.

desc.cn: 开启后可选择获得干员或武器经验素材。
desc.en: Opening this lets you choose to receive either operator or weapon EXP materials.

decoDesc.cn: 卡拉德先生强烈推荐，小道奇教官亲身体验，最适合训练自身的辅助道具都在这款自选箱中。
decoDesc.en: Super recommended by Mr. Krad with Instructor Lil' Dodge as a satisfied user. This selection crate has every supporting kit and item for personal training.

desc.cn: 开启后可选择获得干员技能升级素材。
desc.en: Opening this lets you choose to receive various operator skill upgrade materials.

decoDesc.cn: 装着多种高等级泛用材料的箱子。限制干员战斗能力的，并不仅仅是种族与作战经验，有时他们只是需要一些小小的启发。
decoDesc.en: A crate that contains all sorts of quality general purpose materials. Operator combat performance is not limited by race nor combat experience. Sometimes, they just need a bit of inspiration.

desc.cn: 开启后可选择获得高阶培养素材。
desc.en: Opening this lets you acquire an advanced progression material of your choice.

decoDesc.cn: 一张厚重的调用凭证。为了能够支援您，干员们在凭证上签下了自己的名字。
decoDesc.en: A thick and heavy designation permit. Various operators have signed their names on it to provide you with their support.

desc.cn: 使用后可从6星干员艾尔黛拉/骏卫/别礼/余烬/黎风中任选一位干员调用。
desc.en: Use this to designate and acquire one of the following 6★ operators: Ardelia / Pogranichnik / Last Rite / Ember / Lifeng.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业从各地收集物资后整合出的基质箱。无论手中的武器是多么实验性的款式，你都能在这些补给中找到适合它的基质。
decoDesc.en: An Endfield crate of useful essences gathered from various regions. Your weapon can be the latest experimental prototype, but this crate will have a fitting essence for it.

desc.cn: 使用后可获得基质。
desc.en: Open this to get essences.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业从各地收集物资后整合出的武器箱。有些性情活泼的朋友会在里面放置一些危险武器当作“小惊喜”。
decoDesc.en: An Endfield crate of weapons gathered from various regions. Certain prankers have a habit of placing excessively dangerous weapons in this crate to give their friends a "surprise".

desc.cn: 使用后可获得武器。
desc.en: Open this to get weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 放置了多种武器的支援补给。在第二次天使战争的战场上，绝大部分战士都练就了随手拿起一把武器都能熟练使用的本领。
decoDesc.en: A supply option with plenty of weapons. Most soldiers who fought in the Second Aggeloi War mastered so many weapons that they could take anything from this and put up quite an impressive fight.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 为了使用者能在任何时候面对任何敌人——哪怕是最终的毁灭。武库工程师以这种标准，将最优秀的兵器置入了补给箱中。
decoDesc.en: Something that helps the user face any enemy — even if the final outcome is annihilation. The Arsenal Engineer has adopted such standards to place the best possible weapons in the supply crate.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 请启程前行吧，为了所有汗水，所有伤痕，所有钢铁与火焰。
decoDesc.en: Initiate the journey, for the sake of all the tears, wounds, steel, and fire that have been shed.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着熔铸重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected the smelting forge.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着异彩重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected a passionate range of colors.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着迅行重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected express delivery.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着坚冰重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected the hard, solid ice.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着星声重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected the cosmic voice.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着远途重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected the far expedition.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着崇山重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected the great mountain peaks.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 封装极度严密的沉重箱子。“更自由的武器选择即是更安全的战场”，武库工程师们如此想着，将曾映衬着雷鸣重械的武器们填入了箱子中。
decoDesc.en: A heavy crate with incredibly tight seals. "Availability of weapon choices translates into safer battlefield operations," thought the Arsenal Engineers. And thus they filled up the crate with weaponry that reflected the loud, thunderous peal.

desc.cn: 开启可选择获取其中任意一把武器。
desc.en: Open this to select and receive one weapon provided within.

decoDesc.cn: 通行证上的每一项都是武库工程师认真采访干员们之后所列出的，最符合大家期待的支援项目。
decoDesc.en: Every item on the Protocol Pass is gathered from official operator interviews conducted by the Arsenal Engineers. These items include support projects that everyone hopes to see.

desc.cn: 能够提升通行证等级。
desc.en: Use this to level up the Protocol Pass.

decoDesc.cn: 一部分终末地干员喜欢将协议通行证称为“许愿单”。传说只要在生日前夜许愿，并在床头放上一些衍质源石，就会有善良的武库小机器人送来令人满意的产品。
decoDesc.en: Some Endfield operators enjoy referring to the Protocol Pass as their "wishlist". According to rumors, those who make a wish and place some Origeometry by their pillows during the eve of their birthdays will receive a satisfying reward from the kind little robots of the Arsenal.

desc.cn: 使用后可激活协议通行证的源石配给档位。
desc.en: Use this to activate the Protocol Pass tier: Originium Supply.

decoDesc.cn: “好了，只要在这里签字，您就可以拥有独属于您的定制版协议通行证……嗯？效率？放心吧，必要情况下，我们会空投物资支援的。”
decoDesc.en: "Good. Just sign your name here and you'll get your very own customized Protocol Pass... Oh? Efficiency? Don't worry. We'll airdrop the supplies to your place if necessary."

desc.cn: 使用后可激活协议通行证的协议定制档位。
desc.en: Use this to activate the Protocol Pass tier: Protocol Customized.

decoDesc.cn: 清新香甜的栗子花蜜，洁尔佩塔想着你会喜欢，将它从送信途经的栗子林中买了回来。
decoDesc.en: Sweet and refreshing. Gilberta thinks you might have a liking for honey of chestnut flowers, so she bought some from a chestnut orchard during her messenger work.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复40点理智。
desc.en: Use this to recover 40 Sanity.

decoDesc.cn: 以少许海盐衬托出甜味的冰淇淋，是莱万汀喜爱的若干冰品中排名靠前的一款。
decoDesc.en: Ice cream with a dash of seasalt to bring out its sweetness. This is one of Laevatain's most preferred flavors, of which there are quite a few.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复40点理智。
desc.en: Use this to recover 40 Sanity.

decoDesc.cn: 用料颇丰的草莓可丽饼，伊冯特意为它增添了速冻仔和小嘀嗒的翻糖坠饰。
decoDesc.en: A crepe with a generous load of stuffing. Yvonne also gave it some fondant accessories in the likeness of Frost-e-Bytee and Tink-a-Bella.

desc.cn: 使用后可以恢复40点理智。
desc.en: Use this to recover 40 Sanity.

decoDesc.cn: 以协议技术特制的圆盘，使用了普通刻写手法，配合其他设备可以在干员训练时有效缓解他们的身体疲劳
decoDesc.en: A special disk manufactured using Techno-Protocol and standard data etching processes. Often used with other devices to effectively alleviate physical fatigue of operators during training.

desc.cn: 用于干员精英化阶段一和精英化阶段二晋升的素材。
desc.en: A material that promotes operators to E1 or E2.

decoDesc.cn: 以协议技术特制的圆盘组，使用了高级刻写手法，配合其他设备可以在干员训练时有效缓解他们的身体疲劳。
decoDesc.en: A special disk manufactured using Techno-Protocol and advanced data etching processes. Often used with other devices to effectively alleviate physical fatigue of operators during training.

desc.cn: 用于干员精英化阶段三和精英化阶段四晋升的素材。
desc.en: A material that promotes operators to E3 or E4.

decoDesc.cn: 生命的延续，文明的延续，于此留痕。
decoDesc.en: The perseverance of life and continuation of civilization have left their marks upon this place.

desc.cn: 用于干员技能专精提升的珍稀素材。
desc.en: A rare material that upgrades operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 以协议技术在特定侵蚀环境中提取出的稳定物质，可以使人体适应刺激性更强的强化物质。
decoDesc.en: A stable material extracted from Blighted environments using specialized Techno-Protocol. It can improve bodily tolerance for more powerful enhancement materials.

desc.cn: 用于干员技能专精提升的素材。
desc.en: A material that upgrades operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 以协议技术特制的晶体棱柱，使用了普通结晶法，配合其他设备可以提高人体对强化物质的吸收比率。
decoDesc.en: A special crystal prism manufactured using Techno-Protocol and standard crystallization processes. Often combined with other devices to improve physiological absorption of enhancement materials.

desc.cn: 用于干员技能等级提升的素材。
desc.en: A material that upgrades operator skills.

decoDesc.cn: 以协议技术特制的晶体棱柱组，使用了高级结晶法，配合其他设备可以提高人体对强化物质的吸收比率。
decoDesc.en: A special crystal polyhedron manufactured using Techno-Protocol and advanced crystallization processes. Often combined with other devices to improve physiological absorption of enhancement materials.

desc.cn: 用于干员技能等级提升的素材。
desc.en: A material that upgrades operator skills.

decoDesc.cn: 能够用来检测、验证超距作用的人工合成材料。它们是一种时间晶体，通常成对封装在静态容器内，通过观测其光学外观的回归特征来实现用途。这种材料通常十分稳定，但应尽可能避免打破它们的容器，也应避免进入一对超距辉映体之间的空间。
decoDesc.en: A synthetic item for detecting and verifying various field forces and actions at a distance. The tube usually comprises a time crystal sealed in a static vessel, and uses observable regression properties of the photons to achieve its purpose. Though typically stable, users should avoid breaking the vessel and stay out of areas between a pair of linked tubes.

desc.cn: 用于干员精英化、武器突破、干员技能专精的珍稀素材。
desc.en: A rare material for operator promotion, weapon tuning, and operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 混合D32钢与D64钢制成的新合金。自然界中不存在的人造金属材料，继承了两种原料的高强度和法术传导性，特点是大大提高了材料在源石活性不稳定环境下的性能。它尚在试验阶段，四号样品的性能价格比相对最高。
decoDesc.en: A novel and artificial alloy of D32 steel and D64 steel that cannot exist naturally. D96 steel has inherited the excellent strength and Arts conduction properties of its constituents. It also features better performance in areas with unstable Originium activities. The material is still being experimented upon, with Sample 4 offering the best cost performance index.

desc.cn: 用于干员精英化、武器突破、干员技能专精的珍稀素材。
desc.en: A rare material for operator promotion, weapon tuning, and operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 一种可能在一定程度上利用了超域性质的离子阱装置。可以忽略时间要素，在现实空间内实现对天然快子束流的筛捡和遴选。塔卫二的人类目前并不能做到主动激发和发射快子，这种装置对于固化事件随机性的实验来说是必要的。
decoDesc.en: An ion trap that might be leveraging its innate Æther properties. The lattice ignores temporal factors and is capable of detecting and screening naturally occurring tachyon beams in realspace. Since the people of Talos-II are still incapable of activating and firing tachyons, the lattice is thus essential for any experiments involving random outcome solidification.

desc.cn: 用于干员精英化、武器突破、干员技能专精的珍稀素材。
desc.en: A rare material for operator promotion, weapon tuning, and operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 一种假定的凝聚态液体。人类可以制造它，观察它的光学外观，但暂时无法测定它的实际构成形态。这种材料表现出了在人类所能配置的所有深度环境下，皆能有效防止源石挥发的性质，是一种十分优异的填充材料。
decoDesc.en: A hypothetical condensed matter in fluid state. Though it could be synthesized and the optical properties of the resulting materials could be observed, the actual structure and state of the fluid have yet to be successfully measured. The fluid effectively suppresses Originium sublimation in all Depths that could be artificially created, making it an extraordinarily effective filler.

desc.cn: 用于干员精英化、武器突破、干员技能专精的珍稀素材。
desc.en: A rare material for operator promotion, weapon tuning, and operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 一种对环境源石极为敏感的装置。能有效提升源石附近较大范围内作战武器和设备对源石的敏感性，并且是源石技艺封装存储的一种关键部件。相对于旧的双极纳米片，主要改进了在非现实空间环境下的性能。
decoDesc.en: A device that is extremely sensitive to ambient Originium. It can boost Originium sensitivity of all weapons and devices within a significantly large area. The Triphasic Nanoflake is a key component for containing and storing the Arts, and offers better performance in non-realspace environments compared to the older Bipolar Nanoflakes.

desc.cn: 用于干员精英化、武器突破、干员技能专精的珍稀素材。
desc.en: A rare material for operator promotion, weapon tuning, and operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 一块炽热的源石晶簇。道路在背后，空旷的死寂则在身前，请您……行向起点。
decoDesc.en: A blazing hot Originium cluster. The road stretches out behind you. Before you looms an empty, deathly silence. Please ... head towards the Starting Point.

desc.cn: 用于提升管理员的潜能。
desc.en: Raises the Endministrator's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一块炽热的源石晶簇。道路在背后，空旷的死寂则在身前，请您……行向起点。
decoDesc.en: A blazing hot Originium cluster. The road stretches out behind you. Before you looms an empty, deathly silence. Please ... head towards the Starting Point.

desc.cn: 用于提升管理员的潜能。
desc.en: Raises the Endministrator's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一枚被珍藏的源石碎屑，曾属于她仰慕的那个人。它寄托了那个人的期许，也点燃了少女对协议源石技术的热情。
decoDesc.en: An Originium fragment secreted away. It once belonged to the one she most admires. The fragment bore the hopes of that special someone, and ignited her passion for Protocol-Originium Technology.

desc.cn: 用于提升佩丽卡的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Perlica's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一根被精心修去了毛刺和树皮的树枝。年幼的她曾以此为剑，挥舞出自己心中的侠义。
decoDesc.en: A branch carefully cleaned to remove barbs and bark. She once swung it as a sword when she was but a girl who dreamed of being a hero.

desc.cn: 用于提升陈千语的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Chen Qianyu's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一把改造痕迹明显的旧铳。他知道里面每个零件的位置，清楚它们能在何等情境下发挥作用，也明白自己应在何时将它们拆下单独使用。
decoDesc.en: An old firearm with obvious signs of modification. He knows where every part is, the conditions in which they work, and how they could be removed so he could use them individually.

desc.cn: 用于提升狼卫的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Wulfgard's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一个羽兽木雕，来自曾被游人救助过的孩童。传承“歌谣”的游人，总是会向想活下去的人们伸出援手。如羽兽一般，风若不停，游人不止。
decoDesc.en: A fowlbeast woodcarving made by the children whom the Songseeker once helped. The Songseekers carry the "hanna" with them and always extend a helping hand towards those who wish to survive. They are like fowlbeasts. Since the winds never cease, the seekers will never quit.

desc.cn: 用于提升弧光的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Arclight's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一柄战痕累累的铁誓军制式匕首。以冰雪与高峰为证，远征仍会继续，余烬终将重燃。
decoDesc.en: A standard Oathkeeper dagger bearing the marks of many battles. With ice, snow, and mighty peaks as witnesses, the crusade shall continue, and the embers shall be re-ignited.

desc.cn: 用于提升余烬的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Ember's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一页寂语修会修士的祷词，被赛希当作了书签。这书签曾陪伴她阅遍了寂语修会无穷无尽的典藏。
decoDesc.en: A prayer of a Cabal of Tranquility cleric that Xaihi uses as a bookmark. This bookmark accompanied her as she read through the seemingly endless collection of the Cabal.

desc.cn: 用于提升赛希的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Xaihi's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一本旅行手账，夹杂着艾维文娜从塔卫二各地收集而来的纪念品。从北方旧开拓区的一撮沙土，再到最后一页与你的合照。
decoDesc.en: A traveler's diary with numerous souvenirs and memorabilia that Avywenna collected from various locations of Talos-II. These include a pinch of dirt from the Old Northern Frontiers, and a group photo with the Endmin glued upon the final page.

desc.cn: 用于提升艾维文娜的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Avywenna's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一个小巧的香囊，带着酸橙的清香，还有些花瓣的甜腻。洁尔佩塔把各种各样的材料搭配在一起。每当闻到这个味道时，就会想起她的笑容。
decoDesc.en: An intricate scented sachet giving off the refreshing scents of sour citromes and the cloying sweetness of floral petals. Gilberta made this by mixing all sorts of ingredients together. A whiff of the sachet's fragrance reminds people of her smile.

desc.cn: 用于提升洁尔佩塔的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Gilberta's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一块精巧的护身符。上面写着“永远快过风雪一步”——她想守住那些不幸身陷雪境中的宝贵生命，让他们快过灾厄、越过险境，早日踏上安稳的归途，早日回到家人的身边。
decoDesc.en: An intricate talisman engraved with these words: "May you be forever one step ahead of the storm" — Her wish is to protect precious lives who found themselves hopelessly lost in the snow, help them survive the disaster, escape the dangers, and lead them onto the safe road to home and loved ones.

desc.cn: 用于提升昼雪的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Snowshine's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一本被翻得破烂的《武典》。这里面布满了一位少年的心事，一位少年的勤励，一位少年的向往。
decoDesc.en: A very old and dog-eared Martial Codex. The book is filled with scribbles that convey a young man's feelings, his hard work and dedication, as well as his hopes and dreams.

desc.cn: 用于提升黎风的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Lifeng's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一页纸张，记满了她加入终末地之后所到过的地方、见过的人、留意的事。新的记忆，正逐渐填上往昔的缺口。
decoDesc.en: A piece of paper filled with notes about the places she visited, the people she met, and the things that mattered to her. Freshly made memories are gradually filling up the gaps in her past.

desc.cn: 用于提升莱万汀的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Laevatain's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一张前往菈梵朵玛的车票。她想邀请你一起去逛逛沙滩，吹吹海风……不过，得先完成手头这份超域的论文。
decoDesc.en: A ticket to La Fantoma. You've been invited to enjoy sandy beaches and ocean winds... But that can wait till she completes her research paper about the Ætherside.

desc.cn: 用于提升伊冯的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Yvonne's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一份特制菜单，天上飞的、水里游的，什么都有。大潘的铁锅陪他走遍了塔卫二，能盛下世间的百味。
decoDesc.en: A special menu with all sorts of fowls, fins, and everything in between. Da Pan always traveled the lands of Talos-II with his iron wok, and it has been used to prepare delicious food of every cuisine.

desc.cn: 用于提升大潘的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Da Pan's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一盒东国风味的茶点。比起独自品尝思念的味道，她更乐意在招待来客、工作茶歇和行动部署会这些场合中分享它。
decoDesc.en: A set of Higashinese snacks. Rather than enjoying private moments for nostalgia's sake, she prefers sharing the snacks in other occasions. Examples include visitors of her place, colleagues during work breaks, or teammates at operational deployment briefings.

desc.cn: 用于提升秋栗的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Akekuri's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一份手写的菜谱。里面似乎记录了Z7所有人在饮食上的好恶，从偏爱的口味到绝不会吃的食物，应有尽有。
decoDesc.en: A handwritten menu. It is extremely exhaustive, and includes every Z7 teammates' gastronomic preferences, the flavors they like, and things they would not touch with a ten-foot pole.

desc.cn: 用于提升卡契尔的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Catcher's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一张令人头晕目眩的迷幻唱片。按照埃特拉的说法，她平时就用这些声音帮助入眠，这……这能行吗？
decoDesc.en: A psychedelic vinyl that inflicts dizziness and nausea. Estella says the sounds help her sleep. Is that ... actually possible?

desc.cn: 用于提升埃特拉的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Estella's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一个形似炸弹的小装置。按顺序触动机关，可以打开外壳取出几颗小糖果。真希望平时她也只送这么友好的小“惊喜”。
decoDesc.en: A small gadget shaped like a bomb. Activate the mechanisms in the right sequence to open the casing and access the candies within. Very nice, if only she would hand out these pleasant "surprises" more often.

desc.cn: 用于提升萤石的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Fluorite's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一叠被认真收藏的信件。全部出自安塔尔远在新蓝卡坞的奶奶之手，里面饱含着亲人间最寻常的问候、最质朴的关心与最温暖的想念。
decoDesc.en: A stash of meticulously kept letters, all written by Antal's grandmother who lives New Wrankwood far, far away. The letters contain the most mundane greetings, the simplest messages of care, and the warmest lines of longing between members of a loving family.

desc.cn: 用于提升安塔尔的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Antal's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一只仿生拟饵，阿列什的最新花样，对那些凶猛的掠食鳞有着致命的吸引力。谁知道下一条上钩的是谁呢？
decoDesc.en: A very life-like lure. This is Alesh's new trick, one that exudes a lethal-dose of attraction to vicious predatory fins. Nobody knows which of them would bite next.

desc.cn: 用于提升阿列什的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Alesh's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一块岩石样本，采自塔卫二深处。它记录了大地的变迁，也铭刻了远古的伤痕，无声地诉说着这颗星球的过往。
decoDesc.en: A rock sample mined from the depths of Talos-II. It is a record of this land's geological evolution, a collection of scars from wounds suffered in eons past, and a silent testament of this planet's history.

desc.cn: 用于提升艾尔黛拉的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Ardelia's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一朵被冻气凝结的小花。同样的品种似乎在别礼老家的墓园里十分常见，但毕竟是她送的，应该没有其他意思。
decoDesc.en: A little flower frozen by frigid air. This species is often seen in the town cemetery where Last Rite came from. But since she was the one who gifted this, there shouldn't be other hidden meanings to it.

desc.cn: 用于提升别礼的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Last Rite's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一杆破旧不堪的战旗，曾迎着冷冽的寒风飘扬在雪地之上。无论面对什么样的强敌，在这片仅有生与死的战场，战旗始终屹立不倒。
decoDesc.en: An extremely tattered war banner that once stood amidst the howling cold and fluttered above the fields of snow. In battlefields populated by the living and the dead, this banner had never fallen, no matter how strong the enemy may be.

desc.cn: 用于提升骏卫的潜能。
desc.en: Raises Pogranichnik's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 一块炽热的源石晶簇。道路在背后，空旷的死寂则在身前，请您……行向起点。
decoDesc.en: A blazing hot Originium cluster. The road stretches out behind you. Before you looms an empty, deathly silence. Please ... head towards the Starting Point.

desc.cn: 用于提升管理员的潜能。
desc.en: Raises the Endministrator's Potential.

decoDesc.cn: 能在四号谷地收集到的醚质，是曾经完整之物的微小碎片。
decoDesc.en: An Aurylene that can be found in Valley IV. This tiny fragment used to be part of something greater.

desc.cn: 探索时获得的神秘物质，在协议传送点处可以提交换取奖励
desc.en: A mysterious material you found during exploration. Submit enough of them at any TP Point to get rewards.

decoDesc.cn: 能在武陵收集到的醚质，是曾经完整之物的微小碎片。
decoDesc.en: An Aurylene that can be found in Wuling. This tiny fragment used to be part of something greater.

desc.cn: 探索时获得的神秘物质，在协议传送点处可以提交换取奖励
desc.en: A mysterious material you found during exploration. Submit enough of them at any TP Point to get rewards.

decoDesc.cn: 超域沾染上处于一种空间不稳定状态的物体的碎片。
decoDesc.en: A fragment of an object touched by the Ætherside. It has unstable spatial properties.

decoDesc.cn: 超域沾染上处于一种空间不稳定状态的物体。
decoDesc.en: An object touched by the Ætherside. It has unstable spatial properties.

decoDesc.cn: 填入了肉馅的馅饼。四号谷地居民童年回忆中都有它的影子，热腾腾的馅饼、火炉、家，这些事物总能唤起人的希望。
decoDesc.en: A meat pie. Everyone in Valley IV grew up eating the famous Valley pie. Steaming pies, the stove, and a loving family always bring people hope.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 大火爆炒而成的肉丁。一盘辣炒肉丁通常能让人吃下三碗饭，不用质疑，它一直是开拓区最受欢迎的菜式。
decoDesc.en: Cubes of meat stir-fried over hot fire. A hungry diner can easily go through three bowls of rice with a serving of meat stir-fry. There's a good reason why this is the *most* popular dish in the frontier.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 以琼叶参须、兽排及多种材料炖煮而成的药膳。武陵秋冬常见菜肴。大雪纷飞时，一碗鲜美肉汤足以暖身暖心。
decoDesc.en: A herbal meal prepared by stewing redjade ginseng roots, meat fillet, and other ingredients. A common winter dish of the Wuling region. When the snow starts falling, a bowl of this hearty stew would offer the warmth you need.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 以琼叶参、锦草煎制而成的汤剂，通常被用以温补气血。许多曾受重伤的战士靠着它调理好了自身暗疾。
decoDesc.en: A herbal infusion prepared by decocting redjade ginseng and jincao herbs. Typically consumed to revitalize the body. Many grievously wounded warriors used this decoction to treat various chronic conditions.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 某位乌萨斯厨师在走南闯北过程中发明的菜式，因其巧妙的甜辣调味而闻名开拓区。
decoDesc.en: A mysterious Ursine chef came up with this recipe as he traveled across the lands. It became famous throughout the frontier for its delicious blend of sweetness and heat.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 少油少盐的炒饭，最大限度地保留了蔬菜的清香。
decoDesc.en: Fried rice made with less oil and salt to bring out the wholesome flavors of garden greens and vegetables.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 多级加工后，密制晶体足以被称为“宝石”。
decoDesc.en: The Packed Origocrust is a result of multiple processing steps and looks just like a piece of precious "gemstone".

desc.cn: 致密晶体粉末精炼融合后的高级材料，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A high quality material prepared by refining Dense Origocrust Powder. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在协议技术介入下，经过精细研磨后，致密晶体粉末中的颗粒将通透细腻至几乎不可见的地步。
decoDesc.en: Techno-Protocol grinding is used to prepare this dense powdered form of Origocrust with particles almost invisible to the unaided eye.

desc.cn: 晶体外壳粉末研磨后的细粉，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Acquired by grinding Origocrust Powder. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，晶体外壳二级加工品的质地更加均匀。
decoDesc.en: Origocrust can be shredded to yield a processed product with improved homogeneity.

desc.cn: 晶体外壳的粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Powdered form of Origocrust. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 源石晶体外壳的厚度通常可以作为判断一条矿脉存续时间的重要依据。
decoDesc.en: The thickness of the crystalline crust encasing an Originium formation (referred to as Origocrust) is often used to determine the age of the Originium vein.

desc.cn: 源石加工时剥离的外壳部分，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Crystalline crust acquired by delamination of Originium. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

desc.cn: 获取后可领取日常奖励。
desc.en: Earn enough of this to receive daily rewards.

decoDesc.cn:
1619年源石隘口源石粒子浓度：0.0321
1620年源石隘口源石粒子浓度：0.0322
经检测，隘口周边源石仍保持异常增殖状态。
decoDesc.en:
Originium Gorge Particulate Originium density last year: 0.0321 
Originium Gorge Particulate Originium density this year: 0.0322 
Further testing shows that Originium formations near the gorge are still growing at an anomalous rate.

decoDesc.cn:
真是奇妙，世界上绝大部分源石，在稳定状态下应该不会有任何扩散性表现。可源石隘口，这附近的源石居然能在常态下缓慢生长。
是什么影响了它？
我们设置了探测营地，在周边矿点进行定位，所有结果都指向源石隘口内部。只可惜其内部源石丛生，我们不可能进入其中仔细勘探。
或许我们可以从勘探设备下手，升级后或许会有办法。
decoDesc.en:
This is really odd. Originium formations are usually stable and would neither metastasize nor grow. But the Originium near the Originium Gorge exhibited signs of slow and steady growth despite normal ambient conditions. 
I don't know what's affecting it. 
We've established a surveillance camp and triangulated the source via our nearby mining sites. All readings point to something within the Originium Gorge. But the Originium formations inside the place are just too thick. It was impossible for us to head in for detailed surveillance. 
Perhaps we can use our prospecting machines. Upgrading them might give us a solution.

decoDesc.cn: 侵蚀爆发了，设备不重要，我至少要把实验数据带走。
decoDesc.en: The Blight just ruptured. I don't care about the machines, but I must get the research data out of this place.

decoDesc.cn: 由衍质源石加工来的特殊产物，因其瑰丽的外观和广泛的用途而倍受欢迎。
decoDesc.en: A special product of cut Origeometry. These stones are extremely popular due to their beauty and wide range of uses.

desc.cn: 合成物质，常用于招募干员。
desc.en: An artificial material often used for recruiting operators.

decoDesc.cn: 极度“豪横”的盆装菜式，能明显看出其中的肉远不止一种。请大快朵颐吧，在种种恶劣条件下能烹饪出正常的菜肴实属难得。
decoDesc.en: A basin full of "criminally generous riches". It is obvious that this is prepared with more than one type of meat. Help yourself to a bowl or two. Such normal-looking food is a rarity, considering it was made in a hostile environment.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员终结技能量的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's Ultimate Energy.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 依据《环带公约》的相关条款，缔约各方应在保证折金票在民生经济中正常流通的同时，针对此类调度券的约定发行量进行充足的物资储备，以实现特殊情况下有序有效的调度合作。
decoDesc.en: Pursuant to relevant provisions of the Band Accord, all Accordatories shall, while ensuring the unimpeded circulation of Talosian Credit Notes in the civilian economy, maintain commodity stockpiles to cover the issuance of such stock bills, thereby facilitating orderly and effective joint stockpile redistribution under exceptional circumstances.

desc.cn: 对武陵发行调度券，仅限此地使用，有各种丰富的用途。
desc.en: Stock bills issued in Wuling and only usable in the said region. They have all sorts of uses.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 武陵地区发展的留痕，是每一位奉献者辛劳工作的证明。
decoDesc.en: The mark of regional development in Wuling. The proof of the hard work and sacrifices made by every contributor.

desc.cn: 通过武陵地区的各类建设活动增加的建设值，可提升地区建设等级以获得大量奖励。
desc.en: Construction and development work in Wuling will raise this development metric. This can raise the Regional Development Level to provide a generous reward.

decoDesc.cn: 依据《环带公约》的相关条款，缔约各方应在保证折金票在民生经济中正常流通的同时，针对此类调度券的约定发行量进行充足的物资储备，以实现特殊情况下有序有效的调度合作。
decoDesc.en: Pursuant to relevant provisions of the Band Accord, all signatories shall, in addition to simultaneously guaranteeing that Talosian Credit Notes provide a currency circulation sufficient for the civil economy, guarantee a commodity stockpile sufficient for the agreed-upon supply of such types of allocation orders so as to achieve an orderly and effective joint allocation during extraordinary circumstances.

desc.cn: 对四号谷地发行调度券，仅限此地使用，有各种丰富的用途。
desc.en: Stock bills issued in Valley IV and only usable in the said region. They have all sorts of uses.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 四号谷地地区发展的留痕，是每一位奉献者辛劳工作的证明。
decoDesc.en: The mark of regional development in Valley IV. The proof of the hard work and sacrifices made by every contributor.

desc.cn: 通过四号谷地的各类建设活动增加的建设值，可提升地区建设等级以获得大量奖励。
desc.en: Construction and development work in Valley IV will raise this development metric. This can raise the Regional Development Level to provide a generous reward.

decoDesc.cn:
据传，武陵城的小学生们能精准尝出哪些冻梨是通过源石技艺手工制造，而哪些则是冷库产品。
不要欺骗小孩子哦。
decoDesc.en:
Rumors say that Wuling City grade schoolers can tell actual frozen fruits from those processed and made with Originium Arts. 
Do not lie to the children.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 岳研香茶铺中销量较低的产品，顾客普遍反馈它有一种酸涩口感。但不知为何，从某天开始，人们开始相信它能减弱靠近侵蚀后产生的不适感。
decoDesc.en: This Eureka Teashop product has been hampered by poor sales. Most consumers criticized it for its strangely sour and bitter taste. But one day came when people started believing it has the abilities to alleviate the discomfort caused by being too close to the Blight.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: “冬为眠虫夏成笋”——出自《四时竹林虫考略》。
decoDesc.en: "A hibernating nymph in winter, a budding sprout by summer." — Sishi Zhulinchong Kaolue (literally translated as: A Study of Grovenymphs in Different Seasons)

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 在武陵广受好评的录像带。参考了《六桩案》的形式，用六个带有悬疑感的武侠故事勾勒出了武陵发展历史。访客们公认它是最方便了解武陵的资料。这套录像带普及程度本较高，最近不知为何又出现了销量暴涨的状况。
decoDesc.en: Video tapes of top rated movies in Wuling. This anthology of six Wuxia thrillers (with a narrative structure inspired by that used in The Six Cases) illustrates the founding and history of Wuling. In fact, this anthology is publicly acclaimed as the easiest way to learn about Wuling City. Though one can readily find this anthology in many households, recent sales have spiked for reasons unknown.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 这套厨具与锚点的唯一关联，大概就是厨具的原材料是由锚点创造出的。第一次天使战争期间，缺少金属的人们在杀死富金属环境下生成的天使后，尝试用它们的残骸制作厨具。其中的锅具表面光滑平整，没有任何的砂眼，并且具备优异的导热性与出色的不粘效果，于是这项工艺便流传至今。
decoDesc.en: This set of kitchen utensils is only related to Ankhors because they were made using raw materials derived from Ankhors. During the First Aggeloi War, people who lack metal would kill Aggeloi that spawned in metal-rich environments, then use their remains to make kitchenware. Ankhorilling pots and pans feature smooth, non-stick surfaces, zero pits, and great thermal conductance. These excellent properties ensure that Ankhor-based kitchenware crafting gets passed on till this very day.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 形似幼苗的源石簇。在源石大树炸毁后，工团培植了大量具备长成源石大树可能的幼苗。虽然这种幼苗极难长大，但仍受到了各地源石研究者们的喜爱。
decoDesc.en: An Originium formation that looks like a young sapling. After the destruction of the Great Originium Oak, the UWST began farming these saplings on a large scale. Each of them has a chance of growing into a new Oak. Though hardly any saplings showed any sign of growth, they remain highly sought after by Originium scientists from across the world.

desc.cn: 当地人文物产相关的货组，价值变动幅度极大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with cultural commodities. Such goods are subject to massive price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 四号谷地矿工们常用的矿镐，装备了特制警报器。当镐尖因岩石中不易察觉的侵蚀受损时，它会发出尖锐的警报声。
decoDesc.en: Pickaxes commonly used by miners working in Valley IV. They are fitted with special alarms that give off sharp warning sounds if the pickaxe sustains damage due to undetectable Blight in rock formations.

desc.cn: 当地人文物产相关的货组，价值变动幅度极大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with cultural commodities. Such goods are subject to massive price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: “坚硬脑袋，为您的脑袋保驾护航。”
decoDesc.en: "Hard Noggin. Guaranteed to keep your head in one piece."

desc.cn: 当地人文物产相关的货组，价值变动幅度极大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with cultural commodities. Such goods are subject to massive price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 被雕刻成特定形状的鼷兽骨骼。四号谷地的开拓时期，支援开拓的萨卡兹工人们在离开时，将鼷兽骨骼雕刻成各种设施的形状，赠予留守谷地的工友们。骨雕上的巫术让它可以在源石电池的上方悬浮一段时间。这种工艺品也逐渐遍布文明环带的主要城市与开拓区。
decoDesc.en: An ornamental dangle made using musbeast bones carved into various shapes. During early development of Valley IV, Sarkaz workers were employed to support various projects. Before concluding their contracts, the Sarkaz would present fellow Valley IV crew mates with musbeast scrimshaw dangles carved into the shapes of various machines. Witchcraft within the dangles also lets them float temporarily above Originium batteries. The dangles gradually became a common piece of decor in major cities and frontier areas of the Civilization Band.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 联盟工团联合塞什卡研发，使用附带巫术的晶体外壳制造而成的原始设备，广泛安装在各个源石工厂的传送带上。能有效穿破晶体外壳，且不损伤矿核。
decoDesc.en: A rather primitive machine jointly developed by the UWST and Seš'qa. These drills are often made using Origocrust imbued with witchcraft and commonly installed on the transport belts of various Originium factories. They can penetrate Origocrusts effectively without damaging the mineral kernel.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 自第一次天使战争结束以来，这些罐头已经储存了一百余年。请勿开启食用，它能带来的心灵激励远超于口腹满足。
decoDesc.en: These tinned provisions date all the way back to the end of the First Aggeloi War, which means they have been around for more than a century. Please do not open or consume its contents. They are meant to provide spiritual encouragement far more satisfying than a filled belly.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度适中，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to moderate price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn:
研发灵感得自源石种植实验的水培肉，产于四号谷地周边的自动化肉联厂。
虽然如同泡水面包一样的口感与味道会伤害你的味蕾，但看在它能在桌面上缓缓蠕动的份上，还请谅解。
decoDesc.en:
Scientifically inspired by the myosin hydrocultures of Originium agricultural research. These fillets are grown in the meat-packing plants in the regions around Valley IV. 
Please overlook the fact that the flavor, texture, and gastronomic trauma of hydroculture fillets are akin to those inflicted by soggy bread. These fillets are at least capable of peristaltic locomotion that lets them slowly squirm across a table.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度较大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to large price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 囤积于谷地要塞的矿石病预防口服液。在塔卫二，每日坚持饮用预防口服液可以有效降低感染矿石病的风险。
decoDesc.en: A stash of orally administered syrups for Oripathy prophylaxis. In Talos-II, a daily regimen of the prophylactic syrup can effectively reduce the risks of contracting Oripathy.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度较大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to large price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 塞什卡产出的玩具。游玩者需预告自己即将投出的结果，假若失误，髀石上的巫术就会让玩家头顶“长”出一朵有三十分钟寿命的小花。
decoDesc.en: A toy made in Seš'qa. The player starts by calling out the result of a throw. If they miss, the witchcraft of the knucklebones will cause a flower to sprout on the head of the player. The flower lasts for 30 minutes.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度较大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to large price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 曾袭击四号谷地的巨大天使残骸中发现的晶块，大部分被运输到各地进行材料学实验。由于其外观瑰丽且存量较大，因此也会被工人们加工成胸针、项链等首饰。
decoDesc.en: Blocks of crystals found within the remains of the giant Aggelos that once attacked Valley IV. Most were moved to various institutions for research and testing. However, given the beauteous appearances and ample supply of the crystals, many were fashioned into brooches, necklaces, and other jewelry by the workers.

desc.cn: 当地日用消耗相关的货组，价值变动幅度较大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with daily commodities. Such goods are subject to large price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 由石块、金属及木材构成的积木套组。工人们在拆解天使，回收资源后的休息时间里，会用手旁的边角料拼出各种结构，久而久之，这种行为催生出了一个玩具系列。
decoDesc.en: A set of building blocks made using scrap stone, metal, and wood. Many workers spent their break time (when they're not dismantling the Aggeloi or recycling various resources) building various things with all sorts of easy-to-find scraps. Someone eventually took this concept and created a franchise of toys out of it.

desc.cn: 当地人文物产相关的货组，价值变动幅度极大，可通过物资调度买卖赚取收益。
desc.en: A package loaded with cultural commodities. Such goods are subject to massive price fluctuations. They can also be used in Stock Redistribution to generate revenue.

decoDesc.cn: 偶尔能在肖像天使光环周围采集到的奇异岩石，拥有极好的导热性能。以之为原料制成的散热片在市场上广受欢迎。
decoDesc.en: Strange minerals can sometimes be gathered around an Effigy's halo. The stones exhibit excellent thermal conductance. Heat sinks made out of them are quite popular on the market.

desc.cn: 击败肖像天使的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Effigies. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 偶尔能在天使“鞘翅”部位采集到的异香石，味道较之其他异香石有些许不同。绝大部分人难以描述它的味道，“或许是天空的味道”——他们大多会得出这样的结论。
decoDesc.en: Aggagrit that can be occasionally harvested from Aggeloid "elytrons". Its flavor differs from other types of Aggagrit and many find it incredibly difficult to describe. Most would eventually arrive at this conclusion: "Maybe this is the taste of the sky."

desc.cn: 击败仿生翅天使的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Falsewings. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 偶尔能在天使“撞角”部位采集到的奇异岩石，拥有奇妙香气，用作腌料可以赋予食材极其独特的风味。
decoDesc.en: Strange minerals can sometimes be gathered from the Aggeloi's "ramming horns". They can be used as a food marinade to give it special flavors.

desc.cn: 击败大角天使、刚角天使的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from Rams or Heavy Rams. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 偶尔能在天使“聚能刺”部位采集到的奇异岩石，拥有奇妙香气，可被视作某种咸度适中、能够增香提鲜的调料盐。
decoDesc.en: Strange minerals can sometimes be gathered from the Aggeloi's "energy-focusing tail stingers". They can be used as a food marinate to give it special flavors.

desc.cn: 击败钉刺天使、重刺天使的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from Stings or Heavy Stings. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 偶尔能在天使“盾甲”部位切割下的特殊合金。这是与天师们所发现的与赫铜近似的金属，密度极高。
decoDesc.en: A unique alloy that can be acquired by cutting out Aggeloid "shield armor". The Tianshi have realized that the metal is extremely dense and has properties similar to Hetonite.

desc.cn: 击败跂步晶城的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Walking Chrysopolises. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 新鲜的兽肉，足够新鲜。
decoDesc.en: A piece of fillet. It seems pretty fresh.

desc.cn: 击败野生牙兽、碾骨撕裂牙兽的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Wild Tuskbeasts or Bonekrusher Ripptusks. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 总部传输装备设计资料，解析晶块补全应用环境数据，终末地工业的各类装备就诞生在这两个环节完美衔接后。
decoDesc.en: The HQ provides gear design drawings while decryption crystals offer the necessary environmental readings. Combine these 2 to properly assemble a proper piece of Endfield gear.

desc.cn: 记录了各类战斗数据的特殊晶块，通常在击败敌人后获得，击败等级越高的敌人，获得数量越多，可用于装备制造。
desc.en: A special crystal for recording all sorts of combat data usually dropped by defeated enemies (higher level enemies will drop more). These crystals can be used for gear assembly.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 因长时间接触雾火而出现明显异常的腌肉干粮，不建议将之视作食物，但似乎可以作为柴薪使用。
decoDesc.en: Dried, marinated jerky that looks obviously abnormal due to prolonged exposure to hazefyre. Eating this is NOT advised. However, you may consider using it as backup firewood.

desc.cn: 击败雾火牙兽、雾火爪牙的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Hazefyre Tuskbeasts and Hazefyre Claws. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 碾骨清道夫的装备所使用的特殊备用燃料，似乎是某种混杂了染色剂的动物油脂。在生产与掠夺的情况都不甚乐观时，裂地者们偶尔也会“就地取材”。
decoDesc.en: A special backup fuel usually equipped and used by Bonekrusher Arsonists. It seems to be beast fat mixed with a certain dye. During periods of slim production and/or raiding, Landbreakers would occasionally acquire lipids from "local sources".

desc.cn: 击败碾骨清道夫的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Bonekrusher Arsonists. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 水灯虫的发光器。其中的液体可被当作食用染色剂使用。武陵城中有一种外观模仿天师桩的甜品就离不开它的点缀。
decoDesc.en: The glowing organ of the waterlamp. The fluids within it can be used as an edible dye. Essential for the final garnish for the famous Wuling dessert resembling the Tianshi Pillar.

desc.cn: 击败水灯虫的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Waterlamps. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 柔嫩的肝脏。球刺兽全身上下的肉都有微弱毒性，唯有肝脏是例外。
decoDesc.en: A tender piece of liver. Almost every tissue of the quillbeast is mildly toxic. Its liver is the only exception.

desc.cn: 击败球刺兽的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Quillbeasts. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 刚刚采摘下来的新笋，鲜嫩可口，产自清波寨，是远近闻名的优秀食材。
decoDesc.en: Freshly harvested young bamboo sprouts from Qingbo Stockade. Tender, refreshing, and delicious. This quality food ingredient is famed throughout Talos-II.

desc.cn: 击败莫留财、穿林箭的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Road Plunderers or Grove Archers. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 彪兽前爪周边的细腻绒毛。这些“流光溢彩”的绒毛是被彪兽清理最勤的部分，但你仍能在间隙中看到几缕猎物的血色。
decoDesc.en: Fine, fluffy fur collected from near the frontal paws of the rakerbeast. A rakerbeast would spend a lot of time grooming the "iridescent" part of its fur. You can even see threads of residual blood of unfortunate prey within the gaps.

desc.cn: 击败百眼彪兽的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Spotted Rakerbeast. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 在雾火中“浸泡”多年的极重大弩，从安全角度考虑，已不建议作为武器使用。但裂地者设计的狂野武器偶尔会受到一些收藏爱好者们欢迎。
decoDesc.en: A super heavy crossbow "soaked" in hazefyre for many years. Given safety considerations, using this as a weapon is NOT advised. However, wildly unconventional weapons designed by Landbreakers are highly sought after by various collectors.

desc.cn: 击败碾骨射手的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Bonekrusher Ballistas. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 掺杂了数片草籽外壳的罐装干粉，存在一定毒性。这似乎是裂地者的“冲泡类能量饮料”，但也无法排除他们将之作为调料的可能性。
decoDesc.en: A can of dried powder with bits of seed chaffs and coats. The powder is slightly toxic and the Landbreakers seem to consume it like an "instant energy drink mix". However, there is no discounting the possibility that the powder might be used as seasoning.

desc.cn: 击败碾骨劫掠者、碾骨射手、碾骨渗透者的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Bonekrusher Raiders, Bonekrusher Ballistas, or Bonekrusher Infiltrators. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 碾骨破城者装备的实验型拳甲，本是一种小型攻城兵器。裂地者显然不会在意“用户体验”，此种拳甲会牢牢嵌入使用者的血肉，给他们带来极大的痛苦。
decoDesc.en: A pair of experimental gauntlets equipped by Bonekrusher Siegeknuckles, crafted from miniature siege weapons. The Landbreakers obviously care little about user experience. These gauntlets would dig deep into their wearers' flesh and give them an incredible amount of pain.

desc.cn: 击败碾骨破城者的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Bonekrusher Siegeknuckles. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 被碾碎的野兽软骨，是碾骨焰术师投入巢雕中的“燃料”。实际上雾火并非因此而燃烧，这似乎仅是碾骨焰术师某种希求胜利的自我暗示。
decoDesc.en: Crushed beast cartilage. Bonekrusher Pyromancers would usually use this as "fuel" for their denstacks. However, hazefyre is not produced by burning cartilage. Rather, the pyromancers burn the beasts' remains as a means of convincing themselves of their victory at hand.

desc.cn: 击败碾骨焰术师的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Bonekrusher Pyromancers. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 极劣质的麦粉，不知具体成分，整体呈现出一种诡异的灰色。似乎裂地者有向其中掺杂某种蘑菇粉末，这让这袋麦粉闻起来有发霉的味道。
decoDesc.en: Extremely poor quality flour of unknown ingredients. Overall color is a strange, grayish hue. The Landbreakers seem to have added some dried fungal powder to this mix as the sack of flour exudes a moldy smell.

desc.cn: 击败碾骨先锋的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Bonekrusher Vanguards. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 干涸血渍证明了它的过去，这份恐怖和狂热现在属于你了。
decoDesc.en: The dried bloodstains serve as a proof of its past. The terror and zealotry it once personified are now yours.

desc.cn: 击败碾骨行刑人的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Bonekrusher Executioners. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 虬兽头部用来感知环境的“须”。在春夏相交的时节，虬兽的须会自然脱落，这些看起来像是树根的东西虽然没有什么营养价值，但好在口感绝佳。
decoDesc.en: Nidwyrms have "whiskers" growing on their heads. These appendages appear like tree roots and serve as sensory organs. These whiskers are naturally shed when spring gives way to summer. Although they offer limited nutritional value, they have an incredible texture.

desc.cn: 击败潜地虬兽的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Tunneling Nidwyrms. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 斧甲兽的巨角，于激烈的战斗中折断。战士仅会在战死时放下武器，斧甲兽亦然。
decoDesc.en: The massive horn of the Axe Armorbeast broken during intense battle. Warriors would only drop their weapons when slain. The same applies to Axe Armorbeasts.

desc.cn: 击败斧甲兽的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Axe Armorbeasts. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 含有丰富蛋白质的肉，但在食用前需谨慎处理，避免活性源石粉尘进入体内。
decoDesc.en: This meat is rich in protein but must be meticulously prepared to remove all active Originium dust and particles from the tissues.

desc.cn: 击败源生钳兽、酸液源石虫、火雾源石虫的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Pincerbeasts, Acid Originium Slugs, and Firemist Originium Slugs. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 哪怕闻的时间稍长些都能让人头晕片刻的奇妙液体。曾有好事者将之赠予品鉴师，为它搏来了“味同八十年陈酿”的美誉，但我们都清楚，天使的形成时间只有那短短片刻。
decoDesc.en: A strange liquid capable of inducing temporary tipsiness to those who sniffed it more than once. The fluid won the accolade of "smelling like a fine, eighty-year-old vintage" when some busybody gifted it to a kohlic beverage specialist. However, everyone knows that Aggelos formation is a process far, far shorter than that.

desc.cn: 击败破潮之像的掉落物，可用于仓储节点装箱运送。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Tidalklasts. Can be used at a depot node for Pack and Deliver.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 品尝起来极甜、极腻的黑色液体。自其内部检测出来的主要成分姑且可以被称为“糖精”。
decoDesc.en: A black liquid with an incredibly sweet and cloying taste. The primary contents identified through analyses are currently referred to as "artificial sweeteners".

desc.cn: 击败潮行天使的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Tidewalkers. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 奇怪的水。明明成分仅有水，触摸起来却有着古怪的胶质感，或许是天使形成过程中的什么，让它产生了如此奇妙的变化。
decoDesc.en: A strange form of water. Although wholly composed of dihydrogen monoxide, it felt strangely gel-like to the touch. Perhaps the process of Aggeloid formation has induced strange changes to the properties of this material.

desc.cn: 击败浊流天使的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Mudflows. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 口感奇妙的天然气泡水，冰冰凉凉，饮下能让人精神一振。
decoDesc.en: This natural sparkling water has a strange fizz. It is cool, refreshing, and reinvigorating when consumed.

desc.cn: 击败晶锥天使、棱镜天使的掉落物，可用于精制食药制作。
desc.en: Gatherable from defeated Hedrons or Prisms. Can be used to make fine food and medicine (Fine F&M).

noObtainWayHint.cn: 冒险探索中击败敌人获取

decoDesc.cn: 临时：极其珍贵的货物，似乎是某种神秘药剂，泛着绿色荧光
decoDesc.en: TEMP: Super valuable cargo. Seems to contain some unknown medication emitting a green glow.

decoDesc.cn: 从艾莱扎·柯林斯处获得的权限卡，可在源石实验园区发挥作用。
decoDesc.en: An access card from Aleeza Collins. It might be useful in the Originium Science Park.

desc.cn: 可用于开启源石实验园区大门的权限卡。
desc.en: An access card for opening the gate of the Originium Science Park.

decoDesc.cn: 与“烙铁指令”的专用发信器成套的权限钥匙卡，上面粘上了不知何人的鲜血。
decoDesc.en: An authorization keycard paired with the special signal emitter for the Utjug Order. It has been stained with someone's blood.

desc.cn: 克劳所需的权限钥匙卡，用来启动发送”烙铁指令“专用的发信器。
desc.en: Crowe needs this authorization keycard to activate the special signal emitter and send out the Utjug Order.

decoDesc.cn: 一个外形平平无奇的发信装置，但鲜红色的按钮似乎在警示着危险。
decoDesc.en: An ordinary looking signal emitter, but it sports a bright red button that hints at great danger.

desc.cn: 克劳所需的特殊发信器，用来发送“烙铁指令”。
desc.en: Crowe needs this special signal emitter to send out the Utjug Order.

decoDesc.cn: 适用于武陵环境情况的冶金助剂。武陵潮湿的环境会对装备精锻产生细微的影响，根据这种细节而调整的助剂配方，正是武库产品质量过硬的证明。
decoDesc.en: A metallurgical catalyst designed for the ambient conditions of Wuling. The catalyst's formula has been adjusted to fit humid environments of Wuling as they exert minute influences on the artificing process. This further proves that the Arsenal release products of the most reliable quality.

desc.cn: 在装备精锻中使用，可对武陵的装备进行一次装备精锻。
desc.en: A gear artificing material. Use it to perform artificing on a piece of Wuling gear.

decoDesc.cn: 该原件全称为生物式核心适应型一次性协议铸造原件，主体材料为紫晶。
decoDesc.en: The full name of this component is Biocore-Adaptive Single-Use Protocol Mould. Amethyst is the main material used for producing this.

desc.cn: 通过多种材料加工获得的装备原件，可用于装备制造。
desc.en: A gear component made using various materials. Can be used for gear assembly.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 该原件全称为生物式核心适应型一次性协议铸造原件，主体材料为蓝铁，相较低级版本提高了脱模便利性。
decoDesc.en: The full name of this component is Biocore-Adaptive Single-Use Protocol Mould. This mould is mainly made with ferrium for better ejection than the common variant.

desc.cn: 通过多种材料加工获得的装备原件，可用于装备制造。
desc.en: A gear component made using various materials. Can be used for gear assembly.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 该原件全称为生物式核心适应型一次性协议铸造原件，主体材料为高晶，操作起来更加便利。
decoDesc.en: The full name of this component is Biocore-Adaptive Single-Use Protocol Mould. This mould is mainly made with cryston for easier use.

desc.cn: 通过多种材料加工获得的装备原件，可用于装备制造。
desc.en: A gear component made using various materials. Can be used for gear assembly.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 该原件全称为生物式核心适应型一次性高透明息壤铸造原件，主体材料为密制晶体及息壤。相较寻常版本，拥有更优良的信息传导性能。
decoDesc.en: The full name of this component is a Biocore-Adaptive Single-Use Highly Transparent Xiranite Mould. The main materials for constructing this are Packed Origocrust and Xiranite. This mould offers better data transduction when compared to the standard variant.

desc.cn: 通过多种材料加工获得的装备原件，可用于装备制造。
desc.en: A gear component made using various materials. Can be used for gear assembly.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的初级护甲。
它在心理上给人的鼓励远大于它的实际防御性能。
decoDesc.en:
Basic armor with simple structures. 
Gives people a peace of mind that far exceeds its actual defensive capabilities.

desc.cn: 本装备为临时制品，未通过终末地工业产品检验流程验证，防御能力有限。
desc.en: Provisionally made and failed the final product verification and validation (V&V) process of Endfield Industries. This equipment offers only limited defense.

decoDesc.cn:
多用于矿场作业的防护装备。
《四号谷地安全防护标准》要求劳动保护装备至少需要软性保护及硬性保护两层防护结构。
decoDesc.en:
Protective equipment for mining operations. 
Valley IV Safety and Protection Standards dictate that minimum requirements for work protection must comprise a 2-layered protection of (i) a soft, cushioning layer and (ii) hard, rigid protection.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 临时制成的装备。虽然足够重，但防护能力有限。
decoDesc.en: Though heavy enough, this improvised equipment only offers limited protection.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 临时制成的装备，较之标准型有所微调。虽然足够重，但防护能力有限。
decoDesc.en: Furnished with minor adjustments compared to the standard model. Though heavy enough, this improvised equipment only offers limited protection.

desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化重型防护装备。
在加重加厚了所装配的护甲片后，这些重甲多半时间会被送去集成高威力铳械。
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers heavy protection. 
After attaching thicker and heavier armor plates onto the suit, the armor would likely end up at places where it becomes the target of powerful guns.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化重型防护装备。
如果想要提升防御性能，就无法控制住激增的重量，算是这套装备最严重的痛点。
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers heavy protection. 
Raising defense performance also leads to massive increases in weight, which also happens to be the biggest issue with this equipment.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化重型防护装备。
虽然成本十分之低，但胜在材料品质优秀，因此防护性能足够令人满意。
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers heavy protection. 
Though extremely cheap to manufacture, it offers an acceptable degree of protection thanks to the quality materials used.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化重型防护装备。
仅用两个小巧的支撑结构就帮助穿戴者分担了百分之四十的武器重量，真是巧妙的设计。
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers heavy protection. 
Just two intricate supporting structures are used to help bear 40% of weaponry weight. This is smart design.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化轻型防护装备。
它诞生在集成工业系统相关设备的试运行过程中，因几个尝试混合生产线的随手为之而生。
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers light protection. 
It was a byproduct created during a test run of several mixed production lines involving various AIC Factory facilities.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化轻型防护装备。
护甲片能够灵活装配是这套集成化装备的最大卖点。
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers light protection. 
The biggest feature of this AIC gear is that it allows armor plates to be flexibly attached to the suit.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化轻型防护装备。
“虽然我愿意相信咱们的技术，但它是不是有些太轻了……”
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers light protection. 
"I'd love to believe in our technology, but this feels a little too light..."

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
结构简单的模块化轻型防护装备。
虽然不能提供最顶级的防护，但它至少便于穿戴。
decoDesc.en:
Structurally simple and modular equipment that offers light protection. 
Although they do not offer the best defenses, at least they are easy to wear.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
多用于矿场作业的防护装备。
《四号谷地安全防护标准》要求劳动保护装备至少需要软性保护及硬性保护两层防护结构。
decoDesc.en:
Protective equipment for mining operations. 
Valley IV Safety and Protection Standards dictate that minimum requirements for work protection must comprise a 2-layered protection of (i) a soft, cushioning layer and (ii) hard, rigid protection.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
信使们爱穿的夹克。
四号谷地周边的信使会为自己的交通工具喷涂大树枝干般的纹样。曾保护这片土地的事物至今仍能给予人们力量。
decoDesc.en:
A jacket that any messenger would love to wear. 
Messengers working in and near the Valley IV region will often give their vehicles paintjobs with tree-like patterns. They hope the sight of these majestic plants that once protected this land can bring people strength.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
小巧的解压玩具。
根据权威统计，约有百分之二十的信使会把这样的解压玩具改装为定向追踪器。
decoDesc.en:
An intricate fidget toy. 
Results from a trustworthy poll revealed that about 20% of messengers have modified this stress-relief toy into a self-orienting tracker.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
坚固的照明手电。
它尾部的尖锥偶尔会被用来破开一些尘封的古物。
decoDesc.en:
A sturdy hand-held electric lamp. 
The sharp spike on the other end can also be used to break open old boxes or containers.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
信使们爱用的护手。
走上擂台切磋几手也是信使们的消遣方式之一。
decoDesc.en:
A pair of gloves that messengers love to use. 
Messengers would also pass their time by fighting in the arena.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
信使们爱穿的夹克。
在塔卫二，越野摩托是一种足够物美价廉的交通工具——信使们会为它附上不同的改装模块。
decoDesc.en:
A jacket that any messenger would love to wear. 
Scramblers are cheap and effective modes of transport on Talos-II. Messengers would often outfit these bikes with different mods and modules.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
小巧的解压玩具。
根据权威统计，约有百分之八十的信使会把这样的小玩具改装成微型爆破飞镖。
decoDesc.en:
An intricate fidget toy. 
Results from a trustworthy poll revealed that about 80% of messengers would modify this toy into a miniature dart grenade.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
坚固的照明手电。
它尾部的尖锥通常会被用来凿开一些不愿沟通的骨骼。
decoDesc.en:
A sturdy hand-held electric lamp. 
The sharp spike on the other end can also be used to break the bones of those who refuse to talk.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
信使们爱用的护手。
大部分信使会为自己的交通工具增加一个便捷脱离装置，以便能在突发的侵蚀灾害中保全性命。
decoDesc.en:
A pair of gloves that any messenger would love to wear. 
Most messengers would install easy-to-use lifesaving ejection systems on their vehicles to contend with unexpected Blight ruptures.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
牢固的防护背心。
“在抢修现场必须穿好防护装备，不然你就会看到受损设备向你大声呼救……别给医生添麻烦，好吗？”
decoDesc.en:
A sturdy, protective vest. 
"PPE must be properly worn in emergency repair sites. Failure to do so might make you see damaged facilities and machinery calling out to you for help... Just stop giving our surgeons extra work, okay?"

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
线条流畅的扳手。
“用来当武器意外顺手！”——某位不愿透露姓名的工人。
decoDesc.en:
An elegantly designed wrench with smooth outlines. 
"Pretty handy for bonking heads!" — A worker who wished to remain anonymous

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
重量略大的电池。
经验丰富的工人可以在十分钟内将这种源石电池改装成榴弹。
decoDesc.en:
These batteries are pretty heavy. 
An experienced worker can transform this Originium battery into an improvised grenade within 10 minutes.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
格外牢固的手套。
目前人类还未研发出能够有效耐受侵蚀的防护服，现役防护装备绝大多数仅能应对侵蚀次生灾害。
decoDesc.en:
A pair of very sturdy gloves. 
We have yet to develop PPE suits with true Blight resistance. Most PPE and protective solutions in service could only cope with secondary disasters of Blight events.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
特殊环境作业时必备的防护装备。
严重的侵蚀灾害往往会带来有悖常理的电路故障，抢修者亦需小心。
decoDesc.en:
A piece of equipment essential for special environment operations. 
Severe Blight events often cause anomalous electrical and circuitry failures. Workers assigned to repair work must watch out for them.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
施加了特殊防护镀层的扳手。
必要时可以当作武器使用，用来敲碎某些天使的肢体也不在话下。
decoDesc.en:
A wrench with special protective coating. 
This can also be used as a weapon when necessary. It is fully capable of crushing and pulverizing Aggelos limbs.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
施加了特殊防护镀层的扳手。
必要时可以当作武器使用，用来敲碎某些天使的肢体也不在话下。
decoDesc.en:
A wrench with special protective coating. 
This can also be used as a weapon when necessary. It is fully capable of crushing and pulverizing Aggelos limbs.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
耐用程度极高的电池。
在塔卫二，侵蚀环境下的工程抢险作业极度危险。因此，即便是“如何使用电池”，也需按特殊标准严格培训。
decoDesc.en:
An extremely durable battery. 
In Talos-II, emergency repair work in Blighted conditions is an extremely dangerous job. Hence, workers must undergo strict training based on special standards before they are allowed to use batteries in such environments.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
特殊环境作业时必备的防护装备。
为了避免被异常爆发的电流击伤，在侵蚀灾害现场抢修电路的工程师们必须穿上特制防护服。
decoDesc.en:
A piece of equipment essential for special environment operations. 
All engineers making electrical repairs at Blight rupture sites must wear specialized PPE to avoid injuries caused by anomalous bursts of electrical discharge.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
多用于矿场作业的防护装备。
《四号谷地安全防护标准》要求劳动保护装备至少需要软性保护及硬性保护两层防护结构。
decoDesc.en:
Protective equipment for mining operations. 
Valley IV Safety and Protection Standards dictate that minimum requirements for work protection must comprise a 2-layered protection of (i) a soft, cushioning layer and (ii) hard, rigid protection.

decoDesc.cn:
针对阿伯莉采石场作业情况做出了调整的新型防护装甲。
挖掘前文明遗物的过程中，遭遇的情况通常是多变的、突发的。因此作业中使用的装备必须兼顾防御性、灵活性，以及足够强的攻击能力。
decoDesc.en:
A suit of novel protective armor modified for the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry. 
Excavation of Precursor relics can be a rather convoluted process filled with unexpected changes. Equipment used during excavation must offer sufficient protection, dexterity, as well as offensive capabilities.

阿伯莉重甲系列的作战用型，较之标准型多出了武器连接功能，能够有效适配喷火器、榴弹发射器等装备。
decoDesc.en:
A suit of novel protective armor modified for the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry. 
A combat model of the Aburrey Heavy Armor. When compared to the standard model, this suit features additional weapon connection ports highly compatible with flamethrowers, grenade launchers, and other ordnance.

decoDesc.en:
A suit of novel protective armor modified for the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry.

为了适应阿伯莉采石场突如其来的挖掘作业，工程师们连夜对这套护甲设计做出了调整，为其增添了视觉保护、听觉保护等模块。
decoDesc.en:
Novel protective equipment modified to suit the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry. 
The engineers worked through the night to slap on mods when work at Aburrey Quarry suddenly involved excavation and digging. This armor now features eyesight and hearing protection.

在探索未知环境时，隔音性能足够强的听觉防护装备尤其重要。这款芯片能有效辅助装备者判断自身是否出现了幻听症状。
decoDesc.en:
A piece of novel protective equipment modified for the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry. 
When exploring the unknown, proper sound insulation and hearing protection are extremely important. This chip can effectively help the wearer determine if they are suffering from auditory hallucinations.

针对阿伯莉采石场作业情况做出了调整的新型防护装甲。
“它就那样嵌在岩石中，就像我只是挖出了混凝土里的一截钢筋，但……但我好像听到它在对我说话……”
decoDesc.en:
Novel protective equipment modified to suit the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry. 
"It was embedded in the rock, and I thought I just dug out some rebars in the concrete. But ... but I think I heard it talking to me..."

按照工程师的说法，这套防护装甲的未来迭代方向将聚焦于全面自动化——即使穿戴者失去意识，它也能够带人安全撤离。
decoDesc.en:
Novel protective equipment modified to suit the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry. 
According to the engineers, future iterations of this armor will focus on full automation. The aim is to evacuate the wearer to safety, even if the wearer has been incapacitated.

针对阿伯莉采石场作业情况做出了调整的新型防护装甲。
装配在连体防护装甲外的手部护具，指尖位置集成了六种类型、共计近百个微型传感器，能帮助装备者精确判断出自己究竟接触到了什么——哪怕他们失去了视觉。
decoDesc.en:
Novel protective equipment modified for the work environment of the Aburrey Quarry. 
Hand protection linked to the protective armor suit. The fingertips have been furnished with nearly 100 micro-sensors of 6 different types to help wearers accurately determine what they actually touched — even after losing their sight.

decoDesc.cn:
信使们爱穿的夹克。
在塔卫二，越野摩托是一种足够物美价廉的交通工具——信使们会为它附上不同的改装模块。
decoDesc.en:
A jacket that any messenger would love to wear. 
Scramblers are cheap and effective modes of transport on Talos-II. Messengers would often outfit these bikes with different mods and modules.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Endfield after referencing wildland handcrafting techniques, and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
小巧的解压玩具。
根据权威统计，约有百分之八十的信使会把这样的小玩具改装成微型爆破飞镖。
decoDesc.en:
An intricate fidget toy. 
Results from a trustworthy poll revealed that about 80% of messengers would modify this toy into a miniature dart grenade.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业参考荒野手工艺品设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。

decoDesc.cn:
坚固的照明手电。
它尾部的尖锥通常会被用来凿开一些不愿沟通的骨骼。
decoDesc.en:
A sturdy hand-held electric lamp. 
The sharp spike on the other end can also be used to break the bones of those who refuse to talk.

信使们爱用的护手。
大部分信使会为自己的交通工具增加一个便捷脱离装置，以便能在突发的侵蚀灾害中保全性命。
decoDesc.en:
A pair of gloves that any messenger would love to wear. 
Most messengers would install easy-to-use lifesaving ejection systems on their vehicles to contend with unexpected Blight ruptures.

源石研究园种植作业中会使用的外骨骼装备。
搭载了微电流刺激系统，能有效降低穿戴者的疲劳感——工人们对这种“振奋精神”的小设计尤为满意。
decoDesc.en:
Part of an exoskeleton suit equipped by crystal growers at the Originium Science Park. 
It is furnished with a micro-electrical stimulation system that effectively reduces the wearer's fatigue. The crew mates are exceptionally pleased with this "invigorating" mini design feature.

源石研究园种植作业中会使用的外骨骼装备。
虽然矿石病在塔卫二已能得到有效控制，但还请继续做好基础的呼吸防护。
decoDesc.en:
Part of an exoskeleton suit equipped by crystal growers at the Originium Science Park. 
Although Oripathy can be effectively controlled and treated in Talos-II, users are still advised to wear basic respiratory protection.
