decoDesc.cn:
源石研究园种植作业中会使用的外骨骼装备。
与天灾防护面罩配套的过滤装置，应用时即插即拔，方便快捷。
decoDesc.en:
Part of an exoskeleton suit equipped by crystal growers at the Originium Science Park. 
These filters are designed to work with the Catastrophe Mask, and can be easily plugged or unplugged.

desc.cn: 本装备由特里格拉夫军工厂设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Triglava Armoury and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
源石研究园种植作业中会使用的外骨骼装备。
重点调整了指关节部位的支撑结构，同时提高了抓握能力，能在源石晶簇切割搬运的过程中高效辅助作业。
decoDesc.en:
Part of an exoskeleton suit equipped by crystal growers at the Originium Science Park. 
Key adjustments include supporting structures at the finger joints and improved gripping strength. These gloves greatly improve work performance when cutting and carrying slabs of crystals from Originium clusters.

desc.cn: 本装备由特里格拉夫军工厂设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Triglava Armoury and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
牢固的防护背心。
“在抢修现场必须穿好防护装备，不然你就会看到受损设备向你大声呼救……别给医生添麻烦，好吗？”
decoDesc.en:
A sturdy, protective vest. 
"PPE must be properly worn in emergency repair sites. Failure to do so might make you see damaged facilities and machinery calling out to you for help... Just stop giving our surgeons extra work, okay?"

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
重量略大的电池。
经验丰富的工人可以在十分钟内将这种源石电池改装成榴弹。
decoDesc.en:
These batteries are pretty heavy. 
An experienced worker can transform this Originium battery into an improvised grenade within 10 minutes.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
线条流畅的扳手。
“用来当武器意外顺手！”——某位不愿透露姓名的工人。
decoDesc.en:
An elegantly designed wrench with smooth outlines. 
"Pretty handy for bonking heads!" — A worker who wished to remain anonymous

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
格外牢固的手套。
目前人类还未研发出能够有效耐受侵蚀的防护服，现役防护装备绝大多数仅能应对侵蚀次生灾害。
decoDesc.en:
A pair of very sturdy gloves. 
We have yet to develop PPE suits with true Blight resistance. Most PPE and protective solutions in service could only cope with secondary disasters of Blight events.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
特殊环境作业时必备的防护装备。
严重的侵蚀灾害往往会带来有悖常理的电路故障，抢修者亦需小心。
decoDesc.en:
A piece of equipment essential for special environment operations. 
Severe Blight events often cause anomalous electrical and circuitry failures. Workers assigned to repair work must watch out for them.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

A piece of equipment essential for special environment operations.

decoDesc.cn:
施加了特殊防护镀层的扳手。
必要时可以当作武器使用，用来敲碎某些天使的肢体也不在话下。
decoDesc.en:
A wrench with special protective coating. 
This can also be used as a weapon when necessary. It is fully capable of crushing and pulverizing Aggelos limbs.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
耐用程度极高的电池。
在塔卫二，侵蚀环境下的工程抢险作业极度危险。因此，即便是“如何使用电池”，也需按特殊标准严格培训。
decoDesc.en:
An extremely durable battery. 
In Talos-II, emergency repair work in Blighted conditions is an extremely dangerous job. Hence, workers must undergo strict training based on special standards before they are allowed to use batteries in such environments.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
特殊环境作业时必备的防护装备。
为了避免被异常爆发的电流击伤，在侵蚀灾害现场抢修电路的工程师们必须穿上特制防护服。
decoDesc.en:
A piece of equipment essential for special environment operations. 
All engineers making electrical repairs at Blight rupture sites must wear specialized PPE to avoid injuries caused by anomalous bursts of electrical discharge.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 象征着艰辛前路的装备。“事未竟，路犹长。”
decoDesc.en: This piece of gear is the byword for the difficult road ahead. "The quest is not yet finished, and so the journey is not yet complete."

decoDesc.en: The standard Frontiersmate oxygen tether guarantees at least 4 hours of heavy duty underwater operations thanks to its oxygen cycler technology. The upgraded version further extends this duration to 6 hours.

decoDesc.en: The goal of Frontiersmate equipment is to give a squad of 3 to 5 combatants the ability to directly engage and terminate smaller Aggeloid hosts.

decoDesc.cn:
应龙特勤队所配装备的民用版，缺少了关键力量，但具备了普适性。
鲜有人知，这套护甲的设计师实际上是一位仅差半步就能通过特勤队考核的预备队员。
decoDesc.en:
A civilian version of Yinglung Special Task Force equipment. The lack of a crucial power component actually improved its compatibility with general users. 
Very few people know that the armor designer is actually a reservist who almost passed the YSTF screening test. Almost.

decoDesc.cn:
应龙特勤队所配装备的民用版，缺少了关键力量，但具备了普适性。
优化设计完成那天，他提起笔，在设计图边留下几个字——“天坼地裂，我亦胜之”。
decoDesc.en:
A civilian version of Yinglung Special Task Force equipment. The lack of a crucial power component actually improved its compatibility with general users. 
When the optimizations were finally complete, he added a few words next to the blueprints: "Heavens and earth may break asunder, but I shall prevail and emerge the victor."

decoDesc.cn:
应龙特勤队所配装备的民用版，缺少了关键力量，但具备了普适性。
“曾和我一起训练的熟面孔，我看着他们担起重责，镇守重地，这让我觉得……我像个从惨烈战场上逃走的战败者，一个逃兵。”
decoDesc.en:
A civilian version of Yinglung Special Task Force equipment. The lack of a crucial power component actually improved its compatibility with general users. 
"When I saw familiar faces whom I once trained with carrying out crucial roles and protecting key locations, I felt ... like a defeated loser fleeing a terrible battlefield. I felt like a deserter."

设计灵感来自于碾骨氏族的装备。
厚重护甲不单单具有防护能力，在荒地行人眼中，它也代表着一种冷酷残忍的行事风格。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment with designs inspired by the Bonekrusher Clan. 
This heavy suit of armor not only provides decent protection, wildland roamers also regard it as a symbol for a brutal and merciless way of life.

选剑局为侵蚀潮周边作业所设计的套组装备。
它是一段有关侵蚀潮的记忆：无情大潮始终拒绝生命。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment designed by the Bureau of Swordmancers for those working near the Blight Tide. 
This is a piece of memory about the Blight Tide: The unfeeling surges have always rejected the notion of life.

decoDesc.en:
Equipment designed by the Bureau of Swordmancers for those working near the Blight Tide. 
This is a dash of despair regarding the Blight Tide: The turbid currents of the unknown have washed all over the land.

Equipment designed by the Bureau of Swordmancers for those working near the Blight Tide.

decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
It first saw service with human armies fighting at the Aggeloid Front.

M.I.警用系列装备。
在战争结束后，梅什科工业调整了生产线，以优秀的轻量化工艺获得了城市警用装备的供应资格。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
When the war ended, Mieszko Industries adjusted their production lines and added effective weight-reduction measures. They thus acquired equipment-supply contracts for urban security forces.

decoDesc.cn:
M.I.警用系列装备。
“不要寄望于敌人的怜悯，不要寄望于奇迹的降临，你只能相信你的利刃。”
decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
"Do not trust in miracles or the enemy's mercy. Trust instead in your razor sharp blade."

decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
People often smuggle Mieszko Industries products to the wildlands. Some Landbreaker assassins treat the MI Security Scope as a top-tier accessory.

decoDesc.cn:

“感谢警员先生，我保证这是我这个月最后一次因为没带钥匙而报警了，我保证！”
decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
"Thanks, officer! I swear this'll be the last time I'm calling the police this month for forgetting my keys! PROMISE!"

M.I.警用系列装备。
握柄中填装了源石火药。抵住目标，扣下扳机，短刃会瞬间撕开敌人的装甲和血肉，就像切蛋糕一般顺滑。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
The hilt is filled with an Originium propellant. Push the tip against the target and squeeze the trigger to fire the blade. It will instantly tear through armor and flesh like sponge cake.

desc.cn: 本装备由梅什科工业设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Mieszko Industries and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

这款手套同时具备攻击属性，其验收流程中存在“能否有效击碎天使肢体”这一环节。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
These gloves can also be used as a weapon. Product validation includes an assessment for "effectiveness in smashing Aggeloid appendages".

手环内嵌了微型镇暴用施术单元，整体能量传导性能相当优秀。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment from the MI Security series. 
Features miniaturized Arts Units for riot control and excellent energy conductance.

decoDesc.cn:
耐火性极强的装备。
“人类必将踏遍塔卫二每一寸土地”，奉献者们如此相信，因此愿意在大海之中遏止激流，在焦土之上降伏火焰。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment that features excellent fire resistance rating. 
"Humanity shall spread to every corner of Talos-II." Those who sacrificed their labors and lives believed in this. Thus they stood in the oceans to stop the rushing tide and fought upon the charred lands to subdue the flames.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
耐火性极强的装备。
动火用储能匣也可以被视为一个微型发电站，它能够有效利用环境高温，为使用者提供能源。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment that features excellent fire resistance rating. 
The Hot Work Power Bank can be treated as miniature generators. It effectively converts ambient heat of high temperature environments into usable power for the user.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
耐火性极强的装备。
极高温的环境并不可怕，但若是一处环境的温度会毫无理由地变化，那就需要警惕了。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment that features excellent fire resistance rating. 
Extreme heat is not terrifying. However, be wary if a place suddenly experiences an inexplicable change in temperature.

“在那座火山中，有人听到了歌声。”
decoDesc.en:
Equipment that features excellent fire resistance rating. 
"Someone heard a song at that very volcano."

“嘘，小声点，你就要唤醒它了。”
decoDesc.en:
Equipment that features excellent fire resistance rating. 
"Shh, quiet. You might wake it up."

decoDesc.cn: 医疗者们爱用装备的加重款。穿着生物辅助胸甲的作战人员通常会被人戏称为“移动药品库”，他们通常会在护甲各处塞满急救药物。
decoDesc.en: A heavier version of the medics' preferred equipment. People usually refer to combatants wearing the LYNX Cuirass as "Walking Medkits". These lifesavers often stuff every pocket and holder of their armor with emergency medical supplies.

desc.en: Designed by Rhodes Island and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.en: The medics' preferred equipment. People usually refer to combatants wearing the LYNX Cuirass as "Walking Medkits". These lifesavers often stuff every pocket and holder of their armor with emergency medical supplies.

desc.en: Designed by Rhodes Island and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
医疗者们爱用的装备。
罗德岛开发了能够校准数据的接驳单元，以便在紧急状况下接入不同的维生系统，完成急救作业。
decoDesc.en:
The medics' preferred equipment. 
A connector component developed by Rhodes Island for data calibration. It can be connected to different health support systems to complete various forms of emergency medical care.

desc.cn: 本装备由罗德岛设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Rhodes Island and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
医疗者们爱用的装备。
侵蚀造成的伤害有时并不明显，因此装甲板上也需配置灵活敏锐的探测单元。
decoDesc.en:
The medics' preferred equipment. 
Some Blight injuries are not readily obvious. Hence, sensitive detectors became essential features on armor slabs.

desc.cn: 本装备由罗德岛设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Rhodes Island and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
医疗者们爱用的装备。
除去填补护盾裂口这一作用，在紧急状况下，生物辅助护盾针也可以被用来封闭伤口。
decoDesc.en:
The medics' preferred equipment. 
The LYNX Aegis Injector delivers sealants into cracks to help repair broken shields. It can also be used during emergencies for sealing wounds.

罗德岛仍保留着在装备上配置矿石病监测模组的习惯。
decoDesc.en:
The medics' preferred equipment. 
Rhodes Island still has a tradition of furnishing their PPE with Oripathy monitoring modules.

desc.en: Designed by Rhodes Island and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
选剑局早期向市场推广的产品之一。
天师以“虚怀若谷”为设计理念，在点剑重装甲上真正实现了“化解能量攻击”这一功能。
decoDesc.en:
One of the products marketed by the Bureau of Swordmancers in its early days. 
The Tianshi took "gorge-sized capacity" as their design concept and literally achieved "absorption and neutralization" of energy-based attacks.

desc.cn: 本装备由宏山选剑局设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
选剑局早期向市场推广的产品之一。
火石会以超频方式耗光点剑护甲系统的全部能量，它的光芒只会在生命消逝前夕亮起。
decoDesc.en:
One of the products marketed by the Bureau of Swordmancers in its early days. 
The flint essentially overclocks and depletes the energy reserves of the Swordmancer armor system. It only shines when the wearer brushes against death itself.

desc.cn: 本装备由宏山选剑局设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
选剑局早期向市场推广的产品之一。
“岁末，执剑以南，见山生九首，怒号不止，吉。”
decoDesc.en:
One of the products marketed by the Bureau of Swordmancers in its early days. 
"Year's end. Brought my blade south. The mountain grew nine heads and roared incessantly. An auspicious day."

desc.cn: 本装备由宏山选剑局设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
选剑局早期向市场推广的产品之一。
战术手甲的验收流程包括“穿着手甲将宣纸折成二十四层纸花”这一环节。
decoDesc.en:
One of the products marketed by the Bureau of Swordmancers in its early days. 
Product validation for the tactical gauntlets include this particular assessment: "Make a 24-fold flower with a sheet of Xuan paper while wearing these gauntlets."

desc.cn: 本装备由宏山选剑局设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 轻巧的实验型防护装备。“宏山人会以羽毛比喻重量之轻，本实验室的反重力系列产品距此标准仅有一步之遥。”
decoDesc.en: Lightweight experimental protective equipment. "The people of Hongshan use feather as a simile for lightness in weight. The anti-gravity solutions provided by our Labs are just one tiny step away."

desc.cn: 本装备由轻超域技术实验室设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Portable Æthertech Labs and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
轻巧的实验型防护装备。
“本实验室正在潜心研究侵蚀扩散痕迹的数据化分析方法，欢迎报名参与产品试用。”
decoDesc.en:
Lightweight experimental protective equipment. 
"We're exploring the means of digitally analyzing signs of Blight growth. Everyone is welcome to sign-up for product trials."

desc.cn: 本装备由轻超域技术实验室设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Portable Æthertech Labs and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
轻巧的实验型防护装备。
“为了避免参数混乱导致您像气球一样飘向高空，请随身携带配套稳定盘，谢谢。”
decoDesc.en:
Lightweight experimental protective equipment. 
"Keep the stabilizer on at all times, thank you. This will prevent you from soaring to the skies like an untethered balloon during parameter fluctuations."

desc.cn: 本装备由轻超域技术实验室设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Portable Æthertech Labs and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
轻巧的实验型防护装备。
“请在佩戴本实验室产品时额外装配内衬装备，若您出现幻听、幻视等症状，请卸下本实验室产品并及时进食。”
decoDesc.en:
Lightweight experimental protective equipment. 
"Always wear extra padding when using our products. If you experience any auditory or visual hallucinations, please TAKE OFF our products IMMEDIATELY and consume some food."

desc.cn: 本装备由轻超域技术实验室设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Portable Æthertech Labs and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
设计新颖的装备。
很少有人能理解终末地工业为什么要研发这套适用于信息化战争的防御装备。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment with novel designs. 
Most could not understand why Endfield Industries developed a defensive suit for fighting digital warfare.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
设计新颖的装备。
它能在无边的数据之海中抹去几根善于藏匿的“金针”。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment with novel designs. 
It searches the endless ocean of data for the well-hidden "golden outliers", and then erases them from existence.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
设计新颖的装备。
很少有人能理解终末地工业为什么要提高脉冲系列装备的低温耐受能力。
decoDesc.en:
Equipment with novel designs. 
Most could not understand why Endfield Industries added better thermal insulation for their Pulser Labs series PPE.

desc.cn: 本装备由终末地工业自研，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Independently designed by Endfield Industries and assembled by the AIC. This equipment improves the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
某位“疯狂”天师的遗世之作。
常人或许很难将厨艺与息壤供能联系在一起，但武陵城中偏偏有人能在餐馆中获得设计灵感。
decoDesc.en:
Legacy of a "mad" Tianshi. 
Most would struggle to establish a connection between kitchen work and Xiranite. However, a particular Wuling resident actually derives design inspirations when dining at a restaurant.

desc.cn: 本装备由宏山选剑局设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
某位“疯狂”天师的遗世之作。
……他也曾端着一盆“竹沥炖豆腐”穿街而过，并宣称新一代息壤冷却技术终于被他烹饪了出来。
decoDesc.en:
Legacy of a "mad" Tianshi. 
...He once walked the streets with a large bowl of Tofu Stewed in Bamboo Dew, and claimed that he just concocted the next generation of Xiranite-based refrigeration technology.

desc.cn: 本装备由宏山选剑局设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

……他也曾端着一盆“竹沥炖豆腐”穿街而过，并宣称新一代息壤冷却技术终于被他烹饪了出来。
decoDesc.en:
Legacy of a "mad" Tianshi. 
...He once walked the streets with a large bowl of Tofu Stewed in Bamboo Dew, and claimed that he just concocted the next generation of Xiranite-based refrigeration technology.

desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
某位“疯狂”天师的遗世之作。
……据说这位疯狂天师在乌萨斯厨师端上桌的火锅中看到了一种“生生不息的循环”，成功将长息装甲的续航时间提高了一倍。
decoDesc.en:
Legacy of a "mad" Tianshi. 
...It was said that the mad Tianshi saw a "self-feeding cycle" in a hotpot served by an Ursus chef. This inspiration allowed him to more than double the power duration of Eternal Xiranite protective equipment.

desc.cn: 本装备由宏山选剑局设计，使用集成工业系统制造，能够提高使用者的作战能力。
desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn:
某位“疯狂”天师的遗世之作。
……数日后，疯狂的天师开始拒绝一切“不能让自己获得灵感”的食物，随即，为了探寻“能吞入腹中的息壤”，骨瘦如柴的他消失在了荒野中。
decoDesc.en:
Legacy of a "mad" Tianshi. 
...Days passed and the mad Tianshi began to reject any food that "fail to deliver inspirations". After being reduced to skin and bones, he soon disappeared into the wildlands in pursuit of "palatable Xiranite".

desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

Legacy of a "mad" Tianshi.

desc.en: Designed by Hongshan Swordmancers and assembled by the AIC Factory. This equipment can improve the wearer's combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 仿佛是食物的物品，强烈不建议食用。以受雾火影响的肉干代替木屑，以特殊异香石代替砂糖，如此熏制出来的蔬菜只有真正的“强者”才敢尝试。
decoDesc.en: Despite looking edible, we do not recommend eating this. This is a smoked "plant" prepared by using hazefyre-tainted jerky in place of sawdust and special aggagrit to replace sugar. Only the "bravest of the brave" would dare try it.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。

decoDesc.cn: 记录了作战录像的储存装置，可以帮助新干员掌握作战知识。额外增加了历史战役模拟，能让观众了解到塔卫二最残酷的战争景象。
decoDesc.en: A storage device with combat video recordings. New operators can use this to acquire combat knowledge. This is also furnished with simulations of historical battles so that viewers can better appreciate the brutal nature of actual wars fought upon Talos-II.

desc.cn: 用于干员1-60级等级提升的素材，提供了大量干员升级经验。
desc.en: A material that provides a lot of EXP for leveling up Lv.1-60 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 记录了作战录像的储存装置，可以帮助新干员掌握作战知识。
decoDesc.en: A storage device with combat video recordings. New operators can use this to acquire combat knowledge.

desc.cn: 用于干员1-60级等级提升的素材，提供了少量干员升级经验。
desc.en: A material that provides some EXP for leveling up Lv.1-60 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 记录了作战录像的储存装置，可以帮助新干员掌握作战知识。录像结尾附加了各训练项目成绩优秀干员的访谈记录。
decoDesc.en: A storage device with combat video recordings. New operators can use this to acquire combat knowledge. The end of each recording also features interviews conducted with operators who excelled in various training exercises.

desc.cn: 用于干员1-60级等级提升的素材，提供了中量干员升级经验。
desc.en: A material that provides decent EXP for leveling up Lv.1-60 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业研发的信息存储单元，适配各种读取设备，能有效帮助新干员掌握作战知识。仰赖于寂语修会的助力，本款载体压缩储存了更多信息。
decoDesc.en: A data storage unit developed by Endfield Industries. It is compatible with various data access devices. New operators can use it to effectively acquire combat knowledge. Thanks to support offered Cabal of Tranquility, this carrier features data compression technology and thus stores even more information.

desc.cn: 用于干员61-90级等级提升的素材，提供了大量干员升级经验。
desc.en: A material that provides a lot of EXP for leveling up Lv.61-90 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业研发的信息存储单元，适配各种读取设备，能有效帮助新干员掌握作战知识。

decoDesc.cn: 一份厚厚的笔记。上面的字迹不甚规整，草图却画得仔细，看得出记录者用心回忆了各种细节。
decoDesc.en: A thick stack of notes. The handwriting is messy but the sketch was meticulously done. The author devoted quite a bit of effort to recall and jot down all sorts of details.

desc.cn: 罗曼自用的经验总结，记录了辨识与处理四号谷地周边食材的各种诀窍。
desc.en: Roman used his life-long experience to record various techniques for processing edible plants local to Valley IV.

decoDesc.cn: 一本写满了各类内推信息的小册子。新干员往往会受邀写下自己听闻过的可靠人才，当然，这些信息需要一段时间验证完毕才能录入系统。

desc.cn: 在下一个特许寻访开启时，该寻访情报书将自动转化为对应特许寻访的专有十连凭证，此十连凭证将在对应寻访结束后失效。
desc.en: Once the next Chartered Headhunting banner begins, this headhunting dossier will be automatically converted to a special 10×Permit of the Chartered Headhunting banner. However, this 10×Permit will also expire once that banner ends.

decoDesc.cn: 代表着物资保障额度的凭证。终末地工业会为干员提供包括衣食住行在内的多项保障。
decoDesc.en: A certificate recognized in the exchanges of supply quotas. Endfield operators are guaranteed a wide range of amenities that cover daily expenses, traveling, and accommodations.

desc.cn: 可用于在配额兑换所中兑换物资。
desc.en: Exchangeable for goods at the Quota Exchange.

decoDesc.cn: 代表着干员在各领域拥有专业知识的凭证。您的干员来自天南海北，他们于此写下自己的名字，自己的故事与生命。
decoDesc.en: A certificate that symbolizes the breadth of expertise and knowledge of Endfield operators. Your Endfielders come from all corners of the world. They have etched their names, their stories, and their lives upon this place.

desc.cn: 珍贵的配额资源，可用于在配额兑换所中兑换物资。
desc.en: A rare quota resource. Exchangeable for goods at the Quota Exchange.

decoDesc.cn: “武装到牙齿总不会有坏处。”——肖恩·卡拉德
decoDesc.en: "It doesn't hurt to be armed to the teeth." — Shayen Krad

desc.cn: 武库申领时使用的配额资源，可用于购买武器。
desc.en: A special Arsenal Issue currency. Can be used to purchase weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 代表着物资供给额度的凭证。集成工业系统能够以近乎打印的效率完成物资产出，这正是它的强大之处。
decoDesc.en: A certificate recognized in the exchanges of supply quotas. People say the AIC Factory doesn't produce goods. It "prints" them. That's how fast and powerful it is.

desc.cn: 可用于在配额兑换所中兑换物资。

desc.cn: 可作为礼物送给爱好 [生活]  [文化] 的干员以增加信赖度。
desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Lifestyle] and/or [Culture] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: “侵蚀让世界化开，而您的主体仍然锐利，选择尼克拉斯006C，让我们用目光连接未来。”
decoDesc.en: "The Blight may melt the world, but your individuality remains as keen as before. Choose Nikolas 006C. Connect our vision to the future."

desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Technology] and/or [Nature] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: 模仿星门关键零件制成的小玩具，拥有多种拼装难度，传说完成最高难度的人就有机会修好星门。
decoDesc.en: A toy designed according to key components of the Cosmic Gate. These puzzles come in all sorts of assembling difficulties. Legends say those who complete the most challenging puzzles may have a chance of repairing the Cosmic Gate itself.

desc.cn: 可作为礼物送给爱好 [益智]  [文化] 的干员以增加信赖度。
desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Mind Honing] and/or [Culture] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: 菈梵朵玛冲浪大赛的门票。前往会场时记得携带自己的冲浪板。
decoDesc.en: An entry ticket to the La Fantoma Surfing Festival. Do not forget to bring your own surfing board when you head over to the competition.

desc.cn: 可作为礼物送给爱好 [运动]  [艺术] 的干员以增加信赖度。
desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Sports] and/or [Fine Arts] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: 包装精致的香水，主要成分萃取自耶尔什雪山植物，味道能让人联想起雪山上清冷的风。
decoDesc.en: Intricately packaged perfume. The primary ingredients are extracts of plants growing on the snowcapped peaks of Kjersch. The fragrance is a reminder of refreshing mountain breeze.

desc.cn: 可作为礼物送给爱好 [创意]  [时尚] 的干员以增加信赖度。
desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Creative] and/or [Fashion] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: 人类初次探索塔卫二海洋时发现的瑰丽晶石，有许多流入市场后被加工成了标本。原来海洋深处还会有这样的瑰宝，这让人们倍感振奋。
decoDesc.en: A beautiful crystalline stone found during humanity's earliest attempts to explore the seas of Talos-II. Some of them have entered the market and processed into various collector's items. The fact that such beautiful items exist in the depths of Talosian seas is extremely exciting.

desc.cn: 可作为礼物送给爱好 [自然]  [文化] 的干员以增加信赖度。
desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Nature] and/or [Culture] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: 材料细腻的披巾，塞梦珂的手艺人们将之视为友谊的象征，是赠予友人的上好礼品。
decoDesc.en: A shawl woven from soft, fine fibers. The craftmakers of Simonch treat these shawls as a symbol of friendship. They would make wonderful gifts for your friends.

desc.cn: 可作为礼物送给爱好 [艺术]  [生活] 的干员以增加信赖度。
desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Fine Arts] and/or [Lifestyle] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: 在整个文明环带广为流传的科普刊物，该杂志近期正着重于介绍终末地工业的前沿技术。
decoDesc.en: A popular science periodical in the Civilization Band. Recent issues of the magazine are focusing on the pioneering technologies of Endfield Industries.

desc.cn: 可作为礼物送给爱好 [科技]  [公益] 的干员以增加信赖度。
desc.en: Give it to operators whose hobbies are [Technology] and/or [Charity] to build trust with them.

decoDesc.cn: 出于本身的脆性、重量、侵蚀耐受程度等方面的缺陷，紫晶质瓶在文明环带市场中已逐渐被淘汰。
decoDesc.en: Amethyst bottles are being phased out from markets in the Civilization Band due to its fragility, weight, and Blight resistance.

desc.cn: 由紫晶纤维加工得来的瓶子，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A bottle made by processing Amethyst Fibers. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 具备一定通用性的紫晶零件。
decoDesc.en: An Amethyst part with a wide range of uses.

desc.cn: 紫晶纤维经加工后成型的零件，可用于其他材料合成或设备制造。
desc.en: A device part made by processing Amethyst Fibers. Can be used to produce other items or facility construction.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 部分特殊化学试剂仅能以高晶质瓶储存，其中就包括凶名显赫的“蚀水”——域化三氯化铁溶液。
decoDesc.en: Special chemical reagents can only be properly stored with Cryston Bottles. An example would be the notorious aqua mordax, otherwise known as the "corroding water" or localized ferric chloride solvent.

desc.cn: 由高晶纤维加工后得来的金属瓶，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A metallic bottle made by processing Cryston Fibers. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 具备一定通用性的高晶零件。
decoDesc.en: A Cryston Part with a wide range of uses.

desc.cn: 高晶纤维经加工后成型的零件，可用于其他材料合成或设备制造。
desc.en: A device part made by processing Cryston Fibers. Can be used to produce other items or facility construction.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 罗莎送给罗马诺的手表，除了显示时间外似乎还有其他的功能。
decoDesc.en: Rosa gave this watch to Romano. It keeps the time, but seems to have another feature.

desc.cn: 罗马诺的手表。
desc.en: Romano's Watch.

decoDesc.cn: 一瓶已经用了一大半的药剂，散发着奇特的香味。瓶身贴有“不可过量食用”的手写标签，但“不可过量”四个字已经被磨损得看不清。
decoDesc.en: A half-empty vial of a mysterious medicine with a strange aroma. The bottle has a warning label that reads DO NOT OVERDOSE. The first two words were torn and barely legible.

desc.cn: 工团研究员林奈遗失的药剂。
desc.en: Medicine lost by UWST scientist Linnaeus.

decoDesc.cn: 广泛流通的货币，防伪技术极为高超。能买到东西的钞票才是好钞票。
decoDesc.en: A popular currency furnished with highly advanced anti-counterfeiting technologies. You know it's good money when you can purchase things with it.

desc.cn: 广泛流通的货币，用途广泛。
desc.en: TC for short. This currency is recognized and used in many places.

decoDesc.cn: 被染成息壤色的肉丸。虽然它几可乱真的外观会让人在下箸前犹豫许久，但是它的松软鲜香总能征服食客。
decoDesc.en: Meatballs dyed in a way to make them resemble Xiranite. Although the resemblance is close enough to make diners hesitate, the tenderness, fragrance, and flavors are guaranteed to conquer every foodie.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 外观豪放的乱炒笋，对刀工、火候的要求都不高。武陵有多少户人家便有多少种乱炒的做法。
decoDesc.en: A generous and colorful dish. No one cares how the ingredient is cut or stir-fried, or how strong the fire is. Every Wuling household has their own Flame-Boyance approach.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 家常小菜。大概是许多清波寨孩子们学会的第一道家常菜……大概。
decoDesc.en: An everyday family dish prepared by stir-frying bamboo sprouts with meat strips. This is also the first dish that the children of Qingbo Stockade learn about ... or so they say.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 大火炝炒而成的菜肴。这道菜的烹饪时间应以秒计，稍稍拖沓数秒就会让它的口感一塌糊涂。
decoDesc.en: A dish prepared with a wok and intense fire. Stir-frying this only takes seconds. A blink or two longer and you'll get a disaster with abysmal texture.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 用来开启协议核心的钥匙。
decoDesc.en: A key item for unlocking the Protocol Automation-Core.

decoDesc.cn: 市面上较为少见的铁瓶，即便与异铁极度近似的蓝铁具备较强的抗氧化性，但人们依旧喜爱使用钢制容器。
decoDesc.en: A metallic bottle rarely seen in the market. Although ferrium metal offers better resistance against oxidation, people still prefer the steel variant.

desc.cn: 由蓝铁块加工后得来的金属瓶，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A metallic bottle made by processing Ferrium. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 具备一定通用性的铁制零件。
decoDesc.en: A Ferrium Part with a wide range of uses.

desc.cn: 蓝铁经加工后成型的零件，可用于其他材料合成或设备制造。
desc.en: A device part made by processing Ferrium. Can be used to produce other items or facility construction.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 多级加工后，终末地工业生产的钢材已被列为《塔卫二工业金属侵蚀耐受标准》二级标准参考物。
decoDesc.en: Steel manufactured by Endfield Industries has been subject to multiple processing steps. It has been included in the list of Grade 2 Reference Materials in the Talos-II Blight Resistance Standards of Industrial Metals.

desc.cn: 致密蓝铁粉末精炼融合后的高级材料，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A high quality material prepared by refining Dense Ferrium Powder. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 市面上最为常见的钢瓶。
decoDesc.en: A bottle made of steel, the most common of its kind in the market.

desc.cn: 由钢块加工后得来的金属瓶，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A metallic bottle made by moulding Steel. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 具备一定通用性的钢制零件。
decoDesc.en: A Steel Part with a wide range of uses.

desc.cn: 钢块经加工后成型的零件，可用于其他材料合成或设备制造。
desc.en: A device part made by processing Steel. Can be used to produce other items or facility construction.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在协议技术介入下，经过精细研磨后，致密蓝铁粉末广受绘画爱好者欢迎。
decoDesc.en: Techno-Protocol grinding is used to make this preparation of dense Ferrium powder. It is extremely popular amongst traditional artists.

desc.cn: 蓝铁粉末研磨后的细粉，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Acquired by grinding Ferrium Powder. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在塔卫二为什么会存在与异铁如此近似的金属，这仍是未解之谜。
decoDesc.en: A metal of Talos-II that is remarkably similar to Oriron. No one could explain the similarity.

desc.cn: 由蓝铁矿石精炼得来的金属块，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A metallic ingot made by refining Ferrium Ore. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 蓝铁的形成原因众说纷纭，在工业金属尚未出现的时代，它是人们最为依赖的金属。
decoDesc.en: Many theories have been proposed about the origins of Ferrium. Before the age of industrial metallurgy, Ferrium was the most common metal that people used.

desc.cn: 一种天然存在的蓝色合金，可在工业系统中进行加工。
desc.en: A natural-occurring metal complex with blue coloration. It can be processed with the AIC.

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，蓝铁二级加工品的质地更加均匀。
decoDesc.en: Ferrium can be shredded to yield a processed product with improved homogeneity.

desc.cn: 蓝铁块粉碎后的粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Shredded and powdered Ferrium. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 黑乎乎的肉排，能吃出碎骨。与其说是塞什卡风菜式，倒不如说是裂地者们想象中的塞什卡风菜式。
decoDesc.en: A wholly black fillet with bits of bone inside it. Seš'qamam cuisine? Probably not. This feels more like a Landbreakers' fantasy about Seš'qamam food.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。

noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 混入了小块软骨的咸香饼干，造型可爱，但因为材料原因吃起来又干又噎。据说这道菜源自一张裂地者食谱，真是难得，癫狂的“管子人”偶尔也有细腻心思。
decoDesc.en: Savory cookies with bits of cartilaginous material inside it. Look cute but have an extremely dry and gagging taste. This recipe was rumored to be a Landbreaker creation. It would seem that these raiders are actually capable of focusing on the details. A rare occasion indeed.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。

decoDesc.cn: 根据卡贾提供的秘方制备的提神饮料，最好不要在白天就喝它。
decoDesc.en: A stimulating tisane prepared using Karja's secret formula. Don't drink it in daytime, though.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。

decoDesc.cn: 由异香石调料、特殊骨粉冲泡而成的速食汤。明明味道鲜美，但不知为何总会让品尝者生出一种“拿掉骨粉也无伤大雅”的荒诞思考。
decoDesc.en: A soup mix of aggagrit seasoning and special bone meal. Just add hot water. Despite its savory and wholesome flavors, tasters can't help but weirdly fantasize if the soup mix is just as good "without the bone meal".

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。

decoDesc.cn: 在探索途中想吃到一份正宗约翰老妈汉堡确实不易，但努努力的话，你至少能够还原出厚切汉堡的八成风味。
decoDesc.en: Getting an authentic Mama John's burger is not easy for explorations operating in the field. But if you try hard enough, you can make something that is at least eighty-percent similar to the Mama's famous sandwiches.

decoDesc.cn: 它是永远的生命之源。
decoDesc.en: It has always been the source of life.

desc.cn: 干净的清水，在工业系统中有丰富的使用场景。
desc.en: Pure and clean water. It has plenty of uses in the AIC Factory.

decoDesc.cn: 将息壤溶于清水，许多人第一次听到这件事时，会认为它无比简单，但实际上，如果没有恰当的设备与技术，操作者仅能获得毫无意义的产物——如同泡在水中的砂砾。
decoDesc.en: When people first hear about aqueous Xiranite solutions, most would regard its production as a simple process. However, a user without proper equipment nor techniques would only arrive at a useless product — one that is hardly any different than sand mixed in water.

desc.cn: 溶解在清水中的息壤，可用于其他材料合成。常用于灌装后通过射流无人机消除武陵地区的动态侵蚀。
desc.en: Xiranite dissolved in Clean Water. Can be used to produce other materials. Often filled in containers and loaded on jet drones for Liquid Xiranite spraying and elimination of Active Blight in Wuling.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.en: A basic conveyor belt for transporting things. Belts are the blood vessels of the AIC Factory.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后使用
noObtainWayHint.en: Research the specified tech in the Basic AIC Plan to get this.

decoDesc.cn: 筛选即为秩序。
decoDesc.en: Sorting creates order.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后使用
noObtainWayHint.en: Research the specified tech in the Basic AIC Plan to get this.

decoDesc.en: A logistics unit that AIC Factory managers can use to create an organized transport system and avoid the "spaghetti".

desc.cn: 可让两条传送带交叉运输互不干扰的物流工具。
desc.en: A logistics unit that lets 2 transport belts intersect without obstructing each other.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后使用
noObtainWayHint.en: Research the specified tech in the Basic AIC Plan to get this.

decoDesc.en: A transport system adjustment unit with a smart sorting module. Can be used in all sorts of production lines.

desc.cn: 可让多条（最多3条）分支传送带汇流传输到1条传送带的物流工具。
desc.en: A logistics unit that merges up to 3 transport belts into 1 single belt.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后使用
noObtainWayHint.en: Research the specified tech in the Basic AIC Plan to get this.

decoDesc.cn: 据调查，文明环带内近百分之三十的居民相信：城市排水管道网络中存在着一个庞大、黑暗的地下王国。
decoDesc.en: A survey revealed that nearly 30% of residents in the Civilization Band believe that a dark and massive underground kingdom exists within the sprawling urban sewers.

desc.cn: 可以传输液体或气体的传输物流工具。

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后使用

desc.en: A package of medical supplies for the medical staff.

decoDesc.cn: 罗曼不久前送货到源石实验园区的行车记录，包含被裂地者袭击的完整信息。
decoDesc.en: Dashcam record of Roman's recent delivery to the Originium Science Park. It includes extensive records of the Landbreaker attack.

desc.cn: 记录了不久前那场事故的详细信息，能从中获取莱万汀的源石反应参数。
desc.en: This device has detailed recordings of a recent accident. Use it to acquire data on Laevatain's Originium responses.

decoDesc.cn: 采石场塌方事件的详细调查报告，包括那次塌方事故的亲历者记录和事后调查结果。
decoDesc.en: A detailed investigation report of the Quarry Collapse. Includes testimonies from those who experienced the collapse as well as post-incident analysis.

desc.cn: 采石场塌方事件的详细调查报告，能从中获取莱万汀的源石反应参数。
desc.en: A detailed investigation report of the quarry collapse. It provides data on Laevatain's Originium responses.

name.cn: 采石场塌方事件的调查报告

decoDesc.cn: 莎曼对蚀崖观测站周边灼痕进行调查后提交的报告，包括相关的记录、检测过程和数据分析。
decoDesc.en: A report that Salman submitted after investigating the scorch marks near the Blightcliff Observation Post. Includes relevant records, processes of inspection, and data analysis.

desc.cn: 包含对蚀崖观测站附近所发现灼痕的检测结果，能从中获取莱万汀的源石反应参数。
desc.en: An investigation report on scorch marks found near the Blightcliff Observation Post. It provides data on Laevatain's Originium responses.

name.cn: 蚀崖观测站周边灼痕的调查报告
name.en: IR: Scorch Marks Near the Blightcliff OP

desc.cn: 星火划过静海，初啼刺破长夜。生命拒绝归于沉寂。
desc.en: Starfire streaks over seas ever placid, birthsongs shatter a night everlasting. Thus life refuses the silence never-ending.

decoDesc.cn: 碾骨氏族擅自拆解并藏匿的大桥升降控制台零件，似乎是控制台运转需要的关键部分。
decoDesc.en: A component of the control panel for raising and lowering the bridge. The Bonekrushers ripped it out and hid it. It seems essential for getting the control panel to work.

desc.cn: 用于修复大桥升降控制台的零件。
desc.en: Parts for repairing the control panel of a bridge elevator.

decoDesc.cn: 备用ID卡，能用来启动控制台，打开源石园区大门。
decoDesc.en: A backup ID pass. Use it to activate the control panel and open the gate of the Originium Science Park.

desc.cn: 用来开启源石园区大门的ID卡。
desc.en: An ID card to open the gate of the Originium Science Park.

decoDesc.cn: 在研究所大楼门口，塔塔扫描出侵蚀核心的图像记录。
decoDesc.en: An image record of the Blight Core taken by Tata at the entrance of the Research Center building.

desc.cn: 和TA-TA原型机相处的回忆。
desc.en: Memories made with the TA-TA Prototype.

decoDesc.cn: 塔塔视角里，正在矿脉源区信号塔旁休憩的众人的图像记录。
decoDesc.en: An image record taken with Tata's perspective. CONTENT: Endfield Crisis Team resting next to the signal tower at the Origin Lodespring.

desc.cn: 和TA-TA原型机相处的回忆。
desc.en: Memories made with the TA-TA Prototype.

decoDesc.cn: 竹片上歪歪扭扭画着一个“汤”字，汤汤以此来表示对你的感谢。不过，它能用在哪儿呢……
decoDesc.en: A bamboo slip with a badly written "Tang" written on it. This is a token of appreciation from Tangtang. Now, if you could only find a place to spend it on...

desc.cn: 汤汤给你的信物。
desc.en: A token, given to you by Tangtang.

decoDesc.cn: 布满岁月痕迹的人造组件，被天师阿宝称为“钥匙”。
decoDesc.en: An ancient artifact that Tianshi Bao described as a "key".

desc.cn: 天井院地下捡到的“钥匙”，似乎能激活某种机关。
desc.en: Key picked up somewhere beneath Tianjing Courtyard. It might be able to activate a certain mechanism.

decoDesc.cn: 在矿洞里捡到的普通钥匙，明显已经扭曲得无法使用了。
decoDesc.en: A common key picked up in a mining tunnel, but it has been so malformed that it can no longer be used.

desc.cn: 用于开启裂地者地下牢房的铁门。
desc.en: Use this to open a Landbreaker underground prison cell.

decoDesc.cn: 散落在矿洞里的废旧金属元件。
decoDesc.en: Old metal components found in the mines.

desc.cn: 用于制作弧光所说的可以切开铁门的“热指头”。
desc.en: Use this to make the "hot finger" tool described by Arclight. The tool can be used to cut open the cell door.

decoDesc.cn: 铁誓军风格的医药箱，用于储存铁誓军常用的医疗药物。
decoDesc.en: A medical supplies crate with the designs and markings of the Order of Steel Oath. The Order uses this to store commonly used medical supplies.

desc.cn: 铁誓军风格的医药箱。
desc.en: A medical supplies crate from the Order of Steel Oath.

decoDesc.cn: 从工团救援人员处获得的钥匙卡，被工团内部用来启动部分区域的电梯设备。
decoDesc.en: A keycard received from a UWST SAR Crew Mate. It is used to activate the elevators in certain areas.

desc.cn: 用于启动阿伯莉采石场深层管理区电梯的钥匙卡。
desc.en: A keycard for activating elevators in the Aburrey Quarry Deep Management Post.

decoDesc.cn: 陈旧的钥匙卡片，看上去有段年代了。
decoDesc.en: A worn key card. It looks really old.

desc.cn: 用来打开不知名废弃区域的钥匙。
desc.en: A key. It might be used to open some abandoned area.

decoDesc.cn: 因遭受重击而有点凹陷的箱子，里面装着一些残存的药物。
decoDesc.en: A box dented by heavy blows. There are some medicines left inside.

desc.cn: 重新回收的药物。所剩不多，但尚且可以应急。
desc.en: A box of salvaged medicine. Not much is left but it should help with the emergency.

decoDesc.cn: 修复天师桩后获得的零件，集齐五个后可用于激活大型天师坛。
decoDesc.en: A part acquired by repairing the Tianshi Pillar. Collect 5 to activate the large Tianshi Shrine.

desc.cn: 用于激活天师坛的特殊零件。
desc.en: A special part for activating a Tianshi Shrine.

decoDesc.cn: 只需在协议同步器轻轻一扫，后勤部将立刻为您提供海量优惠服务。
decoDesc.en: Scan this with the Protosync and the Logistics Division will offer you tons of special perks, privileges, and services.

desc.cn: 使用后可获得30天的月卡权益。
desc.en: Use this to get Monthly Pass perks for 30 days.

decoDesc.cn:
驮兽粪便，可以为土壤提供丰富养分。
在野外遇见驮兽时，只要拍一拍，就能收获……一个惊喜。
decoDesc.en:
Burdo-Muck provides all sorts of nutrients to the soil. 
If you see a burdenbeast in the wilderness, give it a gentle pat to get yourself a huge, mucking pat of hot, steaming surprise.

desc.cn: 驮兽的粪便，可以在生长期的田块施肥时作为肥料，有缩短田块生长期时间的效果。
desc.en: Burdenbeast dung. Can be used as a fertilizer on a planting plot during the growth phase to shorten its growth phase.

decoDesc.cn:
驮兽粪便加工后产出的肥料，可以对田块进行施肥。
“一块膨地啪，亩产八万八。”
decoDesc.en:
Processed burdo-muck fertilizer. Can be used to fertilize planting plots. 
"Plop a bar of Bumper-Rich to your beautiful fields! Who'd say no to 88 tons per acre yield?"

desc.cn: 驮兽粪便与液化息壤合成的肥料，可以在生长期的田块施肥时作为肥料，有增加田块收获时产物数量的效果。
desc.en: A fertilizer made by mixing burdo-muck with Liquid Xiranite. Can be used to fertilize a planting plot during the growth phase to increase its harvest yield.

decoDesc.cn: 工团在源石培植项目初期尝试过“粉末培植法”，然而由此培育出的晶簇会快速失去活性。
decoDesc.en: The UWST Originium cultivation project initially attempted "powder seeding" but the resulting crystal clusters would often lose their activity quickly.

desc.cn: 源矿粉末研磨后的细粉，状态稳定，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Acquired by grinding Originium Powder. This stable material can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 工业生产活动所必需的基础型矿物。
decoDesc.en: A basic mineral necessary to support most industrial production.

desc.cn: 以最粗粝的状态被挖掘出来的源石，可在工业系统中进行加工。
desc.en: A raw formation of Originium unearthed in its most natural form. This can be processed in the AIC.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地利用协议技术对源石粉末进行了特殊的稳定化处理。
decoDesc.en: Endfield made use of Techno-Protocol to create a stable form of Originium Powder.

desc.cn: 稳定的源石粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A stabilized form of powdered Originium. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 协议源石的衍生物，在极严苛的环境中才能够合成。沉默注视着塔卫二的帝江号因大地之上的苦难而哀恸——部分终末地干员如此相信，故会将衍质源石称作“协议泪滴”。
decoDesc.en: A derivative of Protocol Originium that can only be made with the most extreme processing environments. Some Endfielders call this the Tear of the Protocol. They believe that Dijiang felt sorrow and shed these Tears when she silently gazed upon the suffering of the Talosians.

desc.cn: 极难获取的特殊源石，较为珍贵，用途多样。
desc.en: An extremely rare crystal habit of Originium with many potential uses.

decoDesc.cn:
…坍塌…坠落危险
非专业人员请勿靠近。
如需帮助请联系…（后面已经破损）
——终末地工业
decoDesc.en:
...Collapsing structure... Fall hazards. 
Off limits to non-professionals. 
If you need assistance, please contact... (the rest is torn and illegible) 
—Endfield Industries

decoDesc.cn:
今天听到裂地者大哥说：”揍人是一种本领，挨揍也是一种本领。“
我觉得装死也是一种。
装傻充愣，及时投降也能算本领吧？
简简单单一句话就有这么多道理，大哥永远是我大哥。
必可活用于下次战帮冲突。
decoDesc.en:
Heard our Landbreaker brute say: "Punching is a skill. Tanking punches is also a skill." 
I think playing dead is a skill, too. 
Acting the fool and kneeling quickly enough should be skills as well. 
Brute is a true boss. His words, though simple, are filled with legit wisdom. 
Definitely gonna use these tricks in the next turf war.

decoDesc.cn:
人多耳杂，所以我写在纸上，看完记得烧了。
裂地者抢走了咱们的营地，物资钱财都被他们夺走了。我偷偷去看过，这些杂种刮地三尺，什么都没给我们剩下。
他们太贪了，所以我有一个计划。
只要我们用一些或明或暗的信件或者涂鸦，暗示哪里藏着我们的积蓄，一定会有足够贪心的杂种去偷偷挖掘，到时候就让他看看我们的手段。
没有人永远是猎物，更没有人永远是猎人。
decoDesc.en:
Too many nosy people around, so I wrote it down on paper. Burn it when you're done reading. 
The Landbreakers took our camp, supplies, and cash. I sneaked over there and saw what they did. The LB scum took apart everything. Even mama's kitchen sink! 
I got a plan to deal with these greedy scab eaters.
We'll leave a few obvious and subtle clues, graffiti, and letters about secret loot stashes that don't exist. Some of the LBs are bound to bite the bait and do their own digging in secret. When that happens, we'll show them what we're made of. 
No one is the eternal prey. And no one is the eternal hunter.

decoDesc.cn:
我太贪了，这是个陷阱。我的腿已经断了，我回不去了。
看到这张纸的人，求你帮忙把钱给我母亲，只给一部分也可以，我把它们藏在
decoDesc.en:
Dammit. I got too greedy. It's a trap, and it broke my friggin' legs. I can't get out. 
If you read this, send my moolah to my mom. You can keep some for yourself. I hid them at...

decoDesc.cn:
（潦草的字迹）
那小鬼不可信，等赚足了之后，不如我们想想办法做掉他。
（更潦草的字迹）
记着下手干净点，我总怀疑他背后有什么人。
decoDesc.en:
(Handwritten scribbles) 
Don't trust that brat. I say we zero him once we make the creds. 
(Poorly written scribbles) 
Make it clean. Methinks the kid gots some bigshot backing him.

decoDesc.cn: 最终被记下的是一小段话语，又或某个委托。线条编织，棋子轻轻落下，您已知晓这一切。
decoDesc.en: The last log is a small passage, or some form of a directive. The threads have been woven and the pieces are in place. You knew about all this.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁管理员的留影“记忆网纸”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks the Endministrator's snapshot: "Memory Mesh". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 最终被记下的是一小段话语，又或某个委托。线条编织，棋子轻轻落下，您已知晓这一切。
decoDesc.en: The last log is a small passage, or some form of a directive. The threads have been woven and the pieces are in place. You knew about all this.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁管理员的留影“记忆网纸”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks the Endministrator's snapshot: "Memory Mesh". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 当群星的碎屑遮掩住光芒，她平静地照亮你的前路。她在闪耀。
decoDesc.en: When debris of the stars blocks the light, she will calmly illuminate your path. Look how she shines.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁佩丽卡的留影“引领者”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Perlica's snapshot: "The Guide". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 龙与剑，闯天涯。
decoDesc.en: The Lung and her blade have embarked on a great adventure.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁陈千语的留影“侠迹”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Chen Qianyu's snapshot: "Errant's Deed". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 荒野上最优秀的猎手总会在最合适的时机现身。
decoDesc.en: The best hunter of the wildlands will always appear at the best opportunities.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁狼卫的留影“狩猎时间到”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Wulfgard's snapshot: "Time for the Hunt". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 当感官不再可靠，游人从歌谣中获得指引。
decoDesc.en: When the senses could no longer be relied upon, a Songseeker could always seek guidance from verses of the hanna.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁弧光的留影“向晚”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Arclight's snapshot: "Dipping Sun". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 咽下事实，消化结果，积蓄力量。
decoDesc.en: Swallow the truth, break down the results, and regain power.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁余烬的留影“誓言未竟”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Ember's snapshot: "An Oath Not Yet Fulfilled". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 她渴望探究与世间万物相关的所有知识，当然，也包括你的。
decoDesc.en: She desires to investigate every facet of knowledge about everything in this world. Of course, that naturally includes you as well.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁赛希的留影“求知欲”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Xaihi's snapshot: "Desire for Knowledge". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 她一直独自旅行，直到遇见了你。
decoDesc.en: She had always traveled alone until she ran into you.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁艾维文娜的留影“找到你咯”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Avywenna's snapshot: "Found Ya". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 少女等待着一个回应，就像在等着一封回信。
decoDesc.en: She waited for a response as though she's waiting for a return letter.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁洁尔佩塔的留影“静候心音”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Gilberta's snapshot: "Patiently Waiting". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 在翻越下一座山峰前，在下一个救援信号到来前，一杯耶尔什风味的热可可绝对是个不错的选择。
decoDesc.en: A mug of hot cocoa of flavors from Kjersch is definitely a great choice before hiking the next mountain or receiving the next SOS distress call.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁昼雪的留影“休整间隙”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Snowshine's snapshot: "Moment for a Break". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 他又来找你掰手腕了。有朝一日，他会成为你的臂膀。
decoDesc.en: He's back again for more arm wrestling. One day, he'll become your right arm.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁黎风的留影“证果”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Lifeng's snapshot: "Proof of Enlightenment". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 火焰吞没了她的过去，但一个许诺，让她决意为未来而挥剑。
decoDesc.en: The flames swallowed her past. But a single promise steeled her resolve to swing her sword for the future.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁莱万汀的留影“火与剑”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Laevatain's snapshot: "Fire and Sword". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 从繁忙的超域研究中抽身，休息一下，聊聊《MARTHE月刊》跟流光幻变指甲油吧？
decoDesc.en: Got some time off the superbusy research project about the Ætherside. Now, why don't we talk about Monthly MARTHE and shimmer-glimmer meta-spectral nail varnish?

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁伊冯的留影“潮流对谈”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Yvonne's snapshot: "Trendy-fique Discourse". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 轻装上阵，引擎轰鸣。他跟他的铁锅，准备出发。
decoDesc.en: Lightly packed plus the trusty iron wok. The motor roars. Time to hit the road.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁大潘的留影“旅行伊始”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Da Pan's snapshot: "The Journey Begins". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 是理想，是期待，是奔腾的热忱——以笑容宣告，她前来报到。
decoDesc.en: Dreams, hopes, and roaring passion — Heralded by her smile. She's reporting in.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁秋栗的留影“前来报到”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Akekuri's snapshot: "Reporting In". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 无论何时，那道手执坚盾的湛蓝身影始终在那里。
decoDesc.en: The deep blue figure is always there with shield in hand. No matter the time.

decoDesc.en: She ceased her quick, dainty steps and was no longer in a rush. Someone familiar caught her eyes, and she paused for a bit.

decoDesc.en: Like the brightest drop of sun atop the frozen peaks, the very sight of her brings instant warmth to those trapped in precipitous snow. She will brave the frigid cold and bring them to survival.

decoDesc.en: She wove an infinity of possibilities that were then etched upon the blueprints. They are the future that she always carries with her.

decoDesc.en: The blade is drawn. The lung has soared. The wind is blowing. The clouds are roiling.

decoDesc.en: The young predator stepped into his personal hunting ground as the Wolf Spirit howled. His eyes are on every single prey, and his guns will bring every single one of them down.

decoDesc.en: She always called herself an Echoling, but the many people she saved from breaker blades insisted on addressing her as an Aldertone.
