decoDesc.cn: 坚硬的血和炽热的钢在北地筑成堡垒。那里不是她的梦魇，那里仍是下一个终点。
decoDesc.en: Red hot steel and solid blood were the brick and mortar of the northern bastions. The North is not her nightmare. It is merely her next destination.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁余烬的留影“不落坚城”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Ember's snapshot: "The Bastion Never Breached". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 不要恐惧未知，不要拒绝混乱——这即是她探究真理的信条。
decoDesc.en: Do not fear the unknown, and do not reject chaos. Such are the tenets that guide her search for truth.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁赛希的留影“凝望真理”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Xaihi's snapshot: "Gaze Long into Veritas". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 面对未知的旅程，信使毫不犹豫地向你发起邀约。
decoDesc.en: The journey is uncertain, but the messenger never hesitated when toasting you this invite.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁艾维文娜的留影“未知邀约”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Avywenna's snapshot: "Mystery Invite". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 将视野倒转，你会发现不一样的景色、不一样的心情、不一样的自己。世界变成了崭新的。
decoDesc.en: Turn your vision upside down and you'll see different views, experience different moods, and become a different you. Oh my, the world has become completely new.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁洁尔佩塔的留影“世界翻转”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Gilberta's snapshot: "Let's Flip the World". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 行走于雪山之间，滑翔于冰雪之上，少女始终疾驰在全力救助他人生命的路途中。
decoDesc.en: The girl trudged through the peaks and carved a path down the snowy slopes. She is always straightlining her way to save lives in distress.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁昼雪的留影“雪中滑翔”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Snowshine's snapshot: "Carving Through the Snow". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 如璞玉，千琢而不晦。
decoDesc.en: Like a block of natural jade, he will endure the chiseling and retain his purity of heart.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁黎风的留影“少年心”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Lifeng's snapshot: "Heart of Youth". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 陪她走进无忆的长夜，陪她焚尽黑暗的梦魇，陪她点燃映照前路的火焰。
decoDesc.en: Accompany her through long nights without memories. Fight with her and burn the dark, nightmarish enemies. Stand with her as she lights fires to illuminate future journeys.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁莱万汀的留影“熔火之邀”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Laevatain's snapshot: "An Invite to the Melting Fire". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

name.en: An Invite to the Melting Fire

decoDesc.cn: 亮丽的涂装、轻快的音乐，还有游戏获胜时的笑容……每个开心的时刻，她都记录了下来，与你共享。
decoDesc.en: Bright-colored coatings, an upbeat soundtrack, and a satisfied smile of victory... She has recorded every joyous moment and now she's sharing them with you.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁伊冯的留影“Win-Win!”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Yvonne's snapshot: "Win-Win!". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 生活不像做菜，能把料备全再下锅。但所见、所感，都能拿来做食材，翻炒出人间百味。
decoDesc.en: Life is nothing like cooking where you can prep everything before dunking them into the wok. However, the things we saw and experienced can be used as ingredients to offer all the tastes of life.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁大潘的留影“人间百味”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Da Pan's snapshot: "All the Tastes of Life". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 她微笑着，像破晓时的风，带着未曾言说的希望，蕴藏着静默的勇气。
decoDesc.en: Like the breeze of daybreak, her smile conveyed hope not yet spoken and carried a courage that waited in silence.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁秋栗的留影“明日新星”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Akekuri's snapshot: "Rising Star of Tomorrow". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 令人放心的安全感与让人满足的饱腹感——永远是他所在的队伍里最不会缺乏的东西。
decoDesc.en: Reassuring sense of security and gastronomic satisfaction — His team is never short on these.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁卡契尔的留影“坚实后盾”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Catcher's snapshot: "Shield to Fall Back On". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 你介意与人分享忙里偷闲的时光吗？
decoDesc.en: Mind sharing your hard-earned free time with someone?

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁埃特拉的留影“秘密时间”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Estella's snapshot: "Secret Hour". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 正义从不缺席，但如果正义迟到，那可就有乐子看了。
decoDesc.en: Justice is always served. However, if justice decides to show up late, then we're in for quite a show.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁萤石的留影“规则边缘”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Fluorite's snapshot: "Gray Fringes of the Rules". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 他学习，他领悟，他正在无尽的求索中迈向那唯一的解答。
decoDesc.en: He learns. He gains enlightenment. He is on an endless path towards the only answer.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁安塔尔的留影“造极”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Antal's snapshot: "A New Zenith". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: “钓鳞时哪一刻心情最好？”“挥竿。”“为什么？”“所有的期待都还在前方，未知让人心跳加速。”
decoDesc.en: "What is the best moment when angling?" "When casting the rod." "Why?" "Because therein lies your hopes. Uncertainty makes the heart race."

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁阿列什的留影“挥竿日”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Alesh's snapshot: "Rod Casting Day". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 冰冷坚硬的岩石上开满了花朵，荒漠充满生机和暖意，悠扬的旋律在耳边哼唱……前辈，这不是梦，对吧？
decoDesc.en: Flowers blooming on cold, hard rocks ... barren lands teeming with life and warmth ... and idyllic songs humming by our ears... Professor, this isn't just a dream, right?

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁艾尔黛拉的留影“心愿”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Ardelia's snapshot: "Aspiration". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 她还有许多问题等待解答，她还有许多困难需要克服。即便如此，她也一定会完成你给的每一项任务，让更多人找回笑容。
decoDesc.en: She has many unanswered questions, and many difficulties not yet overcome. Nevertheless, she will complete all of your assignments and bring back the smiles on everyone's faces.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁别礼的留影“初绽霜花”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Last Rite's snapshot: "First Rime to Bloom". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 硝烟似散非散，千钧之躯落下生与死的棋子；剑锋倚地，支撑着铁誓，亦支撑着守望——此刻，将军。
decoDesc.en: The smoke of ruin still lingered. Numerous pieces, living and dead, fell off the ponderous corpse. His blade served as the support of his body, his steel oath, and his vigil — And then he made his move. Checkmate.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁骏卫的留影“将军”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks Pogranichnik's snapshot: "Checkmate". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 所凝聚的信任在您掌中，它的第一枚碎片名为历史，又名为文明与生命。
decoDesc.en: Trust and faith congealed within your palm. The first fragment is named history. Its other name is Civilization and Life.

desc.cn: 获取后，可解锁管理员的留影“掌握”。干员留影可以在帝江号会客室的EF02循流图像仪上进行展示。
desc.en: Getting this unlocks the Endministrator's snapshot: "Fully Grasped". Operator snapshots can be showcased on a loop using the EF02 Slide Projector in the Reception Room aboard Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 酮化灌木是塔卫二的本土植物，它往往生长于土壤成分较为特殊的环境中。
decoDesc.en: Aketine is a species of flora native to Talos-II. It usually grows at places with unique soil composition.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集或在工厂培育出的植物，内含易燃易爆成分，常用于制造工业爆炸物。
desc.en: A plant that can be gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the AIC Factory. It contains flammable and explosive substances and can be used to make Industrial Explosives.

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，酮化灌木的成分提取过程将更加便利。
decoDesc.en: It is easier to extract target materials and substances from shredded Aketine.

desc.cn: 酮化灌木粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Powdered form of Aketine. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 大部分学者认为，酮化灌木中之所以能提取到硝化物，是因为它吸收了过量含有侵蚀物质的雨水。
decoDesc.en: Nitrates can be extracted from Aketine. Scientists believe this is caused by the absorption of rainwater with excessively high levels of Blighted materials.

desc.cn: 酮化灌木的种子，可用于培育酮化灌木。
desc.en: Seeds picked from the Aketine plant. Cultivate them with crafted farm plots to raise Aketine.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 多齿叶的提取物曾被用于制造急救药物。
decoDesc.en: Dendra extracts were once used as emergency medication.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊植物。
其提取物可在干员1~3级技能强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special plant gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Extracts of this plant can be used for operator skill upgrades at skill levels 1 to 3.

decoDesc.cn: 目前多齿叶仍属于较难培植的塔卫二本土植物之一。
decoDesc.en: Dendras are plants native to Talos-II. Farming dendras can be quite a challenge.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊植物。
其提取物可在干员4~6级技能强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special plant gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Extracts of this plant can be used for operator skill upgrades at skill levels 4 to 6.

decoDesc.cn: 误食多齿叶极可能会使误食者出现血压升高、心动过速、恶心、呕吐等症状。
decoDesc.en: Accidental consumption of dendras may lead to high blood pressure, faster heart rates, nauseousness, and vomiting.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊植物。
其提取物可在干员7~9级技能强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special plant gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Extracts of this plant can be used for operator skill upgrades at skill levels 7 to 9.

decoDesc.cn: 部分研究者猜测，在特殊侵蚀状况下，任何小型灌木都有可能逐渐转化为受蚀玉化叶。
decoDesc.en: Some scientists believe that certain Blight conditions can transform any bush or shrub into the Blighted Jadeleaves.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊植物。
其提取物可在干员技能专精时使用。
desc.en:
A special plant gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Extracts of this plant can be used in operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 具备岩石质感的古老植物，生长期的岩天使叶远看时会被误认为是某种小型天使。在人类沉寂的岁月中，塔卫二的生命并未止步不前。
decoDesc.en: An ancient plant that looks and feels like a rock. The False Aggela takes on the appearance of tiny Aggeloi when growing. Life on Talos-II never stopped evolving, even during humanity's silence.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊植物。
其提取物可在干员技能专精时使用。
desc.en:
A special plant gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Extracts of this plant can be used in operator skill mastery.

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的晶化多齿叶，其根茎的成活性较强。
decoDesc.en: A Kalkodendra tuber carefully selected for survivability.

desc.cn:
晶化多齿叶的根茎，可以用于培养全新的个体。
晶化多齿叶可在干员1~3级技能强化时使用。
desc.en:
A Kalkodendra tuber that can be cultivated into a new adult plant. 
Kalkodendra can be used for operator skill upgrades at skill levels 1 to 3.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的纯晶多齿叶，其根茎的成活性较强。
decoDesc.en: A Chrysodendra tuber carefully selected for survivability.

desc.cn:
纯晶多齿叶的根茎，可以用于培养全新的个体。
纯晶多齿叶可在干员4~6级技能强化时使用。
desc.en:
A Chrysodendra tuber that can be cultivated into a new adult plant. 
Chrysodendra can be used for operator skill upgrades at skill levels 4 to 6.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的至晶多齿叶，其根茎的成活性较强。
decoDesc.en: A Vitrodendra tuber carefully selected for survivability.

desc.cn:
至晶多齿叶的根茎，可以用于培养全新的个体。
至晶多齿叶可在干员7~9级技能强化时使用。
desc.en:
A Vitrodendra tuber that can be cultivated into a new adult plant. 
Vitrodendra can be used for operator skill upgrades at skill levels 7 to 9.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的受蚀玉化叶，其根茎的成活性较强。
decoDesc.en: A Blighted Jadeleaf tuber carefully selected for survivability.

desc.cn:
受蚀玉化叶的根茎，可以用于培养全新的个体。
受蚀玉化叶可在干员技能专精时使用。
desc.en:
A Blighted Jadeleaf tuber that can be cultivated into a new adult plant. 
Blighted Jadeleaf can be used for operator skill mastery.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的岩天使叶，其根茎的成活性较强。
decoDesc.en: A False Aggela tuber carefully selected for survivability.

desc.cn:
岩天使叶的根茎，可以用于培养全新的个体。
岩天使叶可在干员技能专精时使用。
desc.en:
A False Aggela tuber that can be cultivated into a new adult plant. 
False Aggela can be used for operator skill mastery.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 锦草又称锦星草，因其春夏之际星星点点长于山阴处而获此名。
decoDesc.en: The jincao plant is commonly known as the "silkstar grass", named after the star-like flowers of the plant. The plant usually grows on shaded hillslopes.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集或在工厂培育出的植物，粉碎后可用于食品或其他材料合成。
desc.en: A plant that can be gathered from the wilderness or planted in the AIC. Shred it to make food or materials for other products.

decoDesc.cn: 芽针是武陵生存能力最强的草本植物，会在盛夏时节开放出极其绚丽的花朵。
decoDesc.en: The yazhen plant is an extremely hardy grass native to the Wuling region. The plant produces a rather beautiful bloom during summer.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集或在工厂培育出的花朵，粉碎后可用于药品或其他材料合成。
desc.en: A flowering plant that can be gathered from the wilderness or planted in the AIC. Shred it to make medication or materials for other products.

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，锦草粉末需要溶解并灌装后才能使用。
decoDesc.en: Jincao plant can be shredded to a powder form. This must then be dissolved and packaged in a container for easier use.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，芽针粉末需要溶解并灌装后才能使用。
decoDesc.en: Yazhen plant can be shredded to a powder form. This must then be dissolved and packaged in a container for easier use.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 开拓区的幼童们大多喜欢将锦草的叶片折叠起来放在唇边，不起眼的草叶能演奏出兽吼般的声响。
decoDesc.en: Children in the frontier enjoy blowing two jincao leaves placed together to give off a sound that resembles a roaring beast.

desc.cn: 锦草的种子，通过采种获得，可辅以大量清水培育锦草。
desc.en: Seeds picked from the Jincao plant with the Seed-Picking Unit. Cultivate them with Clean Water to raise Jincao.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 芽针会利用自己的“尖刺”，将种子挂在周边小型动物身上传播到远处。
decoDesc.en: Yazhen seeds have tiny hooks that aid in their attachment to animal fur for dispersion.

desc.cn: 芽针的种子，通过采种获得，可辅以大量清水培育芽针。
desc.en: Seeds picked from the Yazhen plant with the Seed-Picking Unit. Cultivate them with Clean Water to raise Yazhen.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 部分武陵住民相信，锦草象征着蓬勃的生命力，他们会将这一意象写入文章中。
decoDesc.en: Some people in Wuling believe that the jincao plant symbolizes hardiness. Many pieces of local literature use the plant as a metaphor for toughness and survival.

desc.cn: 只能在野外采集的特殊植物，粉碎后可用于食品或其他材料合成。
desc.en: A special plant that only grows in the wild. Shred it to acquire materials for making food or other products.

decoDesc.cn: 芽针也可以作为钓鳞道具，几枚芽针叶片稍加弯折改造就能构成一个实用吊钩。
decoDesc.en: The thorny leaves of the yazhen plant can be used for angling. A few simple steps and bending would create a very effective angling hook.

desc.cn: 只能在野外采集的特殊植物，粉碎后可用于食品或其他材料合成。
desc.en: A special plant that only grows in the wild. Shred it to acquire materials for making food or other products.

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，锦草粉末需要溶解并灌装后才能使用。
decoDesc.en: Jincao plant can be shredded to a powder form. This must then be dissolved and packaged in a container for easier use.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，芽针粉末需要溶解并灌装后才能使用。
decoDesc.en: Yazhen plant can be shredded to a powder form. This must then be dissolved and packaged in a container for easier use.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 战争初期，一支宏山侦察队首先发现了这种色彩艳丽的植物，并在紧急状况下将其作为止血药物使用。
decoDesc.en: When the War just began, a Hongshan recon team discovered a plant with brightly colored flowers. Extracts of this plant can be used as an anti-hemorrhagic agent.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集或在工厂培育出的艳丽花朵，粉碎后可用于药品或其他材料合成。
desc.en: A plant with brightly colored flowers that can be gathered from the wilderness or planted in the AIC. Shred it to make medication or materials for other products.

decoDesc.cn: 塔卫二的柑橘属植物主要起源于大陆中部地区，传播至文明环带的品种大多具有果实大，果肉韧性高等特点。
decoDesc.en: Citromes are part of the botanical genus of Zitros that usually grows in the central continental region of Talos-II. The species and cultivars grown in the Civilization Band tend to yield large fruits with tough, fibrous flesh.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集或在工厂培育出的果实，粉碎后可用于食品或其他材料合成。
desc.en: A fruit  that can be gathered from the wilderness or planted in the AIC. Shred it to make food or materials for other products.

decoDesc.cn: 众生长地是“荒地手工业”领域中的翘楚，他们善于使用各种天然材料在艰苦环境中生存。
decoDesc.en: The Hannabit Circuit proved themselves as the true masters of wilderness crafting and would use all sorts of natural materials to aid in their crafting.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集或在工厂培育出的叶片粗粝的植物，粉碎后可用于精细研磨。
desc.en: A plant with extremely rough leaves that can be gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the AIC. Shred it to get a powdered preparation usable in industrial grinding.

decoDesc.cn: 在协议技术介入下，经过精细研磨后，荞花提取物表现出了“异常”活性。
decoDesc.en: Techno-Protocol grinding is used to make this buckflower preparation with "strangely" improved pharmaceutical activity.

desc.cn: 荞花粉末研磨后的细粉，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Acquired by grinding Buckflower Powder. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在协议技术介入下，经过精细研磨后，细磨柑实粉末的味道极度苦涩。
decoDesc.en: Techno-Protocol grinding is used to make this Citrome preparation with an extremely bitter taste.

desc.cn: 柑实粉末研磨后的细粉，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Acquired by grinding Citrome Powder. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，荞花的药性得到了充分释放。
decoDesc.en: Shredding would greatly improve the pharmaceutical effectiveness of Buckflower.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，柑实的风味得到了充分展现。
decoDesc.en: Shredding would greatly improve the flavors of Citrome.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，砂叶中粗粝的部分得到了充分利用。
decoDesc.en: Shredding releases the abrasive grit from sandleaf tissues for industrial use.

desc.cn: 砂叶粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Powdered Sandleaf. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 获得砂叶后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 荞花最初被发现于一处天然石拱下，因此也曾被称作“桥花”。
decoDesc.en: The Buckflower earned its name as it was first found under a natural arch that resembled a bucking, jumping beast.

desc.cn: 荞花的种子，可用于培育荞花。
desc.en: Seeds picked from the Buckflower plant. Cultivate them to raise Buckflowers.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 文明环带的植物爱好者曾评选出“荒野上最常见的植物”，荞花、柑实位处排行榜前十。
decoDesc.en: Hobby botanists and gardeners of the Civilization Band once voted for the Most Common Plants in the Wildlands. Buckflowers and Citromes both made it to the top 10 of the list.

desc.cn: 柑实的种子，可用于培育柑实。
desc.en: Seeds picked from the Citrome plant. Cultivate them to raise Citromes.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: “荒地手工业”的发展历史最早可以追溯到近百年前。为了活下来，流落在荒地上的人类必须用尽一切手段。
decoDesc.en: The history of wilderness crafting can be traced back nearly a century ago. People forced to live in the wildlands had to do everything they could to survive.

desc.cn: 砂叶的种子，可用于培育砂叶。
desc.en: Seeds picked from the Sandleaf plant. Cultivate them to raise Sandleaves.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 四月中旬正是荞花盛放之时，其中色彩最为炽烈者，会被冠以“映火”之名。
decoDesc.en: Buckflowers bloom in mid-April. Plants with the most fiery-red flowers would be called Firebuckles.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集的特殊艳丽花朵，可用于治疗或精制食药，无法获取种子。
desc.en: A plant with extremely brightly colored flowers that grows in the wild. Can be used for treatment and the making of fine food and medicine (Fine F&M). Firebuckles do not provide seeds.

decoDesc.cn: 实际上，依照汁水程度及含糖量，出现在文明环带市场中的柑实可以被细分为十二种品类。
decoDesc.en: Around 12 major Citrome cultivars are currently sold in the markets of the Civilization Band. They come in all sorts of names and offer different juiciness and sugar content. However, they are all Citromes.

desc.cn: 可在野外采集的特殊果实，可用于治疗或精制食药，无法获取种子。
desc.en: A plant with special fruits that grows in the wild. Can be used for treatment and the making of fine food and medicine (Fine F&M). Umbralines do not provide seeds.

decoDesc.cn: 简单调制的映火荞花药粉。应急使用问题不大，但属实有些浪费药性。
decoDesc.en: A simple powdered preparation of Firebuckle. You can use it to treat wounds, but its pharmaceutical potential goes way beyond that.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 简单调配成的综合冲剂，运气不好的话会喝到些许果皮残渣。
decoDesc.en: A simple blended preparation that can be consumed by mixing with some water. If you're unlucky, you might get some bitter bits of rind in your pack.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 当红柱状菌生长到一定阶段，颜色到达一定深度后，它会拥有极高的毒性。
decoDesc.en: Toxicity of the ruby bolete would already be extremely high when the sporocarp reaches a certain size and starts acquiring a reddish hue. This is the pink stage.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊菌类。
可在干员20级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A special fungus gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Promotes Lv.20 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 红柱状菌中红色越深的个体，其提取物作为药物的价值越高。
decoDesc.en: Ruby boletes with darker hues provide extracts with greater pharmaceutical values. This is the red stage.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊菌类。
可在干员40级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A special fungus gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Promotes Lv.40 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 每年因误判红柱状菌生长阶段，误食之而导致多器官衰竭的荒地开拓者数不胜数。
decoDesc.en: Every year, many pioneers suffer multiple organ failure caused by ruby bolete poisoning. This often results from misjudging the edible stage of the fungus. Eating the fungus in ruby stage is extremely dangerous.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊菌类。
可在干员60级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A special fungus gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Promotes Lv.60 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 血菌疑似是某类食肉真菌受侵蚀环境影响后产生的变种，它以吞食得来的生命力就流淌于它的菌丝之中。
decoDesc.en: Bloodcap is likely to be a variant of a carnivorous fungus mutated by ambient Blight. Nutrients consumed by the fungus would course through its mycelia.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊菌类。
可在干员80级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A special fungus gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Promotes Lv.80 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 星门故障后才多见于塔卫二各处的菌类，被携带至塔卫二的泰拉羽兽们对这种意外坚硬的“本土蘑菇”情有独钟，孢子们因此得以躲藏在长羽之间行向各处。
decoDesc.en: A common fungus that proliferated in various regions of Talos-II after the Cosmic Gate broke down. Terran fowlbeasts brought to the new world exhibit a special preference for these surprisingly hard "local mushrooms". Cosmagaric also disperse their spores by attaching them to the long feathers of the fowls.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊菌类。
可在干员80级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A special fungus gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Promotes Lv.80 operators.

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的轻红柱状菌，其菌块活性十足。
decoDesc.en: A Pink Bolete mycelial mass carefully selected for its activity.

desc.cn:
轻红柱状菌的菌块，可以用于培养全新的个体。
轻红柱状菌可在干员20级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A Pink Bolete mycelial mass that can be cultivated into a new adult fungus. 
Pink Boletes can promote Lv.20 operators.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的中红柱状菌，其菌块活性十足。
decoDesc.en: A Red Bolete mycelial mass carefully selected for its activity.

desc.cn:
中红柱状菌的菌块，可以用于培养全新的个体。
中红柱状菌可在干员40级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A Red Bolete mycelial mass that can be cultivated into a new adult fungus. 
Red Boletes can promote Lv.40 operators.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的重红柱状菌，其菌块活性十足。
decoDesc.en: A Ruby Bolete mycelial mass carefully selected for its activity.

desc.cn:
重红柱状菌的菌块，可以用于培养全新的个体。
重红柱状菌可在干员60级晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A Ruby Bolete mycelial mass that can be cultivated into a new adult fungus. 
Red Boletes can promote Lv.60 operators.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的血菌，其菌块活性十足。
decoDesc.en: A Bloodcap mycelial mass carefully selected for its activity.

desc.cn:
血菌的菌块，可以用于培养全新的个体。
血菌可在部分干员80级及以上晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A Bloodcap mycelial mass that can be cultivated into a new adult fungus. 
Bloodcaps can promote certain Lv.80 or higher operators.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的星门菌，其菌块活性十足。
decoDesc.en: A Cosmagaric mycelial mass carefully selected for its activity.

desc.cn:
星门菌的菌块，可以用于培养全新的个体。
星门菌可在部分干员80级及以上晋升时使用。
desc.en:
A Cosmagaric mycelial mass that can be cultivated into a new adult fungus. 
Cosmagarics can promote certain Lv.80 or higher operators.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

decoDesc.cn: 生长于四号谷地的一种罕见真菌，可以在制备药剂时起到催化的作用。工团研究员林奈最早发现它的这一功效。
decoDesc.en: A rare fungus that grows in Valley IV. It can be used as a catalyst when making medication. UWST scientist Linnaeus was the first to discover this property.

desc.cn: 工团研究员林奈制备药剂所需的稀有真菌。
desc.en: A rare fungus that UWST scientist Linnaeus needs for his pharmaceutical preparation.

decoDesc.cn: 灰芦麦易于种植，产量较足，是开拓区民众的主粮。
decoDesc.en: Reed Rye is a hardy cereal with an impressive yield. It is the staple food of most settlers in the frontier.

desc.cn: 通过精细种植才能培育的作物，可直接用于珍贵食药的制作。
desc.en: This crop can only be grown with fine cultivation. Can be directly used in making quality food and pharmaceuticals.

decoDesc.cn: 这种植物的叶片被评为“开拓区味道最苦的药物”。
decoDesc.en: The leaves of this plant are considered the "most bitter herbs of the frontier".

desc.cn: 通过精细种植才能培育的作物，可直接用于珍贵食药的制作。
desc.en: This crop can only be grown with fine cultivation. Can be directly used in making quality food and pharmaceuticals.

decoDesc.cn: 琼叶参药性温良平和，常被宏山人当作温补自身的药材使用。
decoDesc.en: Redjade Ginseng is a mild herb often consumed by people in Hongshan as a fortifying supplement.

desc.cn: 通过精细种植才能培育的作物，可直接用于珍贵食药的制作。
desc.en: This crop can only be grown with fine cultivation. Can be directly used in making quality food and pharmaceuticals.

decoDesc.cn: 金石稻因其圆润的种实、玉石般的质地又被称作“金石晶珠”。
decoDesc.en: The rounded, jade-like endosperm of the Amber Rice is also regarded as "amber pearls".

desc.cn: 通过精细种植才能培育的作物，可直接用于珍贵食药的制作。
desc.en: This crop can only be grown with fine cultivation. Can be directly used in making quality food and pharmaceuticals.

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的灰芦麦，其种子饱满完整，活力较高。
decoDesc.en: Reed Rye seeds carefully selected for their generous size and vitality.

desc.cn: 野生灰芦麦的种子，通过调制成田块并进行精细化培育，可产出灰芦麦。
desc.en: Seeds picked from wild Reed Rye. Cultivate them with crafted farm plots to raise Reed Rye.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的苦叶椒，其种子饱满完整，活力较高。
decoDesc.en: Tartpepper seeds carefully selected for their generous size and vitality.

desc.cn: 野生苦叶椒的种子，通过调制成田块并进行精细化培育，可产出苦叶椒。
desc.en: Seeds picked from wild Tartpepper. Cultivate them with crafted farm plots to raise Tartpepper.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的琼叶参，其种子饱满完整，活力较高。
decoDesc.en: Redjade Ginseng seeds carefully selected for their generous size and vitality.

desc.cn: 野生琼叶参的种子，通过调制成田块并进行精细化培育，可产出琼叶参。
desc.en: Seeds picked from wild Redjade Ginseng. Cultivate them with crafted farm plots to raise Redjade Ginseng.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的金石稻，其种子饱满完整，活力较高。
decoDesc.en: Amber Rice seeds carefully selected for their generous size and vitality.

desc.cn: 野生金石稻的种子，通过调制成田块并进行精细化培育，可产出金石稻。
desc.en: Seeds picked from wild Amber Rice. Cultivate them with crafted farm plots to raise Amber Rice.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 黯石又被称为“古老之石”，它象征着一段人类从未见证过的消亡。
decoDesc.en: Nyxites are also known as the "ancient mineral" and symbolize an age of destruction of such a scale never witnessed by humanity. They come in various hues.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊矿物。
可在武器20级突破强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special mineral gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Tunes Lv.20 weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 人类目前尚不了解黯石这类矿石的生成过程，塔卫二始终没有完全揭开自己的面纱。
decoDesc.en: Humans have yet to figure out how nyxites form. This secret of Talos-II has yet to unveil itself.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊矿物。
可在武器40级突破强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special mineral gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Tunes Lv.40 weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 人类对黯石的命名中以轻、中、重为标准所区分的，实际上是黯石的氧化率。
decoDesc.en: People usually name nyxite crystals based on their color (Kalkonyx, Auronyx, and Umbronyx) but these differences are just caused by the extent of oxidation.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊矿物。
可在武器60级突破强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special mineral gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Tunes Lv.60 weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 研究者推测，燎石是受火山喷发等特殊情况影响的黯石再受侵蚀后形成的特殊矿石。
decoDesc.en: Scientists postulate that Igneosites are metamorphic forms of nyxite subject to volcanic eruptions followed by Blight exposure.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊矿物。
可在武器80级突破强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special mineral gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Tunes Lv.80 weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 因极复杂的水脉变迁才会产生的矿石，最初由宏山天师在勘探武陵水文环境时发现。在特殊深度环境中，随水而来的石砂会因超域能量融于一处，成为大河的年轮。
decoDesc.en: A mineral formation created by extremely complex hydrological changes. Wulingstone was first discovered by Hongshan Tianshi conducting hydrological surveys at the Wuling region. Under the influence of Æther, sediments carried by water would settle at certain depths and eventually form Wulingstone. These rocks are useful in fluviochronology and the study of local hydrological history.

desc.cn:
采集自野外或培养舱培养的特殊矿物。
可在武器80级突破强化时使用。
desc.en:
A special mineral gathered from the wilderness or cultivated in the Growth Chamber. 
Tunes Lv.80 weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 经严格筛选的轻黯石，其子簇具备特殊的培植价值。
decoDesc.en: A Kalkonyx seeding cluster selected for its usefulness in crystal nucleation.

desc.cn:
轻黯石的子簇，可以用于培养全新的个体。
轻黯石可在武器20级突破强化时使用。
desc.en:
A seeding cluster of Kalkonyx that can be used to grow a new crystal. 
Kalkonyxes can tune Lv.20 weapons.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 解锁帝江号并建造对应舱室后生产
noObtainWayHint.en: Dijiang Production (unlock and build cabin first)

desc.en: Leftover plant matter from the seed-picking process. Can be refined and turned into Carbon.

decoDesc.cn: 受源石感染的塔卫二生物，身形极小，但能够发出光芒。
decoDesc.en: A Talosian creature affected by Originium. These little bugs can give off a gentle glow.

desc.cn: 一种微型会飞的萤壳源石虫，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A small flying Originium bug. Can be used to produce other materials.

decoDesc.cn: 受源石感染的塔卫二生物，身形极小，但能够发出光芒。用手触摸它时能直观感受到热度。
decoDesc.en: A Talosian creature affected by Originium. These little bugs can glow and give off a bit of heat.

desc.cn: 一种微型会飞的高能源石虫，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A small flying Originium bug with high energy content. Can be used to produce other materials.

decoDesc.cn: 萤壳虫的外壳在受粉碎处理时仍会发出微光。
decoDesc.en: The powdered exoskeleton of Glowbugs can still give off a gentle glow.

desc.cn: 萤壳虫研磨而成的粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Powdered preparation of Glowbugs. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 灼壳虫的外壳在受粉碎处理时仍会发出微光，对其进行加工时，需随时注意设备温度。
decoDesc.en: The powdered exoskeleton of Scorchbugs can still give off a gentle glow. NOTE: Monitor facility temperature during processing.

desc.cn: 灼壳虫研磨而成的粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Powdered preparation of Scorchbugs. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 总之，先砍树吧。
decoDesc.en: Let's chop down some trees first.

desc.cn: 在野外可采集的普通木材，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Common wood that can be gathered in the Mossfield region. Can be used to produce other materials.

decoDesc.cn: 装配了压缩源石榴弹的抛射装置，在设计上参考了曾服役于对抗天使战争的小型火炮。
decoDesc.en: A launcher of compressed Originium grenades. Designs are based on small field guns used during the Aggeloi War.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>981 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>3秒 攻击方式：以抛物线发射榴弹攻击敌人，榴弹会在敌人附近地面爆炸并造成范围<@ba.fire>灼热伤害。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>981 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>3s Mode of Attack: Launches grenades in a ballistic trajectory. The grenades detonate above ground near enemies and deal area of effect <@ba.fire>Heat DMG.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 装配了压缩高爆源石榴弹的抛射装置，相较于普通榴弹塔拥有了更高的范围性杀伤能力。
decoDesc.en: A launcher of compressed high explosive (HE) Originium grenades. This facility deals more devastating area damage compared to its standard counterpart.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>5585 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>3秒 攻击方式：以抛物线发射Ⅱ级榴弹攻击敌人，榴弹会在敌人附近地面爆炸并造成范围<@ba.fire>灼热伤害，同时在地面留下一片燃烧区域对敌人造成伤害。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>5585 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>3s Mode of Attack: Attacks enemies by launching Mk Ⅱ grenades along a ballistic trajectory that detonate above ground near enemies. The grenade explosion deals area of effect <@ba.fire>Heat DMG and leaves a burning zone that deals DMG to enemies within it.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 内置了特殊施术单元的混合型设备，能通过毒性物质有效阻拦敌人的攻势。据说，其储液罐内部装填的是一种特殊胶水。因设计失败而拥有的腐蚀性，反倒让这种胶水成为了武器。
decoDesc.en: A multi-purpose facility furnished with a special Arts Unit that uses poisonous materials to effectively halt an enemy offensive. They say the storage tank is filled with a special adhesive with a faulty formula that made it highly corrosive instead. However, this "failed" adhesive found new purpose as a weapon instead.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>5485 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>5秒 攻击方式：发射特制毒雾弹，毒雾弹会在敌人附近地面爆炸并造成范围<@ba.natur>自然伤害，同时在地面留下一片毒雾区，对敌人造成伤害并降低移动速度。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>5485 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>5s Mode of Attack: Launches special mist grenades that detonate above ground near enemies. The mist grenade explosion deals area of effect <@ba.natur>Nature DMG and leaves a mist zone that deals DMG and slows the movement speed of enemies within it.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 灌装了封装液氮的实验型设备，其内部的液氮被封存在一种特殊晶体中，装有液氮的晶体会在敌人身上碎裂，在冻伤目标的同时阻碍他们的行动。
decoDesc.en: An experimental weapon with ammo of special crystal rounds filled with liquid nitrogen (LN). The ammo would shatter upon impact, spilling its freezing contents onto the enemy to apply frostbite that impedes their movements.

desc.cn: 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>5秒 攻击方式：发射特殊液氮晶体，晶体爆裂后会降低范围内敌人的移动速度。
desc.en: Attack Interval: <@ba.key>5s Mode of Attack: Fires special liquid nitrogen (LN) crystals that shatter upon impact to slow the movement speed of enemies in the area of effect.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 搭载了能源转化装置的实验型攻击设备，可以理解为是某种城防巨炮的小型变种，因其消耗能量过高，易发生应用风险而不太受市场欢迎。
decoDesc.en: An experimental weapon armed with an energy converter. Treat this as a miniaturized version of a city-defense giga-cannon. The system is unpopular in the arms market due to its steep energy demands and the fact that it is an unstable and risky weapon platform.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>22338 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>8秒 攻击方式：消耗大量充能向目标发射射线，对敌人造成高额<@ba.pulse>电磁伤害。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>22338 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>8s Mode of Attack: Consumes vast amounts of energy to emit a beam that deals massive <@ba.pulse>Electric DMG to enemies.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 电涌塔参考了多种与“电”相关的源石技艺，在增加输出功率的同时极大降低了误伤风险。
decoDesc.en: Years of research on electricity-related Originium Arts gave rise to the Surge Tower. Power output has been greatly increased while minimizing the risk of friendly fire.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>4886 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>3秒 攻击方式：释放电能攻击敌人，攻击会弹射到附近敌人（至多2次），造成<@ba.pulse>电磁伤害。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>4886 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>3s Mode of Attack: Releases electrical arcs that attack enemies. The arc also chains to nearby enemies (up to 2) and deals <@ba.pulse>Electric DMG.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 内置了医疗用施术单元的治疗设备，设计师专门为医疗塔做了球形外观，在伤者眼中，柔和的线条也可以称得上是一种慰藉。
decoDesc.en: A healing facility furnished with medical Arts casting units. The designers made the tower spherical because gentle curves are visually more comforting to the injured.

desc.cn: 最小治疗间隔：<@ba.key>5秒 可将充能转化为治疗量，治疗周围受伤的干员。
desc.en: Minimum HP Treatment Interval: <@ba.key>5s Converts electrical power into healing arts that can treat injured operators nearby.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 内置了特殊种类施术单元的干扰型设备，其发出的声波可以攻击目标的神经系统，使其眩晕。似乎是因为功率极大，这台设备连天使的行动都可以扰乱。
decoDesc.en: A crowd control facility furnished with a specialized Arts unit. It can emit targeted sonic waves that overwhelm an entity's nervous systems to stun them. The overwhelming power of the sonic waves seem to allow them to disrupt Aggeloid movements.

desc.cn: 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>5秒 攻击方式：发射一道震荡波，对范围内的普通敌人和进阶敌人施加<@ba.vdown>晕眩效果。
desc.en: Attack Interval: <@ba.key>5s Mode of Attack: Fires a shockwave that <@ba.vdown>stuns common and advanced enemies within the area of effect.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 灵感来源于天使的远程攻击设备，设计者为它加装了极度精密的光学识别模块，使其可以精准锁定高威胁敌人，并造成有效杀伤。
decoDesc.en: This weapon is inspired by the ranged weaponry of the Aggeloi. The designer has furnished it with high-precision optical recognition modules to accurately target high-threat targets and deal effective damage.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>11634 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>5秒 攻击方式：拥有较大攻击范围，优先锁定范围内威胁更高的敌人，对敌人造成高额<@ba.phy>物理伤害。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>11634 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>5s Mode of Attack: Unleashes long-range attacks that target high-threat enemies first and deal massive <@ba.phy>Physical DMG.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 将复杂铳械结构简化后，以自动化设计逻辑结合于一体的攻击设备，其原型机常被各小型开拓聚落用于阻挡危险野生动物。
decoDesc.en: Once the complex firing mechanism was simplified, it was combined with the logic of automation designs to create this integrated weapon platform. Many frontier outposts and villages used prototypes of this system to defend themselves against dangerous wildlife.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>609 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>2秒 攻击方式：持续发射能量弹，对敌人造成<@ba.phy>物理伤害。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>609 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>2s Mode of Attack: Continuously fires energy bolts that deal <@ba.phy>Physical DMG.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 铳械塔的升级版本，因其更高的杀伤能力而被人称为“坟墓挖掘器”。
decoDesc.en: An upgraded version of the Gun Tower. People call this the Tomb Digger due to its merciless killing power.

desc.cn: 攻击力：<@ba.key>2136 攻击间隔：<@ba.key>2秒 攻击方式：持续发射Ⅱ级能量弹，每第4次攻击会发射一次强力能量弹，对敌人造成<@ba.phy>物理伤害。
desc.en: ATK: <@ba.key>2136 Attack Interval: <@ba.key>2s Mode of Attack: Continuously fires Mk II energy bolts with every 4th shot being an empowered bolt. The bolts deal <@ba.phy>Physical DMG.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: “你确定这里面的东西真是管理员的？”
decoDesc.en: "Are you sure the things inside belong to the Endmin?"

desc.cn: 用于便捷存取仓库物品的设备。
desc.en: A facility that allows quick access of items in the Depot.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 车、铣、刨、磨。
decoDesc.en: Comes with grinding wheels, planing wheels, polishing bits, and milling cutters.

desc.cn: 能够加工各式零件的平台。
desc.en: A facility capable of processing various parts.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 在第一次听到拆解机故事的情况下，有百分之八十的听众不愿意相信这台能够精密作业的设备，其设计灵感居然会来自于工团用来锯切天使的大型拆解台。
decoDesc.en: Eighty percent of those who first heard the story of the separating unit simply refused to believe this fact: The design of this facility was inspired by large UWST disassembling stations for sawing and cutting apart Aggeloi carcasses.

desc.cn: 用于进行物理分拆的设备。
desc.en: A facility that physically disassembles various items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: “换个应用方法，多些产品销量。”
decoDesc.en: "Give me an alternative function. I need sales!"

desc.cn: 用于供给液体的设备。
desc.en: A facility for dispensing fluids.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 专利性的无菌分装技术极大程度上降低了产品发生污染现象的可能性。
decoDesc.en: The patented sterile packaging technology has greatly reduced the probability of product contamination.

desc.cn: 能够将原料灌装到容器的设备。
desc.en: A facility capable of filling containers with various materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 剥离、塑造……材料的形态将在高温中变换，直至焕然一新。
decoDesc.en: Crystal delamination and thermal moulding... Heat changes, transforms, and even enables reactions in various materials to create something new.

desc.cn: 使用高温精炼其他材料的设备。
desc.en: A facility that performs high temperature refining of various materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 有没有听到它嚼碎硬物的声音？
decoDesc.en: Can you hear the crunch of the heavy industrial shredders?

desc.cn: 能粉碎各种材料的重型设备。
desc.en: A heavy facility that shreds and pulverizes various materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 如何使设备在储存腐蚀性液体时，也能耐受外界侵蚀现象，这一问题困扰了工程师们近五年时间。
decoDesc.en: It took the engineers nearly 5 years to come up with a tank that can store corrosive fluids while being resistant against the effects of ambient Blight.

desc.cn: 存储液体的设备。
desc.en: A facility for storing fluids.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 根据集成工业系统第二次危险环境试验性投放后制定的升级要求，仓库存货口与仓库取货口的用料升级为了耐蚀钢材。
decoDesc.en: An upgrade plan was stipulated after the AIC Factory was deployed for a second time in a high-threat area. Blight-resistant steel was used to construct Depot Loaders and Depot Unloaders.

desc.cn: 可将物品运送至当地仓库的活动端口，只能贴靠仓库存取线放置。
desc.en: A placeable loading point that delivers goods from the AIC Factory to a local depot. The Depot Loader must be placed right next to the Depot Bus.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 在息壤与集成工业系统结合的设备中，息壤粒子主要起着“稳定”作用。一如对抗裂隙与侵蚀，于设备内流动的息壤粒子能保证物品在借助存取线出入仓库时不会因周边环境异常而受到干扰。
decoDesc.en: For facilities that incorporate Xiranite with AIC technology, the Xiranite particles mainly provide "stabilizing" effects against rifting or the Blight. Xiranite particles flowing within these facilities can ensure that the movement of goods in/out of the depot via loaders/unloaders would not be affected by local environmental anomalies.

desc.cn: 可以在集成核心区域放置的仓库存取线基段，需要和仓库存取线源桩或其他生效的仓库存取线基段相连，其上可贴靠仓库存货口和仓库取货口。
desc.en: A bus section that can be deployed in the Core AIC Area. The Depot Bus Section must be connected to a Depot Bus Port or other active Depot Bus Sections. Once active, Depot Loaders and Depot Unloaders can be attached to the Depot Bus.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 一些工程师偶尔会因息壤而产生自己都无法理解的疯狂念头。工业的终点是什么？像息壤这种“自由”的材料，是否有更进一步的可能？有朝一日，人类的工业技术是否能推进至“无形”的程度？他们如此想着，便会觉得自己走出的每一步都更为意义非凡。
decoDesc.en: For some engineers, Xiranite would often inspire crazy ideas that they themselves couldn't even explain. What is the endpoint of industry? Are there other possibilities for Xiranite, the material of unprecedented "freedom"? Will human industrial technology ever reach the "formless" state? The more the engineers think, the more they believe that every step they take is a revolutionary one.

desc.cn: 作为仓库存取线的起始点，可以在集成核心区域自由放置。
desc.en: The origin of the Depot Bus. The Depot Bus Port can be placed anywhere in the Core AIC Area.

decoDesc.cn: 帮助，欺骗，用双眼观看，用双手验证……在塔卫二的困境中，这正是“联系”的证明。
decoDesc.en: Assist or deceive. Observe with your eyes. Validate with your actions... This is the proof of our "links" as we face the challenges of Talos-II together.

desc.cn: 用于留下标记信息的设备。
desc.en: A facility that can be used to post and leave beacon memos.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 该款设备是终末地工业对外销售的主力产品。
decoDesc.en: The best selling product of Endfield Industries.

desc.cn: 用来开采源矿的机械设备，可使用源石完成自供能，不需要通电就可以运作。
desc.en: A mining rig for digging up Originium Ore. This rig does not need to be connected to the power grid to work as it powers itself using the Originium it mines.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作

decoDesc.cn: 因各项数据过于平均，该款设备在开拓区的销量并不算好。
decoDesc.en: Market performance for this facility was mediocre due to its equally mediocre stats.

desc.cn: 在通电状态下，可以用来开采源矿、紫晶矿的机械设备。
desc.en: Requires power. This mining rig can mine Originium Ore and Amethyst Ore.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 二型电驱矿机重点升级了刀头组件的强度，具备了更强的环境适应性和在更深矿层作业的能力。
decoDesc.en: The Mk II upgrade of the electric mining rig features improved drill bit hardness, improved performance in rugged environment, and deeper mining capabilities.

desc.cn: 在通电状态下，可以用来开采蓝铁矿等多种矿物的机械设备。
desc.en: Must be connected to the power grid with adequate power to work. This mining rig can mine Ferrium Ore and other minerals.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业最终选择向工团订购一批产自塔卫二南部的特种钢材，以求应对反应设备产生的腐蚀性故障。
decoDesc.en: After multiple incidents of reactor failures caused by material fatigue and corrosion, Endfield finally decided to approach UWST and purchase a batch of special steel from southern Talos-II.

desc.cn: 进行固液体化学反应的设备。
desc.en: A facility for running solid or liquid-state chemical reactions.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 该款由终末地工业自研的设备，最大技术优势在于对内部光照、温度以及植物激素状态的实时监控与调整。
decoDesc.en: This facility is designed entirely by Endfield Industries. Its cutting edge technologies include real-time monitoring and modulation of silo lighting, temperature, and plant hormone levels.

desc.cn: 能够培育各类普通植物的仓形设备。
desc.en: A cultivating silo for growing various common plants and crops.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: “无线供电”是终末地工业最大的技术突破，这项技术基于协议技术进行了拓展，是整套集成工业系统的运转基础。
decoDesc.en: Wireless electrical connection is one of the biggest technological breakthroughs achieved by Endfield Industries. This tech was further improved with Techno-Protocol to provide the very foundation of the AIC Factory.

desc.cn:
通电后可给较大范围内的终末地设备无线供电。
完成后续工业计划研发后可进行30m内短距离电力运输。
desc.en:
Once connected to the power grid, this pylon can wirelessly power all Endfield facilities within a sizable area of effect.
Researching certain AIC Factory Plan technologies also gives this facility a 30-meter power transmission capability.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 装配了息壤接收模块的协议供电桩。对于在中继器间飞奔的电流来说，息壤接收模块就像黑暗中的灯塔，能够精准地牵引着它以极低的损耗率走向供电桩。
decoDesc.en: A Techno-Protocol Electric Pylon furnished with a Xiranite receiving module. For electrical currents coursing between the relays, such modules serve as beacons in the darkness that accurately guide them towards their destination pylons with extremely low transmission loss.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域外可自动连接协议核心与息壤中继器（80m内）、息壤供电桩以及其他电力设备（30m内），但无法连接核心区域内的其他电力设备。在集成核心区域内仅会自动连接协议核心。可进行范围供电与短距离电力传输。
desc.en: When outside the Core AIC Area, this facility auto-connects to the PAC and Xiranite Relays within an 80-meter radius; and to Xiranite Pylons and other power facilities within a 30-meter radius. However, it cannot connect to other power facilities within the Core AIC Area. When inside the Core AIC Area, it only auto-connects to the PAC. This facility can be used for powering facilities within range and power transmission across short distances.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 中继器是集成工业系统中成本最高的设备之一，它的整体设计思路更趋近于协议核心。
decoDesc.en: The Relay Tower is one of the most expensive AIC facilities to construct. Its overall design is based on the PAC.

desc.cn:
可以在80m范围内完成电力配给的中继设备，只能进行电力传输。
完成后续工业计划研发后可给小范围内的终末地设备无线供电。
desc.en:
This relay can be used to transmit power to other facilities within an 80-meter radius.
Researching certain AIC Factory Plan technologies also lets it supply power to other Endfield facilities within a small area.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 将息壤技术与协议供电技术结合后诞生出的电力中继装置。其中息壤部分起到了识别、定位、稳定三项作用，保证了设备间不会出现胡乱连接的现象，极大降低了发生烧毁事故的可能性。
decoDesc.en: An electrical relay that combines Xiranite and Techno-Protocol electrical infrastructure technologies. The Xiranite components perform three major functions of identification, positioning, and stabilization. This avoids connection gridlocks between facilities and greatly minimizes the risk of accidental fires.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域外可自动连接协议核心与全部息壤电力设备（80m内），但无法连接核心区域内的其他电力设备。在集成核心区域内仅会自动连接协议核心。可进行电力传输与小范围供电。
desc.en: When outside the Core AIC Area, this facility auto-connects to the PAC and any Xiranite power facilities within an 80-meter radius. However, it cannot connect to other power facilities within the Core AIC Area. When inside the Core AIC Area, it only auto-connects to the PAC. This facility can be used for power transmission and powering facilities within a short range.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业最初设置的供电终端位于北极无人区，它已在那片人烟灭绝的冻土上伫立了近百年。
decoDesc.en: The very first Endfield Industries Electric Nexus was placed in the Northern Barrens. It had stood on that uninhabited permafrost for nearly a century.

desc.cn: 作为电路末端的终端设备，可接入电网为其他场所供电。
desc.en: Electric Nexuses are usually placed at the end of power transmission lines. Connect them to the power grid to supply power to nearby facilities.

desc.cn: 利用源矿或电池提供电能的设备，只有接入电网才能生效。
desc.en: The Thermal Bank is a facility that converts Originium Ore or batteries into electrical power. It must be connected to the power grid to work.

decoDesc.cn: 协议核心是终末地工业的绝对技术核心。以跨过那扇门为起始的积累，正悄然生长为参天巨树。
decoDesc.en: The Protocol PAC (PAC) represents the core technology of Endfield Industries. The seed was planted when they stepped through the door, and it is slowly growing to become a massive technological oak.

desc.cn: 可进行能量利用的大型终末地核心设备。
desc.en: A massive Endfield core facility that can supply power to various facilities and industrial processes.

decoDesc.cn: 点与点连接成线，这是集成工业系统铺向无人之地的第一步。
decoDesc.en: The AIC Factory shall connect one node to the next in order to expand into the uninhabited frontiers.

desc.cn: 可进行能量利用的附属次级核心设备，需要通过电网与协议核心连接才能正常工作。
desc.en: A secondary core facility that can supply power to various facilities and industrial processes. It must have an electrical connection to the main PAC to function.

decoDesc.cn: 在宏山科学院突破净水技术壁垒前，塔卫二地下水资源侵蚀污染问题困扰了人类许久。
decoDesc.en: Blight pollution of aquifers was a problem that plagued Talosians for years until Hongshan Academy of Sciences provided the definitive water treatment solution.

desc.cn: 向固定位置喷洒液体的设备。
desc.en: A facility that sprays fluids at a fixed direction.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 为了实现小范围内小型物品的协议转移功能，终末地工业花费了近十年时间。
decoDesc.en: It took Endfield engineers nearly a decade to achieve tele-protocol of small items within limited range.

desc.cn: 拥有多个容纳格的储物设备，由于在通电状态下可将其中物品转移至仓库，因此多用于产线末端。
desc.en: A storage facility with several item storage slots. Once connected to the power grid and given enough power, it can teleport items to the Depot. Hence, the stash is often placed at the end of production lines.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 本设备脱胎于某种历史悠长的炎国农产品加工机械。
decoDesc.en: This facility was based on a traditional crop processing machinery from Yan.

desc.cn: 可以对粉末材料进行细致研磨处理的设备。
desc.en: A facility that performs fine grinding of powdered materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 塔卫二各地曾诞生过诸多形制各异的电池，在人类摆脱战争困局后，这些产品的生产标准逐渐获得了统一。
decoDesc.en: All sorts of batteries had been made in various regions of Talos-II. When the war finally ended, humanity gradually established unified standards and specifications for battery production.

desc.cn: 用于封装部分能量元件的设备。
desc.en: A facility for packaging certain power components.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 滑索类设备最初被用于跨越北极无人区复杂的雪山侵蚀地貌，在人类昔日越过天使封锁线的行动中，它居功至伟。
decoDesc.en: The earliest ziplines of Talos-II were constructed to help traverse the precipitous Blighted regions of the uninhabited snowy mountains in the Northern Barrens. Ziplines were the leading technology that helped humanity defeat the Aggeloid Blockade.

desc.cn: 可在80m范围内相连，架起索道的小型设备。
desc.en: A small zipline facility that can be connected to another zipline facility within an 80-meter radius to create a zipline.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 最近，滑索类设备已经开始走入旅游从业者与极限运动爱好者的视线，这足见终末地工业相关人员的销售能力。
decoDesc.en: Recently, ziplines became a growing fad in the tourism sector as well as extreme sports athletes. The Endfield marketing team really demonstrated their skills in this case.

desc.cn: 可在110m范围内相连，架起索道的大型设备。
desc.en: A large zipline facility that can be connected to another zipline facility within a 110-meter radius to create a zipline.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 滑索类设备最初被用于跨越北极无人区复杂的雪山侵蚀地貌，在人类昔日越过天使封锁线的行动中，它居功至伟。
decoDesc.en: The earliest ziplines of Talos-II were constructed to help traverse the precipitous Blighted regions of the uninhabited snowy mountains in the Northern Barrens. Ziplines were the leading technology that helped humanity defeat the Aggeloid Blockade.

desc.cn: 可在80m范围内相连，架起索道的小型设备。
desc.en: A small zipline facility that can be connected to another zipline facility within an 80-meter radius to create a zipline.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 在极端环境下，仓库存货口和仓库取货口会与运载设备直接接合，以满足包括无菌、耐蚀在内的各项需求。
decoDesc.en: In extreme environments, the Depot Loaders and Depot Unloaders can be directly connected to the facilities to ensure germ-free and low Blight transportation.

desc.cn: 可选择物品从当地仓库取出的活动端口，只能贴靠仓库存取线放置。
desc.en: A placeable unloading point that transfers goods from a local depot into the AIC Factory. The Depot Unloader must be placed right next to the Depot Bus.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 一件足够优秀的装备原件，需要经历压嵌、编织等多道工序。
decoDesc.en: A top-tier piece of equipment must undergo multiple processing steps that include textile weaving and compression lamination of various fabric and lining.

desc.cn: 能够将不同材料嵌合加工成装备原件的设备。
desc.en: A facility that laminates different materials together to create gear components.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成基础工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Basic AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 地生五金。
decoDesc.en: The land is a cradle of wealth.

desc.cn: 用于息壤相关产物合成的设备。
desc.en: A facility for making Xiranite-based products.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵工业计划对应研究后制作
noObtainWayHint.en: Production: Requires Specified Wuling AIC Plan Tech

decoDesc.cn: 击败危险敌人掉落的活性化物质，可以用于调整武器，强化特殊武器性能。此样品为浑浊级。
decoDesc.en: A reactive material dropped by dangerous enemies. Can be used for weapon activation and performance boosting. This sample is rated as turbid.

desc.cn: 可以注入到武器内，提升武器技能等级。
desc.en: Infuse this into a weapon to improve its skill level.

decoDesc.cn: 该产品外壳破碎导致内容物泄露会威胁到人体健康，请谨慎使用。
decoDesc.en: Use and handle with care. Contents are hazardous to health. Compromising casing integrity may cause the said contents to leak.

desc.cn: 通过设备封装获得的电池，可用于发电、设备充能或与据点进行交易。
desc.en: A battery packaged by AIC Factory facilities. It can be used to supply power, charge up facilities, or traded at various outposts.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: “能工巧匠”在必要时能够将中容电池改造为爆破性武器。
decoDesc.en: A skilled artisan can easily convert a standard capacity (SC) battery into an improvised explosive weapon.

desc.cn: 通过设备封装获得的电池，可用于发电、设备充能或与据点进行交易。
desc.en: A battery packaged by AIC Factory facilities. It can be used to supply power, charge up facilities, or traded at various outposts.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 回收废弃电池是许多荒地居民的主业。
decoDesc.en: Many wildlands settlers make a living by stripping waste batteries of recyclable materials.

desc.cn: 通过设备封装获得的电池，可用于发电、设备充能或与据点进行交易。
desc.en: A battery packaged by AIC Factory facilities. It can be used to supply power, charge up facilities, or traded at various outposts.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: “息壤供能”是武陵与终末地工业重要的合作项目之一。
decoDesc.en: Xiranite Power is a key project jointly pursued by Wuling and Endfield Industries.

desc.cn: 通过设备封装获得的电池，可用于发电、设备充能或与据点进行交易。
desc.en: A battery packaged by AIC Factory facilities. It can be used to supply power, charge up facilities, or traded at various outposts.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 该物品爆炸风险较高，请谨慎携带及使用。
decoDesc.en: This is a dangerous explosive. Carry and use with care.

desc.cn:
组装出的爆炸物。
可直接使用进行攻击，爆炸时对周围所有敌人造成伤害。
desc.en:
A packaged explosive. 
Can be used to directly attack targets. The resulting explosion deals damage to all nearby enemies.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 多级加工后，高晶纤维已经能够应用于多种信号传输场景。
decoDesc.en: Cryston Fibers can undergo various processing steps to create a material for transmitting data and communication signals.

desc.cn: 高晶粉末精炼融合后的高级材料，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: A high quality material prepared by refining Cryston Powder. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在协议技术介入下，经过精细研磨后，未妥善保存的高晶粉末会在非密封容器中“流动”。
decoDesc.en: After fine grinding, improperly stored Cryston Powder will start to "flow" in non-hermetic containers due to Techno-Protocol influences.

desc.cn: 紫晶粉末研磨后的细粉，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Acquired by grinding Amethyst Powder. Can be used to produce other materials.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 将紫晶加工成纤维后，其拉伸度获得了极大的增强。
decoDesc.en: Factory-drawn Amethyst fibers exhibit vastly increased strength.

desc.cn: 由紫晶矿精炼得来的纤维，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Fibers made by refining Amethyst Ore. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 在经过粉碎处理后，紫晶二级加工品的质地更加均匀。
decoDesc.en: Amethyst can be shredded to yield a processed product with improved homogeneity.

desc.cn: 紫晶纤维粉碎后的粉末，可用于其他材料合成。
desc.en: Shredded and powdered Amethyst Fibers. Can be used to produce other items.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 紫晶在精密工业等领域的使用较为广泛，是塔卫二电子工业的基础材料之一。
decoDesc.en: Amethyst has a wide range of uses in precision manufacturing. The crystal is one of the essential basic materials in the electronic industry of Talos-II.

desc.cn: 内蕴紫色晶体的岩石，可在工业系统中进行加工。
desc.en: An ore containing a purple colored crystalline material. It can be processed with the AIC.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地失窃的建材，被裂地者匆忙收进箱中，是否意味着裂地者正在内乱呢？
decoDesc.en: Building materials stolen from Endfield, haphazardly stuffed into crates by the Landbreakers. Perhaps something is going on amongst the raiders themselves.

decoDesc.cn: 塔卫二常见的电能储存装置，能够给机械提供应急电能。
decoDesc.en: A power storage device commonly seen in Talos-II. Provides emergency electrical power to various types of machinery.

decoDesc.cn:
用于大型备用电源的零件。
用来修复电源类设备的自动套组，为照顾不重视用电安全的人而特意设计成了现在的样子。
decoDesc.en:
A part for large backup power supplies. 
This is an auto-module kit for repairing power facilities. Designed specifically in this fashion to cater to users who are often negligent about electrical safety.

desc.cn: 用来修复大型备用电源的零件。
desc.en: A part for repairing large backup power supplies.

decoDesc.cn: 源石副产物中心发现的原型机零件，交给安德烈后可以修复在锚点灾害中损坏的原型机。
decoDesc.en: Special parts found in the Originium Byproduct Processing Center. Give them to Andre to repair the prototype damaged during the Ankhorfall.

desc.cn: 用于修复原型机的零件。
desc.en: Parts for repairing a prototype.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地失窃的物资箱，被加密了，连佩丽卡的权限也无法解锁。
decoDesc.en: A stolen Endfield supply crate. The container is encrypted. Even Perlica's authority level failed to open it.

decoDesc.cn: 从流民身上获取的可疑戒指，似乎在裂地者的身上也见过同样的东西。
decoDesc.en: A suspicious ring acquired from a nomad. The Landbreakers seem to be wearing the same rings as well.

decoDesc.cn: 能够短时间内抑制矿石病的药剂。
decoDesc.en: A pharmaceutical agent capable of suppressing Oripathy symptoms for a short time.

decoDesc.cn: 用于特殊终末地设备的能量电池。
decoDesc.en: An energy battery for special Endfield facilities.

decoDesc.cn: 装有抗生素注射液的医疗器械，使用起来简单便捷。
decoDesc.en: A medical kit capable of administering antibiotic solutions. Easy to use and effective.

decoDesc.cn: 仅被用来急救的医疗器械，特殊的接口设计保证了它能在无菌状态下切入人体组织。
decoDesc.en: A medical kit for emergency treatment. Special contact point designs allow it to make germ-free incisions into human tissue.

decoDesc.cn: 能够修复轻度故障设备的自动设备，是终末地工业特有的技术产品。
decoDesc.en: An auto-tool capable of repairing lightly damaged facilities or machines. This technological product is only produced by Endfield Industries.

decoDesc.cn: 工团的应急维修箱，里面存放着各式设备最常用的维修零件。
decoDesc.en: An emergency repair kit of the UWST. It contains a set of commonly used machinery repair tools.

decoDesc.cn: 老站长从不离身的安全帽。它出现在施工环境中，却未佩戴在老站长身上，这代表着某种不祥的可能。
decoDesc.en: The site director's helmet. The old man hardly parted with this. But here it lies, in the middle of a construction site and not on the man himself. This hints strongly at a certain possibility.

desc.cn: 老站长的安全帽。
desc.en: Helmet belonging to the old site director.

decoDesc.cn: 不太常见的旧式供电装置，现在已经少有人会使用这种规格的电池了。
decoDesc.en: An uncommon power unit with an older design. Only a few would use batteries of such specifications nowadays.

decoDesc.cn: 随处可见的源石集成电路。
decoDesc.en: A ubiquitous Originium integrated circuit (ORIC).

decoDesc.cn: 完成本次测试版本终局挑战的证明！
decoDesc.en: A proof of accomplishment given to the heroes who completed the final challenge of this test!

decoDesc.cn: 针对部分罕见疾病而研发出的药剂，每年产量极少，因此价格相当高昂。
decoDesc.en: A special pharmaceutical agent designed to counter certain rare diseases. This is expensive as annual production is extremely low.

decoDesc.cn:
为了方便使用而做了便利化设计的供电设备零件。
简单的拆装方式与小巧的体积带来了些许风险，这代表着它可以被任何人轻易提走。
decoDesc.en:
A special part for electrical supplies designed for convenience. 
Its easy-to-dismantle and miniaturized designs pose certain risks. People can just carry off the part without permission.

decoDesc.cn:
"疯了，绝对是疯了！出现侵蚀现象是正常的，可这里出现这样大的一个洞穴明显不正常。具体数据在表格页，你们只需要看一眼就知道！
我个人意见是立刻撤离，要多快有多快！然后派专家来解决问题！
所有侵蚀现象里，与空间异常有关的绝对是最危险的！我不管什么学界的研究成果，只要和空间有关！就是最危险的！
你们不是没听过史上赫赫有名的那几个侵蚀现象吧？
虽然我们的实验数据一直很稳定，周边不该发生侵蚀现象，但现在的侵蚀问题再不解决，我们都（粗口）会赫赫有名！名垂青史！"
decoDesc.en:
"Madness! This is definitely madness! We can expect some Blight, but having a massive pit appearing at this place IS NOT NORMAL. All the figures are in the datasheet. Just one glance and you'll see! 
"My personal view is to EVAC NOW. ASAP! Then send in the professionals to handle the problem! 
"Of all the Blight phenomena out there, spatial anomalies are the most dangerous! I don't care about the results of whatever field of research you quote. Spatial blightery is the worst and most THREATENING! 
"Did none of you read about the worst Blight events we had in history? 
"I know our experimental data is stable and we shouldn't be getting Blight manifestations in this region, but if we don't take care of this Blight problem, our blighted names will be remembered in history as the blightbrained criminals who let it blight the hell of everything!"

decoDesc.en: An object with moderate weight. You can hear things rolling around inside when you lift it. Best be gentle with this thing.

decoDesc.cn: 重量较轻，拿起时有剧烈声响，建议小心挪放。
decoDesc.en: An object that feels pretty light. Lifting it gave off really loud noises. Best be very gentle with this thing.

decoDesc.cn: 重量较沉，根据大小推测，可能其中含有密度较大的金属。
decoDesc.en: An object that feels quite heavy. Judging from the size, it probably contains extremely dense metals.

decoDesc.cn:
诺伯特先生感谢你的帮助，并送予你了一个纪念品。
这块银光闪闪的物质似乎是某种稀有金属，也有可能是危险的侵蚀材料……
那么它究竟是什么呢？建议你不要向诺伯特先生提问，因为诺伯特先生很可能也不清楚。
decoDesc.en:
Mr. Norbert gave you this souvenir as a token of his gratitude. 
This silvery material is either a rare metallic alloy or dangerously Blighted material... 
What exactly is it? Best not ask Mr. Norbert because the Junkyard Lord probably doesn't know either.

decoDesc.cn:
诺伯特感谢你的帮助，并再次送予你了一个纪念品。
这个看起来近似于相机的物体，出乎意料地不具备“拍摄”功能。
那么它究竟是什么呢？建议你不要向诺伯特提问，诺伯特也不清楚。
decoDesc.en:
Mr. Norbert gave you yet another souvenir as a token of his gratitude. 
This object looks like a camera but surprisingly lacks the ability to take photographs. 
What exactly is it? Best not ask Mr. Norbert because the Junkyard Lord probably doesn't know either.

decoDesc.cn: 诺伯特用来修复无人机控制塔的材料，可以用于加固控制塔。
decoDesc.en: Norbert needs this to repair the drone control tower. It can be used to reinforce the facility.

decoDesc.cn: 诺伯特用来修复无人机控制塔的材料，是控制塔不可缺少的一部分。
decoDesc.en: Norbert needs this to repair the drone control tower. It is an indispensable component of the facility.

decoDesc.cn: 诺伯特用来修复无人机控制塔的材料，是控制塔能否成功运行的核心部件。
decoDesc.en: Norbert needs this to repair the drone control tower. This core component ensures the proper functioning of the facility.

decoDesc.en: This sticker made it to the most recommended list amongst Endfield photography enthusiasts. United Workers' Syndicates of Talos II — A partner of excellence and quality.

desc.cn: 贴在照片上的装饰贴纸，可以在拍照功能中使用。

decoDesc.cn: 自“记忆”中获得的贴纸。轻巧、沉默，却也足够沉重。
decoDesc.en: A sticker acquired from the "memories". Though light and tranquil, it carries quite a somber vibe.

desc.cn: 贴在照片上的装饰贴纸，可以在拍照功能中使用。
desc.en: A decorative sticker that can be applied to a photograph. Can be used in the Camera feature.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业摄影同好贴纸推荐榜入选贴纸。嗯……满满的生活感。
decoDesc.en: This sticker made it to the most recommended list amongst Endfield photography enthusiasts. Mmm... The vibe and smell of happy living.

desc.cn: 贴在照片上的装饰贴纸，可以在拍照功能中使用。
desc.en: A decorative sticker that can be applied to a photograph. Can be used in the Camera feature.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业摄影同好贴纸推荐榜入选贴纸。了解更广阔的世界，留下更多记忆。
decoDesc.en: This sticker made it to the most recommended list amongst Endfield photography enthusiasts. Explore the world beyond and make memorable moments.

desc.cn: 贴在照片上的装饰贴纸，可以在拍照功能中使用。
desc.en: A decorative sticker that can be applied to a photograph. Can be used in the Camera feature.

decoDesc.cn: 酸甜适中的柑橘味布丁，在熬煮过程中撒入了异香石碎屑调味，并用源石虫提取物固形。啊啊……这种甜到发腻的香气。
decoDesc.en: Citrome-flavored pudding with balanced sour and sweet flavors. Bits of aggagrit were added during boiling. Originium Slug extracts were then used to solidify the entire thing. This cloyingly sweet aroma is simply ... magnificent.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员终结技能量的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's Ultimate Energy.

noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 几乎完脱去水分的虫肉干，吃起来很有嚼头。在四号谷地，这是喂养宠物的上品食料。
decoDesc.en: Slug meat that has been completely dehydrated. The pulled jerky is incredibly chewy. This is one of the best pet foods in Valley IV.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.
