noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 印有“克莱韦思商贸公司”标识的文件袋，但标识似乎是旧版本的。
decoDesc.en: A document holder furnished with the old logo of Clavis TGCC Trading.

desc.cn: “克莱韦思商贸公司”的文件袋。
desc.en: "Clavis TGCC Trading" Document Holder.

decoDesc.cn: 一个记载了埃里克松商贸公司员工信息的移动终端。如哈特曼所说，其中并没有亚历山大的名字。
decoDesc.en: A handyterm with the Erikssohn Trading House employee roster. Just as Hartmann said, Aleksandr's name is missing from the roster.

desc.cn: 用来证明亚历山大不是埃里克松商贸公司员工的证据。
desc.en: Evidence proving that Aleksandr is not an employee of Erikssohn Trading House.

name.cn: 埃里克松商贸员工信息终端

decoDesc.cn: 一台屏幕损坏的最新款移动终端。被行踪不明的记者拉奎尔遗留在了失踪现场。
decoDesc.en: The latest handyterm but its screen is broken. Raquel the missing journalist left it at the place where she disappeared.

desc.cn: 记者拉奎尔的移动终端，现已损坏。
desc.en: A broken handyterm belonging to Raquel the journalist.

decoDesc.cn: 帮助寨民修复竹筏的竹子，已经被人成捆扎好了。
decoDesc.en: Bamboo for helping stockade residents repair their bamboo rafts. Someone has been kind enough to tie it up into a neat bundle.

desc.cn: 一捆竹子，用来帮助寨民修复竹筏。
desc.en: A bundle of bamboo. Can be used to repair the stockade resident's bamboo raft.

decoDesc.cn: 很少有人知道这种植物的口感，其实通过特别的烹调方式可以烹饪出神奇的味道。
decoDesc.en: Very few actually know how this plant tastes like. In truth, special cooking methods will bring about magical tastes.

desc.cn: 沾着露水的锦草，深受武陵地区动物喜爱。
desc.en: Jincao herbs with some dew on them. The beasts of Wuling love the herb.

decoDesc.cn: 十分坚硬的咸味面包。枢纽区基地决定建设后，初到四号谷地的终末地干员们考虑到可能会发生的物资断供状况，特意在补给清单中加入了这种极耐储存的应急干粮。
decoDesc.en: An extremely hard and salty tack. After the decision to construct the Hub Base was made, the first Endfield operators arriving at Valley IV considered the possibility of supply shortage. Hence, they specifically added these emergency rations known for their extremely long shelf lives to the supply list.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 酸辣味的腌水果。柑实未完全成熟时味道极酸，但连皮一起切块，再加入苦叶椒与异香石料粉腌制后，却能产生酸辣爽口的味道。
decoDesc.en: Fruit preserves with a sour and spicy flavor. Unripened citromes can be extremely sour, but cut them to pieces (along with the rind) and marinate them in a blend of tartpeppers and aggagrit condiments. The result is a refreshing riot of sour and spicy.

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 请在协议相关装置覆盖区使用本类建材。
decoDesc.en: Only use these materials within the effective range of Protocol facilities.

desc.cn: 进行工业建造的基础建材，可用于“帝江号”的升级建造。
desc.en: A basic construction material. Can be used to upgrade Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 若建材发生自动扭曲、颜色异常等现象，请加急致电管理员或佩丽卡监督。
decoDesc.en: If this material exhibits any sign of warping or discoloration, IMMEDIATELY CONTACT the Endministrator or Supervisor Perlica.

desc.cn: 进行工业建造的突破建材，可用于“帝江号”的升级建造。
desc.en: An advanced industrial construction material. Can be used to upgrade Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 友谊的见证。
decoDesc.en: Proof of friendship.

desc.cn: 可用于在采购中心 - 信用交易处兑换养成材料等重要资源。
desc.en: Exchangeable for progression materials and other important resources at the Acquisition Center - Credit Store.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 通过生产助力等社交玩法获取
noObtainWayHint.en: Social Gameplay (Production Assist and Clue Exchange)

decoDesc.cn: 标准天师桩模型。打开最高亮度后可以当作大台灯使用。
decoDesc.en: A standard Tianshi Pillar model. Switch it on and adjust to maximum brightness to use it as a large table lamp.

desc.cn: 可放置在帝江号中央环厅的行迹高塔中进行展示。
desc.en: This can be showcased at the Tower of Trails at the Central Ring of Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 可爱的小动物模型。工人们相信能在危险的塔卫二环境中存活下来的长耳兽能带给人勇气。
decoDesc.en: A model of a cute critter. UWST crew mates treat long-ears as a bringer of courage as they are capable of surviving the dangerous environments of Talos-II.

desc.cn: 可放置在帝江号中央环厅的行迹高塔中进行展示。
desc.en: This can be showcased at the Tower of Trails at the Central Ring of Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 摩托车的模型。弧线2000是终末地推出的经典款式，广受欢迎。它轻盈稳定，适应多地形，因此连模型也很抢手。
decoDesc.en: A scale model of a motorcycle. Arc 2000 is a classic and popular vehicle manufactured by Endfield Industries due to its light weight, reliability, and all-terrain performance. Even its scale models are widely sought after.

desc.cn: 可放置在帝江号中央环厅的行迹高塔中进行展示。
desc.en: This can be showcased at the Tower of Trails at the Central Ring of Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 多功能钻探器的模型。在谷地开拓之初发生的突如其来的天使袭击事件中，这一款钻探器承担了钻碎锚点的重任。
decoDesc.en: A scale model of the multi-purpose drill. During the sudden Aggeloid attack when construction work first began at the Valley, this drill crawler carried out the crucial task of smashing the Ankhor to bits.

desc.cn: 可放置在帝江号中央环厅的行迹高塔中进行展示。
desc.en: This can be showcased at the Tower of Trails at the Central Ring of Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 源石树苗的模型。作为礼品，它代表着成长、新生、希望的祝福，多数时间会摆在病人的床头。
decoDesc.en: A scale model of the Originium sapling. This is a gift, a blessing of growth, rebirth, and hope. It is usually placed at the side of a patient's bed.

desc.cn: 可放置在帝江号中央环厅的行迹高塔中进行展示。
desc.en: This can be showcased at the Tower of Trails at the Central Ring of Dijiang.

decoDesc.cn: 若使用错误手段开启，本档案会在约三秒内自燃成灰。
decoDesc.en: This dossier will self-combust in three seconds if opened the wrong way.

desc.cn: 成套线索整合而成的情报档案，可用于各类地区行动。
desc.en: A clue dossier generated by a complete set of clues and findings. Can be used for initiating operations in various areas.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 开启会客室情报交流获取

decoDesc.cn:
终末地工业与合作方所签订物资供应协定的使用凭证。
仅限武陵区域有效。
decoDesc.en:
Endfield Industries and its partners have signed an agreement to trade supplies and commodities with this currency. 
This currency can only be used in the Wuling region.

desc.cn: 可在“帝江号”的供应链专员拉冬处使用，兑换武陵的货品。
desc.en: Supply chain specialist Ladonn aboard Dijiang will accept this currency and give you Wuling goods in return.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成武陵据点的订单获取

decoDesc.cn: 芯片理应记录着帝江号扩容规划，其中却仅有巨量难解的乱码……或许有人能将之解析清楚，但那人是谁呢？
decoDesc.en: This data chip should contain plans for expanding Dijiang but its memory array only contains vast amounts of incredibly encrypted code... Someone might know how to decipher this, but who might that be?

desc.cn: 可在“帝江号”的总控中枢使用，进行飞船整体升级的拓展规划。
desc.en: Use this at the Control Nexus aboard Dijiang to unlock the next expansion phase of the entire vessel.

noObtainWayHint.en: Acquire this by completing the adventure of the main story.

decoDesc.cn:
终末地工业与合作方所签订物资供应协定的使用凭证。
仅限四号谷地区域有效。
decoDesc.en:
Colloquially abbreviated as Vallico. Endfield Industries and all Convention signatories agree to use this fiat currency for trading supplies and commodities. 
This certificate is legal tender only in the Valley IV region.

desc.cn: 可在“帝江号”的供应链专员拉冬处使用，兑换四号谷地的货品。
desc.en: Supply chain specialist Ladonn aboard Dijiang will accept these certs and offer you goods from Valley IV in return.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 完成四号谷地据点的订单获取

decoDesc.cn: 代表着福气的精致连连乐。轻轻一刮，无论数字大小，皆是福气，祝您宏运连连。
decoDesc.en: An intricate connect-and-win voucher that represents Fortune. Scratch it and see. It doesn't matter what the numbers are, because Fortune is always smiling on you.

desc.cn:
使用后从以下奖励中随机获得一种。
- 嵌晶玉×200
- 嵌晶玉×260
- 嵌晶玉×280
- 嵌晶玉×300
desc.en:
Use this to randomly get 1 of these rewards:
- Oroberyl×200
- Oroberyl×260
- Oroberyl×280
- Oroberyl×300

decoDesc.cn: 代表着好运的精致连连乐。轻轻一刮，这美妙的数字便是好运的象征，祝您福气满怀。
decoDesc.en: An intricate connect-and-win voucher that represents Luck. Scratch it and see. The beautiful strings of numbers are symbols of Luck, and may you have plenty of it.

desc.cn: 使用后获得嵌晶玉×880。
desc.en: Use this to get Oroberyl×880.

decoDesc.cn: 为了能让刚苏醒的管理员更快适应终末地上的工作，人力资源事务部特别计划了一次人才招聘。
decoDesc.en: To familiarize the freshly awakened Endministrator with the many ongoing projects of Endfield, the HR Division planned a special recruitment event.

desc.cn: 终末地工业内部凭证，可用于在「启程寻访」中寻访10次。
desc.en: An internal certificate of Endfield Industries. Use this to perform 10×headhunting in [New Horizons Headhunting].

decoDesc.cn: 塔卫二上不乏精英干将。为了满足终末地工业日益增长的人才需求，人力资源事务部特别准备了针对特殊人才招聘的临时应急手段。
decoDesc.en: Talos-II is home to plenty of talented individuals. To satisfy the ever-increasing demand for skilled operators of Endfield Industries, the HR Division has prepared a special and temporary contingent measure for headhunting.

desc.cn: 终末地工业内部凭证，可用于在「特许寻访」中寻访1次。
desc.en: An internal certificate of Endfield Industries. Use this to perform 1 headhunting in [Chartered Headhunting].

decoDesc.cn: 塔卫二上不乏精英干将。为了满足终末地工业日益增长的人才需求，人力资源事务部特别准备了针对特殊人才招聘的临时应急手段。
decoDesc.en: Talos-II is home to plenty of talented individuals. To satisfy the ever-increasing demand for skilled operators of Endfield Industries, the HR Division has prepared a special and temporary contingent measure for headhunting.

desc.cn: 终末地工业限时凭证，可用于在「特许寻访」中寻访1次。
desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 1 headhunting in [Chartered Headhunting].

decoDesc.cn: 一张特殊的人事凭证，为招选具备某些特殊条件的干员而准备，由于准备紧急，它不可避免地受困于时效性。
decoDesc.en: A special HR permit for headhunting operators who meet various unique requirements. Given the emergency of this request, this permit will inevitably expire after a certain time limit.

desc.cn: 终末地工业限时凭证，可用于在「熔火灼痕」特许寻访中寻访1次。该凭证将在「熔火灼痕」特许寻访结束后失效。
desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 1 headhunting in [Scars of the Forge] Chartered Headhunting. This certificate will expire when [Scars of the Forge] Chartered Headhunting ends.

decoDesc.en: A special HR permit for headhunting operators who meet various unique requirements. Given the emergency of this request, this permit will inevitably expire after a certain time limit.

desc.cn: 终末地工业限时凭证，可用于在「热烈色彩」特许寻访中寻访1次。该凭证将在「热烈色彩」特许寻访结束后失效。
desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 1 headhunting in [Hues of Passion] Chartered Headhunting. This certificate will expire when [Hues of Passion] Chartered Headhunting ends.

decoDesc.cn: 一张特殊的人事凭证，为招选具备某些特殊条件的干员而准备，由于准备紧急，它不可避免地受困于时效性。
decoDesc.en: A special HR permit for headhunting operators who meet various unique requirements. Given the emergency of this request, this permit will inevitably expire after a certain time limit.

desc.cn: 终末地工业限时凭证，可用于在「轻飘飘的信使」特许寻访中寻访1次。该凭证将在「轻飘飘的信使」特许寻访结束后失效。
desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 1 headhunting in [The Floaty Messenger] Chartered Headhunting. This certificate will expire when [The Floaty Messenger] Chartered Headhunting ends.

decoDesc.cn: 人力资源事务部的工作人员往往会在某些时段忙到焦头烂额，只要管理员有什么英雄事迹遍传四方，终末地就会多出不少新干员。
decoDesc.en: When tales of the Endministrator's heroic deeds spread to a place, Endfielders at the HR Division would be quickly overwhelmed with work. When the hectic OT blows over, new faces will show up in the roster of Endfield operators.

desc.cn: 终末地工业内部凭证，可用于在「特许寻访」中寻访10次。
desc.en: An internal certificate of Endfield Industries. Use this to perform 10×headhunting in [Chartered Headhunting].

decoDesc.cn: 一张特殊的人事凭证，为批量招选具备某些特殊条件的干员而准备，由于准备紧急，它不可避免地受困于时效性。为了这张凭证，人力资源事务部的干员们付出了数十个日夜，请务必妥善使用。
decoDesc.en: A special HR permit for headhunting operators who meet various unique requirements. Given the emergency of this request, this permit will inevitably expire after a certain time limit. NOTE: HR operators have spent entire weeks preparing this permit. Use it wisely.

desc.cn: 终末地工业限时凭证，可用于在「热烈色彩」特许寻访中寻访10次。该凭证将在「热烈色彩」特许寻访结束后失效。
desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 10×headhunting in [Hues of Passion] Chartered Headhunting. This certificate will expire when [Hues of Passion] Chartered Headhunting ends.

desc.cn: 终末地工业限时凭证，可用于在「轻飘飘的信使」特许寻访中寻访10次。该凭证将在「轻飘飘的信使」特许寻访结束后失效。
desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 10×headhunting in [The Floaty Messenger] Chartered Headhunting. This certificate will expire when [The Floaty Messenger] Chartered Headhunting ends.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业在塔卫二上有着广阔的人脉与资源。每当终末地人力资源事务部准备挖掘某个领域的人才时，总会有人闻讯而来。
decoDesc.en: Endfield Industries has many connections and resources throughout Talos-II. Whenever the Endfield HR Division starts headhunting in a particular sector of the industry, someone will always answer the call.

desc.cn: 终末地工业内部凭证，可用于在「基础寻访」中寻访1次。
desc.en: An internal certificate of Endfield Industries. Use this to perform 1 headhunting in [Basic Headhunting].

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业发放的武器兑换凭证。拥有这类凭证的人，即便并非终末地内部人员，也能顺利发起武器支援申请。
decoDesc.en: A weapon exchange certificate from Endfield. Anyone, even non-Endfielders, can use this certificate and apply for support from the Endfield Arsenal.

desc.cn: 特殊武库凭证，可通过它进行武库申领，同时获取十件武器。
desc.en: A special Arsenal certificate. Can be used for Arsenal Issue and acquire 10 pieces of weapons.

decoDesc.cn:
用来探测醚质的施术单元，外观近似罗盘，能够利用表盘中心的小小醚质来定位其他醚质。
“罗盘”处于超频运转状态，仅仅是简单激活就会让指针疯转起来。
decoDesc.en:
An Arts Unit for detecting Aurylene. This device looks like a compass, and contains a tiny Aurylene in its center to locate other Aurylene in the environment. 
This "compass" seems to be operating at an overclocked state. The needle would spin wildly upon simple activation.

desc.cn: 消耗品，使用后可探测出当前区域内的一个未发现的醚质。解锁当前区域所有地图迷雾后才可使用。（仅限四号谷地地区生效）
desc.en: Consumable. Usage reveals an undiscovered Aurylene within the current area. Usable only after all fogged places of the map have been charted. This item only works in Valley IV.

decoDesc.cn:
最初被用于探查四号谷地金属资源的特制探测器，使用与储藏箱相同的金属材料制成，能够指向放置在各处的储藏箱。
“致绝境中的坚守”——仪器边缘刻着如此字样。
decoDesc.en:
A special detector once created by prospectors looking for metal resources in Valley IV. It is made of the same metals used in storage crates. Using this points you to storage crates scattered throughout the area. 
Several words have been engraved along the edge of the device: "To those who persevere in hopelessness."

desc.cn: 消耗品，使用后可探测出当前区域内的一个未发现的储藏箱。解锁当前区域所有地图迷雾后才可使用。（仅限四号谷地地区生效）
desc.en: Consumable. Usage reveals an undiscovered storage crate within the current area. Usable only after all fogged places of the map have been charted. This item only works in Valley IV.

decoDesc.cn: 摩擦摩擦，扭一扭，共享电力好朋友。
decoDesc.en: Rub, rub, twist, twist! Good friends share electricity!

decoDesc.en: A heavy casting die made using rare materials. Techno-Protocol activation lets this die enhance general material strengths in weapons.

desc.cn: 用于武器突破的素材。
desc.en: A material that tunes weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 以稀有材料做成的模具，通过协议技术激活后，可以提高武器的综合材料强度。
decoDesc.en: A casting die made using rare materials. Techno-Protocol activation lets this die enhance general material strengths in weapons.

desc.cn: 用于武器突破的素材。
desc.en: A material that tunes weapons.

decoDesc.cn: 使用了集成化工业技术的一次性装置套组，可以深度自动化检查武器全部结构，修补暗伤，极大提高武器性能。
decoDesc.en: A single-use toolset with AIC technology. Provides automated in-depth inspection of the entire weapon structure. Also repairs internal material damage and significantly enhances weapon performance.

desc.cn: 用于武器等级提升的素材，提供了大量武器升级经验。
desc.en: A material that provides a lot of weapon EXP.

decoDesc.cn: 使用了集成化工业技术的一次性微型单元，可以自动化检查武器局部位置，修补暗伤，轻微提高武器性能。
decoDesc.en: A single-use micro-device with AIC technology. Provides automated inspection of weapon parts. Also repairs internal material damage and slightly enhances weapon performance.

desc.cn: 用于武器等级提升的素材，提供了少量武器升级经验。
desc.en: A material that provides some weapon EXP.

decoDesc.cn: 使用了集成化工业技术的一次性小型装置，可以自动化检查武器全部结构，修补暗伤，提高武器性能。
decoDesc.en: A single-use mini-kit with AIC technology. Provides automated inspection of the entire weapon structure. Also repairs internal material damage and enhances weapon performance.

desc.cn: 用于武器等级提升的素材，提供了中量武器升级经验。
desc.en: A material that gives decent weapon EXP.

decoDesc.cn: 记录着某种植物资料的密档。据分析，这种近似荞花的植物多见于协议空间中存在天使残骸的区域，就像是从残骸中生长出来的一样。
decoDesc.en: Classified records about a particular plant that resembles buckflowers. It is native to the Valley's Aberrants and common in areas with Aggelos remains in the Protocol Space. This seems to suggest that the plant grew on the remains themselves.

desc.cn: 谷地像差区域1的白色包裹中掉落，可用于提交委托。
desc.en: Acquired from Aberrant Zone 1 white quality packages. Can be submitted to complete commissions.

decoDesc.cn: 金质秦茳尺雕像，不知为何会出现在这片协议空间中。其呆滞的表情惟妙惟肖，让人看到后第一时间就能联想到她远眺供能高地的神态。
decoDesc.en: A gold statuette of Qin Jiangchi. Nobody knows why it showed up in the Protocol Space. Her dazed and blank expression is extremely well done. A single glance could remind people how she looked when gazing upon the Power Plateau in the great distance.

decoDesc.cn: 记录册上的每一个数字都代表着我们对这片未知之地更深度的掌握。
decoDesc.en: Every number in this logbook represents our deeper understanding of this unknown realm.

desc.cn: 从谷地像差带出沉积结核或完成某些委托获得，累积后可领取奖励。
desc.en: Acquired by bringing out precipitation nodules from the Valley's Aberrants or by completing certain commissions. Earn enough Operation Metrics to claim rewards.

decoDesc.cn: 成因特殊的醚质晶块，闪闪发光，具有独特的科研价值。
decoDesc.en: A glimmering Aurylene Crystal created through special means. It offers unique research values.

desc.cn: 从谷地像差带出沉积结核转化获得，可用于委托提交和刷新。
desc.en: Acquired by converting precipitation nodules brought out from the Valley's Aberrants. Can be submitted to complete or refresh commissions.

decoDesc.cn: 包含大量稀有特征的物质样本，一个遗落的爆破单元的外壳残块。轻轻敲击，仍能感受到内部传来的澎湃能量。
decoDesc.en: A material sample with many rare properties. This is a casing fragment of a lost detonation unit. A gentle tap allows one to feel the explosive energy contained within.

decoDesc.en: A material sample with many rare properties. A fragment that fell off an ever-rising orb of hazefyre. Those who approach it might hear the surging cries of a great crowd. Upon reaching the zenith, a warrior's path of carnage ceases abruptly.

decoDesc.cn: 色彩黯淡的小块高密度晶体，是物质在协议空间变化过程中，受挤压而形成的晶石核心。它能孵化出过去的、真实的投影。
decoDesc.en: A small, dense, and dark colored crystal formation. Such materials usually arise when matter is subject to compressive forces generated by transformations of Protocol Space. It can give birth to realistic projections of the past.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 色彩黯淡的中块高密度晶体，是物质在协议空间变化过程中，受挤压而形成的晶石核心。它能孵化出夸张的、未诞的幻想之物。
decoDesc.en: A sizable, dense, and dark colored crystal formation. Such materials usually arise when matter is subject to compressive forces generated by transformations of Protocol Space. It can give birth to exaggerated imaginations never thought of before.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。

decoDesc.en: A large, dense, and dark colored crystal formation. Such materials usually arise when matter is subject to compressive forces generated by transformations of Protocol Space. It can also give birth to wild, twisted, yet superficial fantasies.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。

decoDesc.cn: 小块高密度晶体。生命、希望，以及一点点爱……物质在“起点的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A small and dense crystal formation imbued with life, hope, and a sprinkle of love... It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Origins.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。

decoDesc.en: A sizable and dense crystal formation imbued with growth, power, and a dash of confusion... It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Origins.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。

decoDesc.en: A large and dense crystal formation imbued with depletion, despair, and a touch of death... It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Origins.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。

decoDesc.cn: 小块高密度晶体。“最初的战胜者，幸存下来的人，背负着一条道路，一整个文明”……物质在“重压的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A small and dense crystal formation. "The first victors and survivors took the path, as well as the entire civilization, upon themselves." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Pressure.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 中块高密度晶体。“冰冷的瞥视，拥有碾碎一切的重量”……物质在“重压的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A sizable and dense crystal formation. "The cold glance bears the weight to crush everything in sight." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Pressure.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 大块高密度晶体。“在千钧岩壁下，人类依旧能开凿出供生命容身的石室”……物质在“重压的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A large and dense crystal formation. "Though they faced the daunting cliffs, humanity succeeded in chiseling out a stony alcove for the nurturing of life." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Pressure.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 小块高密度晶体。“孩子们离开故乡，随即迷失于黑夜之中，因此哭声不止”……物质在“焚烧的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A small and dense crystal formation. "The children left home but became lost in the night. Thus they never stopped crying." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Conflagration.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。

decoDesc.en: A sizable and dense crystal formation. "It ended when they touched their first tool and struck their first burst of sparks." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Conflagration.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 大块高密度晶体。“凿穿大山吧，点燃自我吧，走出长夜吧”……物质在“焚烧的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A large and dense crystal formation. "Tunnel through the mountains! Ignite yourselves and leave the long night behind." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Conflagration.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 小块高密度晶体。“正因如此，钢铁与水泥在各处拔地而起，得以成为大地的框架，文明的骨骼”……物质在“接续的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A small and dense crystal formation. "And that was how steel and concrete sprouted from the ground. They become the framework of the land, the skeleton of Civilization." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Connection.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 中块高密度晶体。“蔓延出的血肉，弥补着大地的裂伤”……物质在“接续的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A sizable and dense crystal formation. "Blood and flesh grew forth to mend the gashes of the land." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Connection.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 大块高密度晶体。“第一声心跳响起，答案触手可及”……物质在“接续的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A large and dense crystal formation. "When the first heartbeat was heard, the answer was well within reach." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Connection.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 小块的高密度晶体。“近在咫尺处的答案，仅差一跃”……物质在“跃升的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A small and dense crystal formation. "The answer was so close, just one jump away." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Leap.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 中块的高密度晶体。“高高跃起，成为星辰”……物质在“跃升的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A sizable and dense crystal formation. "Make the giant leap and become the stars themselves." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Leap.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 大块的高密度晶体。“而后，烧去千万年间的荒芜，将托举者们引向前方”……物质在“跃升的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A large and dense crystal formation. "Eons of barrenness burned to lead the uplifted ones forward." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Leap.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 小块的高密度晶体。“否定生命之物，像差因它而成”……物质在“雾火的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A small and dense crystal formation. "The aberrants are derived from entities that rejected life." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Hazefyre.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 中块的高密度晶体。“在像差之中，未诞的未来正在结出畸形苦果”……物质在“雾火的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A sizable and dense crystal formation. "Within the aberrants, a future yet realized gives birth to an abominable gall." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Hazefyre.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 大块的高密度晶体。“截断前路的雾火就在此处，啃食文明的恶意仍在弥散”……物质在“雾火的像差”中如此挤压成形。
decoDesc.en: A large and dense crystal formation. "Here is the hazefyre that chokes the path. The malignance consuming Civilization has continued to spread." It is created by compressive forces generated by the Aberrant of Hazefyre.

desc.cn: 击碎谷地像差中的沉积晶石后采集获得，或击败谷地像差中的敌人掉落，可转化为醚质晶块。
desc.en: Acquired by shattering precipitation crystals and gathering the pieces, or by looting defeated enemies in the Valley's Aberrants. Can be converted into Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“协议稳定”技术相关数据的芯片。这个受超域影响的协议空间尚未演化完成，将其稳定下来，减少突发性灾害发生的可能，是进行探索的第一步。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Protocol Stabilization" technology. The evolution of this Æther-affected Protocol Space is incomplete. Stabilizing it will reduce the possibility of sudden disasters and achieve the first step of exploration.

decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Container Expansion" technology. "Increase the thickness of the lead containment layer for safety considerations... After all, nobody knows if the stored item would suddenly jump out and bite your hand."

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“紊乱耐受”技术相关数据的芯片。请将这种“贴片”放在您的太阳穴上，在协议空间产生变化时，它能保护您免受认知干扰的影响。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Derangement Tolerance" technology. Please stick this "surface-mounting chip" on your temple. It will protect you against cognito interferences that might arise when the Protocol Space undergo changes.

desc.cn: 可增加对环境紊乱的耐受程度，降低紊乱值增长速度。
desc.en: Raises tolerance to ambient Derangement and slows down rate of Derangement increase.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“紊乱耐受”技术相关数据的芯片。请将这种“贴片”放在您的太阳穴上，在协议空间产生变化时，它能保护您免受认知干扰的影响。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Derangement Tolerance" technology. Please stick this "surface-mounting chip" on your temple. It will protect you against cognito interferences that might arise when the Protocol Space undergo changes.

desc.cn: 可增加对环境紊乱的耐受程度，降低紊乱值增长速度。

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“爆炸物携行”技术相关数据的芯片。由武库工程师亲自设计，保证您火力充足。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Portable Explosives" technology. It is personally designed by an Arsenal Engineer to guarantee your firepower.

desc.cn: 可携带工业爆炸物进入谷地像差。
desc.en: Allows the user to bring Industrial Explosives into the Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“爆炸物携行”技术相关数据的芯片。由武库工程师亲自设计，保证您火力充足。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Portable Explosives" technology. It is personally designed by an Arsenal Engineer to guarantee your firepower.

desc.cn: 可携带更多工业爆炸物进入谷地像差。
desc.en: Allows the user to bring more Industrial Explosives into the Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“结核精炼”技术相关数据的芯片。“这些沉积结核……呃……就像是处在不同孵化阶段的羽兽卵，分析它们就和开奖没什么区别。”
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Nodule Refining" technology. "These precipitation nodules are... well... kinda like fowlbeast eggs at different stages of development. Analyzing them is like opening a gacha egg."

desc.cn: 带出的沉积结核可以转化为更多醚质晶块。
desc.en: Precipitation nodules successfully brought out can be converted into more Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“结核精炼”技术相关数据的芯片。“这些沉积结核……呃……就像是处在不同孵化阶段的羽兽卵，分析它们就和开奖没什么区别。”
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Nodule Refining" technology. "These precipitation nodules are... well... kinda like fowlbeast eggs at different stages of development. Analyzing them is like opening a gacha egg."

desc.cn: 带出的沉积结核可以转化为更多醚质晶块。
desc.en: Precipitation nodules successfully brought out can be converted into more Aurylene Crystals.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“碎片化医疗”技术相关数据的芯片。在受到紊乱环境的干扰下，依旧奋力保全您的生命健康。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Fragmented Treatment" technology. Though subject to interference exerted by ambient Derangement, it will do its best to keep you alive and safeguard your health.

desc.cn: 在谷地像差中，击败敌人可恢复全队生命值最低干员的生命值。
desc.en: Restores HP to the teammate with the lowest health by defeating enemies in the Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“战术节奏”技术相关数据的芯片。“借力打力！避免力竭！”至少小道奇所转述的卡拉德先生的教导，是如此简洁的。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Tactical Tempo" technology. "Use their energy against themselves to avoid exhausting yourself!" Lil' Dodge certainly knows how to translate Mr. Krad's lessons into short, simple phrases.

desc.cn: 在谷地像差中，击败敌人可恢复技力。
desc.en: Recover SP by defeating enemies in the Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“装甲镀层”技术相关数据的芯片。装甲上添加的沉积结核镀层能有效抵御协议空间中的威胁。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Armor Gilding" technology. Applying a precipitation nodule coating on the armor can effectively defend against the threat posed by the Protocol Space.

desc.cn: 在谷地像差中，干员生命值上限提高。
desc.en: Operators enjoy higher Max HP in the Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“蓄能爆发”技术相关数据的芯片。“这是一个足够危险的尝试，我们试着用您的武器来‘拨动’像差，以起到歼灭敌人的作用。”
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Charge Burst" technology. "This is quite a dangerous test. We're trying to use your weapon to 'activate' the Aberrant and annihilate the enemies."

desc.cn: 在谷地像差中，每次进战第一个技能伤害增加。
desc.en: The first skill cast after start of every battle deals more DMG in Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“能量捕获”技术相关数据的芯片。在像差中，敌人也是一种宝贵资源。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Energy Capture" technology. Enemies in the Aberrants are valuable resources as well.

desc.cn: 在谷地像差中，击败敌人可恢复终极能量。
desc.en: Grants Ultimate Energy by defeating enemies in the Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 录入了“应力回馈”技术相关数据的芯片。或许未来的某一天，在干涉像差的技术获得长足进步后，我们能从这个扭曲协议空间中获得更多“回馈”。
decoDesc.en: A chip storing data related to the "Stress Feedback" technology. Perhaps one day will come when we finally make enough progress in Aberrant-interference technologies, giving us better "feedback" from these twisted Protocol Spaces.

desc.cn: 在谷地像差中，技力恢复速度提高。
desc.en: Grants faster SP Recovery in the Valley's Aberrants.

decoDesc.cn: 极简单的小零食。那些离开家的人、无法回到故乡的人……往往会在最简单的甜味中窥见几缕旧时光。
decoDesc.en: An extremely simple snack. For expatriates who cannot return home ... a quick fix of nostalgia can be acquired in the most simple of sweets.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 弹弹的蔬菜冻。商家会用模具将蔬菜冻特意做成龙泡泡的形状，不存在别的选择，大家都喜欢龙泡泡。噢，多么可爱的龙泡泡。
decoDesc.en: These jellied greens are bouncy and jiggly to the touch. Special molds were used by the manufacturers to create jellied greens shaped like Chubby Lung. It is the only option since everyone likes Chubby Lungs so much. Kyaaa! Chubby Lung! They're so cute!

desc.cn: 使用后可以回复干员生命值的战术物品。
desc.en: Use this tactical to restore the operator's HP.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 打开瓶盖，喝下去，感受气泡在你的唇齿喉间跳动，最后打个嗝儿，就这么简单。
decoDesc.en: Pop it open and start chugging. Feel the fizz dance on your tongue, then give a satisfied burp. It's that simple.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 十分考验烹饪者厨艺的菜肴。球刺兽的肝脏火候稍过便会和橡胶一般硬。如何让它拥有与新笋相同的口感——这是各位大厨需要首先解决的难题。
decoDesc.en: A dish that poses a serious challenge to the chef. Quillbeast livers can quickly overcook and assume a texture similar to rubbery leather. A skilled cook must first come up with a way to give it the same tender crisp of young bamboo sprouts.

desc.cn: 使用后可以提升干员战斗效果的消耗品。
desc.en: Use this consumable to improve the operator's combat performance.

noObtainWayHint.cn: <@obt.key>简制手册</>中解锁对应配方后可进行制造
noObtainWayHint.en: Unlock <@obt.key>Crafting Manual</> formula to make this

decoDesc.cn: 在基质蚀刻环节会使用到的特殊冷却脂。温度极易影响到基质蚀刻的结果，故加工环节需使用造价昂贵的冷却脂。
decoDesc.en: A special coolant gel used in the essence etching process. Results of etching are extremely sensitive to temperature changes. This process thus requires the use of coolant gels, which can be extremely expensive to make.

desc.cn: 用于提升基质技能等级的珍贵素材。
desc.en: A rare material that upgrades essence skills.

decoDesc.cn: 记录更多干员使用武器的偏好，聆听他们有关武器的期待……武库工程师们尝试使用通行证这种方式，让终末地的武器研发效率更上一层楼。
decoDesc.en: The Arsenal Engineers are always recording operator weapon preferences and other expectations they have... The Protocol Pass is an attempt used by the Arsenal to boost weapon R&D efficiency in Endfield.

desc.cn:
可为所有协议通行证的武器补给所包含的武器提升潜能，对于未来协议通行证的武器补给中新增的武器同样有效。
(适用武器详情可前往百科查看)
desc.en:
This can raise the potential of any weapon provided by Protocol Pass weapon supplies, including weapon supplies from future pass seasons.
Go to the Database for details on applicable weapons.

decoDesc.cn:
清波寨寨民们“手搓”出的定位工具，稍加改造就能拥有探测醚质的能力。
在接近探测目标后，仪器中的水将猛地沸腾起来，因此需要小心使用。
decoDesc.en:
A positioning tool "handcrafted" by the residents of Qingbo Stockade. A few simple tweaks gave it the ability to detect Aurylene. 
Use with caution. The water within the device will start boiling violently as one approaches the item being detected.

desc.cn: 消耗品，使用后可探测出当前区域内的一个未发现的醚质。解锁当前区域所有地图迷雾后才可使用。（仅限武陵地区生效）
desc.en: Consumable. Usage reveals an undiscovered Aurylene within the current area. Usable only after all fogged places of the map have been charted. This item only works in Wuling.

decoDesc.cn:
使用了息壤技术的小型探测器，能有效确认特殊金属的位置，因此可以被用来寻找储藏箱。
崭新出厂！熠熠生辉！
decoDesc.en:
A small detector furnished with Xiranite technology, giving it the ability to accurately locate metallic objects. The detector can thus be used to locate storage crates. 
Fresh off the production line! Look how it shimmers!

desc.cn: 消耗品，使用后可探测出当前区域内的一个未发现的储藏箱。解锁当前区域所有地图迷雾后才可使用。（仅限武陵地区生效）
desc.en: Consumable. Usage reveals an undiscovered storage crate within the current area. Usable only after all fogged places of the map have been charted. This item only works in Wuling.

decoDesc.cn: 将源石与巨兽力量结合于一处后诞生出的新型源石材料。它撑起了武陵的万家灯火。
decoDesc.en: A novel Originium-based material acquired by fusing the mineral with Feranmut power. This material fuels life and prosperity in Wuling.

desc.cn: 通过特殊设备获得的材料，可用于特殊设施修复或与据点进行交易。
desc.en: A material produced by a specialized facility. Can be used for repairing special facilities or for trading with various outposts.

noObtainWayHint.cn: 工业发展后使用设备生产

decoDesc.cn: 只需在协议同步器轻轻一扫，后勤部将立刻为您提供海量优惠服务。
decoDesc.en: Scan this with the Protosync and the Logistics Division will offer you tons of special perks, privileges, and services.

desc.cn: 使用后可获得30天的月卡权益。
desc.en: Use this to get Monthly Pass perks for 30 days.

decoDesc.cn: 一部分终末地干员喜欢将协议通行证称为“许愿单”。传说只要在生日前夜许愿，并在床头放上一些衍质源石，就会有善良的武库小机器人送来令人满意的产品。
decoDesc.en: Some Endfield operators enjoy referring to the Protocol Pass as their "wishlist". According to rumors, those who make a wish and place some Origeometry by their pillows during the eve of their birthdays will receive a satisfying reward from the kind little robots of the Arsenal.

desc.cn: 使用后可激活协议通行证的源石配给档位。
desc.en: Use this to activate the Protocol Pass tier: Originium Supply.

decoDesc.cn: “好了，只要在这里签字，您就可以拥有独属于您的定制版协议通行证……嗯？效率？放心吧，必要情况下，我们会空投物资支援的。”
decoDesc.en: "Good. Just sign your name here and you'll get your very own customized Protocol Pass... Oh? Efficiency? Don't worry. We'll airdrop the supplies to your place if necessary."

desc.cn: 使用后可激活协议通行证的协议定制档位。
desc.en: Use this to activate the Protocol Pass tier: Protocol Customized.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>砂叶</>和<@tips.key>紫晶纤维</>，自动生产<@tips.key>高晶纤维</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Sandleaves</> and <@tips.key>Amethyst Fibers</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>Cryston Fibers</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>紫晶矿</>，自动生产<@tips.key>紫晶纤维</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Amethyst Ore</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>Amethyst Fibers</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>蓝铁瓶</>和<@tips.key>锦草溶液</>，自动生产<@tips.key>锦草软饮</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Ferrium Bottle</> and <@tips.key>Jincao Solution</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>Jincao Drink</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>蓝铁瓶</>和<@tips.key>芽针溶液</>，自动生产<@tips.key>芽针针剂</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Ferrium Bottles</> and <@tips.key>Yazhen Solution</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>Yazhen Syringes [C]</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入可形成溶液的<@tips.key>植物</>和<@tips.key>清水</>，自动生产<@tips.key>植物溶液</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input soluble <@tips.key>plants</> and <@tips.key>Clean Water</> to auto-produce the <@tips.key>solution of that plant</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>芽针</>和<@tips.key>清水</>，自动生产<@tips.key>芽针溶液</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Yazhen</> and <@tips.key>Clean Water</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>Yazhen Solution</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>息壤</>和<@tips.key>致密源石粉末</>，自动生产<@tips.key>低容武陵电池</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Xiranite</> and <@tips.key>Dense Originium Powder</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>LC Wuling Batteries</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>蓝铁瓶</>和<@tips.key>任意液体</>，自动生产<@tips.key>装满该液体的蓝铁瓶</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Ferrium Bottle</> and <@tips.key>any fluid</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>Ferrium Bottles filled with that fluid</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入1份可采种种植的<@tips.key>植物</>和<@tips.key>清水</>，自动无限生产<@tips.key>植物</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Clean Water</> and 1 unit of <@tips.key>any plant that can be processed at the Seed-Picking Unit and Planting Unit</> to auto-produce an endless amount of <@tips.key>that plant</>.

desc.cn: 在集成核心区域放置此蓝图后，输入<@tips.key>清水</>和<@tips.key>稳定碳块</>，自动生产<@tips.key>息壤</>。
desc.en: Place this blueprint in the Core AIC Area, then input <@tips.key>Clean Water</> and <@tips.key>Stabilized Carbon</> to auto-produce <@tips.key>Xiranite</>.

decoDesc.cn: 一张特殊的人事凭证，为招选具备某些特殊条件的干员而准备，由于准备紧急，它不可避免地受困于时效性。
decoDesc.en: A special HR permit for headhunting operators who meet various unique requirements. Given the emergency of this request, this permit will inevitably expire after a certain time limit.

desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 1 headhunting in [Scars of the Forge] Chartered Headhunting. This certificate will expire when [Scars of the Forge] Chartered Headhunting ends.

desc.en: A limited-time Endfield Industries certificate. Use this to perform 10×headhunting in [The Floaty Messenger] Chartered Headhunting. This certificate will expire when [The Floaty Messenger] Chartered Headhunting ends.

decoDesc.cn: 在开拓区常见的一种武器类型，基础设计已难以追溯。这种武器制造工艺并不复杂，常见工业设备都可生产。
decoDesc.en: A weapon commonly seen in the frontiers. No one knows who came up with the basic designs. This particular piece can be easily produced by common industrial machinery.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 梅什科工业最新推出的独立产品。据传这款设计源于寂语修会的发掘产物，内含绝密技术，分金裂石，无坚不摧。
decoDesc.en: The latest standalone product from Mieszko Industries. Designs were based on a relic unearthed by the Cabal of Tranquility. The weapon itself was furnished with highly classified technologies, allowing it to cut through almost anything with ease.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 北进重工支援所的高端产品。一款采用旧技术设计的链式切割器，目前已不再大规模生产，但设计依然可靠。
decoDesc.en: A high-end product of Northmarch Support Hub. This chain cutter was designed with older technology. Though no longer mass produced, the weapon continues to prove its reliability in the field.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业制造的特别装备之一。焰形剑搭配的交错式源石线路能提高基质效率。灵感来于观测到的塔罗斯现象。
decoDesc.en: A specialized weapon manufactured by Endfield. The flamberge was furnished with interlaced Originium circuitry to enhance essence performance. This setup was inspired by various phenomenon observed on Talos.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 巫术时刻限量发行的特殊武器之一，似乎是依循着什么古老传说打造的外形，仿佛能捕捉梦境中的呻吟。
decoDesc.en: A special limited-release weapon from the Witching Hour. The appearance of the greatsword is probably based on an ancient legend. It seems capable of ripping wails of anguish out of the realm of dreams.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 熔炉要塞出品的制式大剑。虽然精通者寥寥，但由于上手十分简单，历来是新兵的入门武器首选。
decoDesc.en: A standard greatsword made by Fort Forgefane. Although very few have mastered this weapon, the weapon is easy to wield and has been the most popular choice amongst raw recruits for many years.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业制造的干员基础装备之一。由武库工程师达尔霍夫负责设计。该设计为攻坚任务提供装备选择。
decoDesc.en: One of the standard-issue operator weapons manufactured by Endfield Industries. This weapon is designed by Endfield Arsenal Engineer Darhoff. Its designs offer a viable option for those taking part in assault operations.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 宏山选剑局研发的制式大剑。剑身使用了新型特种涂料，防护能力优良，即使处于极端恶劣环境下也能免受影响。
decoDesc.en: A standard greatsword developed by Hongshan Swordmancers. The weapon is furnished with a new specialized coating that offers excellent protection, even if the weapon were to be used in extreme and hostile environments.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 梅什科工业小规模生产的特别产品。本品是梅什科工业与骑士竞技专家克伦威尔合作系列的最后一款设计。
decoDesc.en: A special Mieszko Industries weapon with a limited production run. This was the final design of the collaborative project pursued by the arms company and the Knights Major expert Cromwell.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 巫术时刻推出的古怪武器之一。刀身由寻常的冰块打造，但表面附着的奇特源石技艺让其变得坚不可摧。
decoDesc.en: A strange weapon released by Witching Hour. The blade body is chiseled out of an ordinary-looking block of ice, but its surface is infused with a special form of Originium Arts that made it literally indestructible.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 宏山选剑局制造的优质大剑。较之同类产品，它更轻盈，但杀伤力却没有降低分毫。
decoDesc.en: A quality greatsword manufactured by Hongshan Swordmancers. When compared to other greatswords, this one is lighter but just as deadly.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业出品的系列制式装备。由资深武库工程师奥佩罗所组建的原型创意组设计。可根据实战需求，装配不同的模块套件。
decoDesc.en: A standard weapon produced by Endfield Industries. Design is provided by the Creative Prototyping Team founded by Senior Arsenal Engineer Opero. The weapon can be furnished with various modules according to the needs of actual battle.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业制造的干员进阶装备之一。武库沿用了安德烈的设计方案，可预存储术式，在紧急情况下快速传导法术。
decoDesc.en: One of the advanced weaponry manufactured by Endfield for their operators. The Endfield arsenal adopted Andre's blueprints to create a drone capable of storing Arts so that they can be quickly cast in emergencies.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业制造的干员基础装备之一。由武库工程师吉米尼负责设计。这款施术单元格外受新进干员喜爱。
decoDesc.en: One of the standard-issue operator weapons manufactured by Endfield Industries. This weapon is designed by Endfield Arsenal Engineer Jiminy. The Arts Unit is extremely popular with newly minted Endfield operators.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 终末地工业制造的施术单元之一。结构大胆，传导性强，难以驾驭。许多干员将熟练使用它当作小有所成的证明。
decoDesc.en: One of the Arts units manufactured by Endfield Industries. It sports bold structural designs, superb Arts conductance, but is incredibly difficult to control. Mastering this weapon was considered a proof of competency amongst operators.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 雷神工业研发的一款施术单元，以简洁和轻量著称。其材料用量不足普通施术单元的一半。
decoDesc.en: An Arts unit developed by RAYTHEAN Industries. This particular weapon is known for its minimalist and lightweight designs. Making it requires only half of the materials needed to produce a standard-issue Arts unit.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 巫术时刻推出的古怪施术单元之一。反直觉地削弱了源石技艺的适应性，只为强调古老提卡兹巫术的黑暗逻辑。
decoDesc.en: One of the strange-looking Arts units released by Witching Hour. Its counter-intuitive designs include a deliberately reduced Originium Arts compatibility just to highlight the dark logic of Ancient Teekaz witchcraft.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 轻超域技术实验室签约作品。艺术家亲手錾刻的金属器件与冰碛岩的纹理缀合，形成独一无二的施术回路。
decoDesc.en: A contracted product from Portable Æthertech Labs. Features metal components hand-engraved by cræft-adepts to create etch figures that match those of the tillite parts. The result is an Arts unit with unique Arts casting circuitry.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 宏山选剑局研发的施术单元，采用了珍贵的息壤材料。因其材料特性，使用者必须具备极高的操控准确度。
decoDesc.en: An Arts unit developed by Hongshan Swordmancers and made using Xiranite. Given the fickle nature of this rare material, only wielders capable of the highest levels of focus and precision could wield this Arts unit effectively.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 北进重工支援所开发的施术单元，拥有毫无争议的最佳源石技艺传导性。只有最强壮的使用者才能驾驭这一产品。
decoDesc.en: An Arts unit developed by Northmarch Support Hub. It is, without question, the unit with the best Originium Arts conductance. Only the most capable casters could master this weapon.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 巫术时刻研发的施术单元之一。除了基本源石线路外，一切材质不明。这真的是可以在塔卫二造出来的东西吗？
decoDesc.en: One of the Arts units developed by Witching Hour. With the exception of its basic Originium circuitries, the rest of the unit was constructed using an unknown material. Can this really be built in Talos-II?

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 梅什科工业研发的施术单元之一。选用特制D64钢壳，配多款定制模块。这款产品让人联想起昔日竞技场的烟火秀。
decoDesc.en: One of the Arts units developed by Mieszko Industries. The weapon features special D64 steel chassis and a suite of customizable modules. Its appearance reminds people of firework displays of knight majors from the past.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 雷神工业的经典尖端产品，其原型从第一次天使战争时便投入使用。该产品不断迭代至今，强大的火力意味着安全与保障。
decoDesc.en: A classical top-tier product of RAYTHEAN. Its prototype was deployed in the First Aggeloi War. The weapon has received numerous upgrades and optimizations since then, with the modern version offering incredible firepower that translates into greater protection and safety of the delivery.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 梅什科工业为寂语修会定制的施术单元。该产品从设计、验证到落地生产和调试都在寂语修会修士的指导建议下完成。
decoDesc.en: An Arts Unit designed by Mieszko Industries for Cabal of Tranquility. Every step from product design, verification, manufacturing, to tuning has been carried out under the guidance of a Cabal cleric.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
desc.en: A weapon equipped by Endfield operators to significantly boost their combat capabilities.

decoDesc.cn: 梅什科工业的高端线产品之一。优秀的源石技艺传导性让它不像其他时髦产品那样华而不实。
decoDesc.en: A product from the elite series of Mieszko Industries. This weapon offers excellent Originium Arts conductance, making it more practical than other fashionable pieces that focused on style over substance.

desc.cn: 终末地干员用武器，装备之后可以显著提升干员的作战能力。
